Bote doko ipwa pete dokona sukusale piso peyami. Dokopa bote peyamo dorena piso porambaiye minyuo epapala pyao laiyuo palyapala ipwa doko kasokole minyiya. Minyapala bote doko pyao mangalya mangana piya.
Ene endenge siyamo dokopa nakama peteyami dorena Yesu baa ipwa pete dokona mee ketae moko karo yana yana peya.
Disaepole dupwame baa ipwa dokona yana yana epeyamo doko kando semangolamo lapala pakame kumapala pii poraiyuo lao ipwa kuku nyiyami.
Dokopa Yesumi nakama aopa lamaiyuo, Nakama monarena poraiyuo rali pipala paka nalapape. Dake namba ipunu pilyamo. Mona nemba nalapape, leya.
Dokopa Pitame isingi lao, Kamongo, emba ramo doko ipwa pete dokona yana yana emba karene dokona namba ipu laa, leya. Dokopa baa epena leya.
Dokopa Pita bote doko yaki nyepala pyakala ipwa pete dokona papala Yesu kareyamo dokona yana yana panya peya.
Dopa piyamopape porambaiye doko kandapala pakaya. Pakapala ipwa dokona yalyalana piya. Dopa pipala pii rekyae lao lapala, Kamongo namba lete nyii, leya.
Dokopa Yesumi kingi aopa pyasinju lapala baa minyarala nyepala dopa lamaiya. Akali Anatu kapa ingingi lao poraiyuo suu pyaa nange dake, akipamo embena mona dokona pii lama suu pyalepe? leya.
Nakamba bote dokona pao peteyambinyi dokopa porambaiye doko pyai nao rali piya.
Dokopa wambu bote dokona peteyami dupwame banya lenge kambu dokona pangu sepala, Kinyi emba Anatunya Ikinyingilyamo leyami.
Ipwa pete doko yalo papala yuu Genesarete pao kando nyiyami.
Yuu dokona range akali dupwame baalamo lao kandapala yuu kipwa kipwa dupwa peparaena lapo pena leyaminyisa anga pingi wambu peparae baa kareyamo dokona lanyuo epeyami.
Epapala wambu dupwa banya komau pinjingi doko kapa minyandena lapyali lao piso sakamiyami. Dokopa minyandapa piyami dupwako mee ingiya.
Dokopa Parisi dupwape Mawa Pii mana lenge akali dupwapeme Jerusaleme dokona karo epo Yesu kareyamo dokona epapala dopa lamaiyami.
Rakange kyawa dupwame piyaminyili pyuo pyuo karamano doko akipamo embena disaepole dupwa kaepala dopa pii nalyamisi? Nakama nenge nalana dokopa kingi wate pii napala nenge kandale, leyami.
Baame nakama isingi dopa lamaiya. Akipamo nakama rangena yulu pingi renge dokona reke lao Anatunya mawa pii doko kaepala pii nalyamipi?
Dokona lao Anatumi dopa pipwape leya. Endangi rakangepa rape rape lao karalapape. Mendeme rakange panda endangi kilya kando lara ramo baa pyao kumakalu pirami, leya.
Dopa leyamopape nakamame lao dokopa dopa lenge. Akali mende endangi panda rakange lamaiyuo, Nambana bange emba nyereli doko Anatunya ingyuo waso retapunu silyamo, lara ramo
doko banya rakange rape rape lao nyisa nara ingilyamo, lao karaminyi. Dopa lao karaminyi dokonako suu pyao nakamame doo minyuo pyuo karenge dokona reke lao Anatunya mawa pii kambanyi nembo karaminyi.
Nakama yanengena mamba kiso karenge akali dupwa Anatunya akali Aisayame nakamasa kando nolako dopa leya.
Wambu dapwa meekambunya lao namba ketae pyambuo petaminyi. Namba suu pyaa napala ama wakale wakale suu pyaro petaminyi.
Nakama yanengena mamba kiso nambana kingi lao karapalape nakama rangena mawa pii dupwa Anatunya lapala mana lamaiyuo karaminyi, leya Yesumi.
Wambu malu kareyami dupwa epena lapala Yesumi dopa lamaiya. Kalena sepala soo gisalapape, leto.
Neta singi bange dupwa nenge katana penge dokome imambu kwaeya nange. Nenge katana pii potemo epenge dokome imambu kwaenge, leya.
Banya disaepole dupwa epapala baa dopa lamaiyami. Parisi dupwame embena pii lapinyi doko soo epe nasami doko emba silipi? leyami.
Baame isingi dopa leya. Rakane yake panda karamo dokome ee waingi wara pii naya dupwa peparae yuku nyuo nembarami.

Nakama lao karenale kaeyalapa. Nakamame lenge koo ingyuo karo akali lenge koo yango lapo lanyuo pelyaminyi. Lenge koo mendeme lenge koo yango lanyuo para ramo doko laparae suu mendena rukyala pao palirambi leya.
Dokopa Pitame isingi lamaiyuo, Kongwalu pii doko namwa renge polo langipi, leya.
Dokopa Yesumi dopa leya. Nakama opetae ene soo gisapa nalyamipi?
Neta singi bange nenge kata papala mee andoromba dokona piso ii ranyi nembenge doko see nalyamipi?
Doko pii kambunya epenge doko mona dokona piso epenge dokomeko wambunya imambu kwaenge.

Dokona lao bange monana koko sepala neta epenge dupwa suu pingi koo dupwape wambu pingipi kepo pingipi yuu yuu pyuo pundapala pyuo karenge yulupi waa nyingipi kote lao panga singipi mata kando kyambo lengepe koo yulu dupwa neta epenge.
Renge koo dupwame wambunya imambu kwaenge. Dopa pilyamopape kingi wate pii napala nenge nenge dokome wambunya imambu kwaeya nange, leya.
Yesu yuu doko yaki nyepala yuu Rayapa yuu Saitonepana pinjingi dolapona peya.

Dokopa Kenane enda yuu range mende epapala baa pii ketae palyuo dopa lamaiya. Kamongo, Dapitinya Ikinyingi, namba kando kondapala nyisape. Nambana wanenge doko imambu koo dokome baa maralyapyamopa randa andake nyilyamo, leya.
Dokopa baame isingi mende laa naya. Banya disaepole dupwame epapala baa piso soo, Enda matarena pii rekyae lao epelyamo doko kaepala pena lamai, leyami.
Baame isingi lao, Isaraele rara wambu lapo sipisipi dopale ingyuo ralo pyuo neta karaminyi dupwana iki namba puu lao mapanyi peeya lyakande, leya.
Dopa leyamopape enda doko epo banya lenge kambu dokona wapambu pii pyaro pisipala, Kamongo, namba pyuo nyisape, leya.
Baame isingi lao dopa leya. Wane wanakepena nenge nyuo suwa dupwa karamo dokona pyambuo mairama doko kapa ingya nalyamo, leya.
Dokopa enda dokome dopa leya. Kinyi, Kamongo, dokoko doŋo suwa kauwange dokona nenge kapa injisi rate isa penge doko suwa doko kapa nyuo napa pingi leya.

Dokopa Yesumi baa isingi lamaiyuo dopa leya. Enda, emba kapa ingyara lao poraiyuo suu pyalyane doko kandelyo. Mende pyakapyali yaka lao suu pyapinyi doko angi pinya, leya. Dokopa yuu gii dokopako enda dokona wanenge doko aopa mee ingiya.
Yesu yuu doko yaki nyepala ipwa Galili pete maronge kipwa kipwa dokona kata peya. Papala yuu kyau mendena pulyuo pao peteya.

Dokopa wambu ama malu baa peteyamo dokona epeyami. Kata paa nange dupwape lenge kwaenge papae rambungi pii laa nange dupwape dee anga pingi wambu malu opetaepe lanyuo epapala banya kimbu siyamo dokona reteyaminyipa baame pyuo elya pyuo nyepa piya.

Dokopa pii laa nange dupwa pii lao, papae rambungi dupwa elya pyuo karo, kata papya nange dupwa kata papyuo, lenge koo dupwa lenge rao piyaminyi doko wambu malu kareyaminyi dupwame kandapala nakama ayaka lao mona nembeyami. Mona nembapala Anatu Isaraele wambu dupwame suu pyao karenge doko lakando ketae pyambuyami.

Dokopa Yesumi banya disaepole dupwa epena lapala dopa lamaiya. Wambu malu nambamoo pipya role pyao yuu rema karamwanopa nakama nenge narami see nalyamo dokona namba kondo pilyamo. Kata parami dokopa lopo dokome yame yame lasara lapala nenge naa naraminyipa pena laro lao suu pyaa nalyo, leya.
Dokopa banya disaepole dupwame baa lamaiyuo, Wambu ama malu karaminyi dapwa borete kapa narami dupwa yuu muiyane dakena anjarae nyeramase? leyami.
Yesumi nakama lamaiyuo, Nakamana borete akipare silyase? leya. Nakamame lao, Yanda ipingi nyero oma mendasipa opetae silyamo, leyami.
Wambu malu rukuraka pyuo kareyami dupwa isa yuu dokona petena leya.
Lapala baame borete yanda ipingi nyero dusipape oma dusipape nyepala ange lao ateŋa lapala kau lao disaepole dupwa maiyamopa disaepole dupwame wambu dupwa mokwa soo maiyami.
Dokopa wambu peparae nao sikya pyuo neyami. Enakana nenge kau lasi kakana siyamo dupwa yapo nyuo pisiki minyasi yanda ipingi nyero simbuyami.
Nenge neyami dupwa akali akalisa pao kisima daako, ama malu wakasa 4,000 ) enda wane wanakepe opetae.
Baame wambu malu dupwa pena lapala bote mendena pisipala yuu Makatana lenge dokona epeya.
Parisi dupwape Satyusi dupwapeme epapala baa apa pilyape lao kandalana, yake panda dokona yulu palenge mende namwa pyuo lasaka pirinyi, lao baa piso soo leyami.
Baame nakama isingi lamaiyuo, Alemanji dokopa nakama lao, Yake doko kone wakasa pilyamo dokona kandapala rakya panyi piralyamo lenge kandale.

Yangama dokopa, Yake doko kondamu raro karamo dokona epapu apunda andake epara, lenge kandale. Dopa lao nakamame yake dopa pilyamo dopa pilyamo lao kandapala dopa piralyamo lao singi. Yulu doko silyaminyipape namwa karamano yuu gii dakepale pyuo karaminyi dupwa kandapala enakana mende dopa piralyamo lao kando see nalyaminyi.

Wambu epapu ando karaminyi dupwa koo ingyuo range isakalya pyuo karaminyi. Nakama yulu andake mende pyuo lasaka pii lao karaminyipape yulu andake mende lasaka pii naro. Akali Jona keta piyamo doko suu pyao dopale mende piramopa doko iki kandarami, leya. Lapala nakama yaki nyepala peya.
Banya disaepole dupwa ipwa pete dumuwangu epo kando nyuo dokopa borete kame sepala minya nao mee epo kando nyiyami.
Yesumi nakama lamaiyuo, Parisi dupwape Satyusi dupwapena isi doko pyarepanyi nembo waso karalapape, leya.
Dokopa nakamame range sukusa lao, Namwa borete minya nao imwano kandapala laiamo kandapi, leyami.
Dokopa Yesu dopa lalyaminyi lao sepala dopa leya. Nakama kapa ingingi lao suu pyaa nale nale lao karaminyi akali dupwa, akipamo nakamame, yango sukusa borete see nalyamo dokona lao karamisi?

Kando sepa nalyamisi? Wambu akalisa pao akalisa kingi paki daako ama malu wakasa ( 5,000 ) dupwame borete kingi paki dusipa neyami dokopa nenge kakana siyamo yapo nyuo pisiki minyasi akiparena reteyama lao suu pyaa nao karamisi?

Dokonako ingyuo wambu akalisa kisima daako ama malu wakasa ( 4,000 ) dupwame borete yanda ipingi dusipa neyami dokona nenge kakana siyamo yapo nyuo pisiki minyasi akipare reteyama lao suu pyaa naoko karamisi?
Nambame lao Parisi dupwape Satyusi dupwapena isi doko waso minyuo karalapape, lapu kandapi dokopa mee borete dokona laa napu doko apa pyuo nakama see nalyamisi? leya.
Dopa leyamo dokopa mee boretena isi doko waso kando karalapape laa napyaiyamo. Parisi dupwape Satyusi dupwapena mana pii dokonasa lapyalyamo lao soo manjo nyiyami.
Yesu yuu Sisaria Pilipai kipwa kipwa dokona epapala baame banya disaepole dupwa piso soo, Akali dupwame lkinyingi Akali doko kando apiŋi lao apa lami kandapisi? leya.
Dokopa nakamame lao, Lapome emba Jone bapitisimo nyakamaingi akali doko, lami. Lapome ilalnja lenge, lapome Jeremaya, panda akali Anatunya poropeta akali ingyuo karene lenge, leyami.
Dokopa baame nakama lamaiyuo, Dopa lalyaminyiko doŋo nakama rangeme namba kando apa pyuondeŋe lao suu pilyamisi? leya.
Salmone Pitame isingi lao, Emba Koraisa, Anatu lete karalu karenge dokona Ikinyingi doko, leya.

Dopa leyamo dokopa Yesumi baa isingi lamaiyuo, Saimone Jonena Ikinyingi doko, emba keta renge keyange palamo. Isa akali mendeme doko langyapyande daa. Anatu yake panda karamo dokome emba pyongo pyapyamopa lapi lyakande.

Dokonako ingyuo emba Pita lenge (pii doko kana dopale) doko suu pyao kana andake dokona nambame nambana Elyambu Pingi doko pyakalyinya lao elya piru. Dokopa kumunginya renge poral dokome Elyambu Pingi doko kapa pyao amasu minya nara.
Yake pandana isingi yulu dokona sukusa kambu lumbungi kii yakane dusipa emba jero. Emba isa panda dakena lapo daa larenepape kapalamo larenepape doko yake dorena larene dokonako ingyaraŋa leya.
Lapala baame disaepole dupwa lamaiyuo, Namba kando Koraisa karamo lao mendali lamai nalapape lao lamaiyuokondali piya.

Yuu gii dokopale piso Yesumi banya disaepole dupwa lamaiyuo, Jerusaleme dokona paronopa kamongo dupwape purisi mupwa dupwape Mawa Pii mana lenge akali dupwamepe randa malu jepa pyuo karapala pyao kumakaraminyipa yuu repo dokona lete minyalyuo nyeramo paro ingilyamo, leya.
Dopa leyamo dokopa Pitame baa lambuo nyepala pyalana pyuo lao, Kamongo, Anatumi dopa pii nana lena. Emba keta dopa pyuo paa nana, leya.

Dokopa Yesumi kapu kyepala Pita lamaiyuo, Satane, emba nambana lenge kambu silyamo dorena kata kaepala matarena puu. Mena gyaana kyalende oko sili lao lapisa pilyamo. Emba Anatu suu pyao karamo dokona daa. Isa wambumi suu pinginyili pyuo lapilyamo leya.

Lapala Yesumi banya disaepole dupwa lamaiyuo, Akali mende namba paronuli pyuo eparo lao suu pyara ramo doko baa range kame soo kaepala banya isa mamando minyalyuo nyepala soo namba paronuli pyuo epara.
Mendeme baa range kyawa lete nyera ramo doko lete karenge doko pyakuiyuo nembarasa pira. Dee mendeme nambana kingi reke lao koo keta palyuo kumara ramo dokome range lete wai pyao nyerasa pira.

Dokona lao akali mendeme yuu muu dupwana bange peparae nyuo karara ramo dokopa banya kyakana renge doko yaki nyuo kaeyara ramo dokome elyape keta parase? Mendeme banya kyakana renge doko yaki nyuo kaera ramo doko bange akimi range yano pyao nyerase?
Dokona lao lkinyingi Akali doko banya Rakangena yanga paupau lenge doko paleta banya aŋala dupwa role pyao epapala akali dupwa peparae nakamana yulu pyuo karengenyili pyuo yole maira.
Kinyi langilyu, lapo dae karaminyi dusipame ene kumapa naraminyipa Ikinyingi Akali kiŋi ingyuo eparamo kandarami, leya.
Yuu pakinyamange epo papeyamopa Yesumi Pitamoo Jemesa yangonge Jonemoo nyuo lanyuo yuu kyau londe mendena nakama yeelyo karala peyami.

Peyaminyi dokopa baame nakama dusipana lenge kambu siyamo dorena karapala baa wamba yongo karenge doko kaepala yongo wakale maralyiya. Dokopa banya lenge kambu doko neta rao karenge doko suu pyao rao kareyamopa banya komau dusipa yanga paupau lao kyewa lao mama nyiya.
Dokopa llainja Mosesepa pano epapala nakamba Yesumoo pipya nakama lao pii mende leyaminyi akali dusipame kando kareyami.

Dokopa Pitame Yesu lamaiyuo, Kamongo, namwa dae kapa karamano. Embame dopa pipili lao suu pyare ramo doko namba anda paka rema yukurole. Mende embena mende Mosesena mende llainjana pyakamyuo piruwale, leya.

Ene lao kareyamo dokopa kopa kyewa lenge mende epo nakama kareyami dokona yambe piya. Yambe piyamo dokopa kopa dokona piso pii mende lao epeya. Akali dake nambana lkinyingiŋi nambame baa mona retapala rae mallyu. Banya pii soo karalapape, leya.
Disaepole dusipame pii doko sepala pangu soo lenge kambu yambe pyaro soo ama pakayami.
Dopa piyaminyipape Yesumi epo nakama minyandapala, Paka napala sipuralapape, leya.
Dokopa nakamame lenge pendekae lapala Yesu baa iki kareyamo kandeyami.

Yuu kyau dokona lupyuo epo dokopa Yesumi nakama lamaiyuokondali pyuo lao Ikinyingi Akali ene kumuo palyuo lopo minyalyuo nyepa naramo dokopa pii repa repa pipyamo kandalaminyi kandapi doko dopa pipyaŋa lao wambu mendali lamai nalapape, leya.
Dokopa disaepole dusipame baa piso soo, Dopa lapinyipape, akipamo Mawa Pii mana lenge akali dupwame llalnja wambo epara ingilyamo lao karengese? leyami.
Yesumi isingi lao, llainja baa wambo eparako doŋo. Epapala dokopa yulu peparae rolae sinya lao pyuo rapa rapa pira ingilyamo.

Ilainja baa wambo epapeya leto. Epeyamo dokopa wambumi baalyamo lao soo gisa napala baa kando suu pilyamano ote lao mee langa pyuo kareyami. Doko suu pyao lkinyingi Akali baa dopa piraminyipa randa nara, leya.
Dopa leyamo dokopa disaepole dusipame Jone bapitisimo nyakamaingi dokonasa lalyamo lao soo manjo nyiyami.
Wambu malu rukuraka pyuo kareyami dokona epeyaminyi dokopa akali mende dokona epapala wapambu pii pyaro piso dopa leya.

Kamongo, Yesu embame nambana ikinyingi doko kondapala pyuo nyakape. Baa manda rengeme manjipa pilyamopa baa randa andake nao karenge. Yuu malu baa isare dokona rukyala pao palipa pingi, yuu malu ipwa dokona rukyala pao palipa pingiko.
Doko embena disaepole dupwa karaminyi dokona baa lanyuo ipunupa nakamame baa pyuo elya pyuo nyelana saka nalaminyi, leya.

Dopa leyamo dokopa Yesumi dopa lao isingi leya. Nakama wambu epapu ando karaminyi dupwa Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyaa napala simbi simbi pyuo karaminyi. Yuu akipare namba nakama pipya role pyao kararamase? Yuu akipare nakama ukiaki minyuo kararaminyipa nambame nakama mata kui lao mana langyuo kararose? Namba karo dakena wane doko lanyuo ipupwa, leya.
Dokopa Yesumi imambu koo doko kando pyalana pyuo lamaiyamopa imambu koo doko wane yaki nyuo neta epeyamopa wane doko aopa mee kareya.
Enakana Yesu iki kareyamo dokopa banya disaepole dupwa epo baa piso siyami. Imambu koo doko raka lanyi nembalana saka namwa doko apa pipyasa pipya, leyami.

Baame nakama lamaiyuo, Anatumi kapa ingingi doko angingyuo suu pyaa nami dokona saka nami. Dokona lao kinyi langilyu, isa masata waingi kuki ingilyamo dokona manda manju Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyarami ramo doko nakamame yuu kyau dake kando purukuo dumurena pena laraminyipa dokona para. Dokona mende pinya saka naa narami.
Doko nenge wasaka pyuo ateŋa lao pisa narami ramo doko yulu dopale kapa pii narami, leya.
Yuu Galili dokona disaepole dupwa epo sukusa sukusa pyuo kareyami dokopa Yesumi nakama lamaiyuo, Ikinyingi Akali doko akali lapo keta minya sakamiraminyipa
pyao kumakaraminyipa yuu repo dokopa lete minyalyuo nyera ingilyamo, leya. Dokopa nakama monarena randame kumuo kareyami.
Yuu Kapaneame dokona epeyaminyi dokopa tembole anda dokona lao takisi nyingi akali dusipame Pita kareyamo dokona papala, Embena mana lenge dokome tembole anda dokona lao takisi pyaa nangese? leyami.

Baame lao, Daa, baa takisi pingi, leya. Lapala anda epeyamo dokopa Yesumi wambo baa lamaiyuo, Saimone, embame apa lao suu pilipi? Isa yuu dakena kiŋi akali dupwame apimoome takisi kana pinya lengese? Nakambana yuu range wambu dupwa panda wambu menge dupwase? leya.
Dokopa, Wambu menge dupwa pinya lao karenge, leyamo dokopa Yesumi baa lamaiyuo, Dokona lao banya wambu dupwa koo soo karenge.

Koo soo karengeko doŋo akali dusipa imbu singi nyakamisarama lapala embame ipwa kota dokona papala uku pyambware. Dokopa oma wambo peparae nenge kata doko angapu lakipala kana mone mende kando nyere. Doko nyepala namwana takisi doko suu pyao akali dusipa mairi, leya.
Yuu gii dokopa disaepole dupwa Yesu kareyamo dokona epapala, Yake pandana isingi yulu dokona api mendali mupwa wakasa ingyuo karape? leyami.
Dopa leyami dokopa baame wane mende epena lapala nakama kareyami dokona sukusa pyambuya.

Pyambwapala dopa leya. Kinyi langilyu, nakama mona kapu kyepala wane wanakepena mona palenge dopale ingyuo kara narami ramo doko nakama yake pandana isingi yulu dokona sukusa kando nyii naramisa pira.
Mendeme wane dake namba kuki ingyuo karo lao suu pinginyili pyuo suu pyao karara ramo doko yake pandana isingi yulu dokona mupwa ingyuo kararasa pira.
Mendeme nambana kingi lao wane dapale yako lao nyera ramo doko namba yako lao nyerasa pira leya.

Dokonako suu pyao mendeme namba kapa ingingi lao suu pyao petaminyi wambu kuki dokona mende suu longwanyi koo keta pyambwara ramo doko akali pyambwara dokona pendoko dokona kana reeko mende anjapala baa ipwa kota dokona koko kumunya lao pyao pyambwamili doko kapa ingyapyali.
Isa yuunya akalimi akali yango kata koona ralinyi pyambwarami dupwa kondo piralyamo. Kinyi yulu dopale pyaka serako doŋo, akali angi randa nyuo maira doko koo keta paliralyamo.

Dokona suu pyao embena kingi pakipi panda kimbu pakipimi emba suu longwanyi koo keta pyambwara ramo doko pyao pyakepanyi nembare. Emba kingi paki panda kimbu pakipi molo molo pisi kareta karo lete karenge arapu dokona parene dokome kapa pira. Doko kaepala emba kingi laparaepe panda kimbu laparaepe karepeta kararenepa isare uliyapu nyuo rao karalu karenge panda dokona emba nyuo pyambwarami ramo doko kapa pii nara.

Doko suu pyao embena lenge dokome emba koo dokona suu longwanyi pyambwara ramo doko emba lukunyi nembare. Emba lenge paki iki rao seramo lete karenge arapu dokona parene dokome kapa piramopa lenge laparae rao seramo kararenepa isare panda dokona pyambwarami doko kapa pii nara.

Wambu kuki karaminyi dapwana mende kando angi daaŋa lao suu pyasarama lao waso karalapape. Dokona lao nakama dopa langilyu. Wambu kuki dupwana aŋala dupwa yake panda dokona karapala nambana Rakange yake panda karenge dokona lenge kambu kando karaminyi.
Dokona suu pyao Ikinyingi Akali dokome wambu koo keta pupingele petaminyi dupwa nyiso pyuo nyela epeya.

Apa lao suu pilyamisi? Akali mende banya mena sipisipi akalisa pao akalisa kararaminyi dokona mende anda epa nara ramo dokopa baame sipisipi akalisa mange mendaki dee ipisu mange mendakiko karo dupwa yuu kyau pyalya pyana pingi dokona mee karena lapala mendaki pana nayamo doko koto nyela paa narase?
Dokona suu pyao kinyi langilyu, sipisipi akalisa mange mendaki dee ipisu mange mendakiko neta paa narami dupwa rae maiyuo kondaramopape mende paramo nyera doko ama wakasa rae maiyuo kondara.
Doko suu pyao nambana Rakange yake panda karenge dokome wambu kuki karaminyi dokona mende isa paa namili lao suu pyao karamo.

Akali yango mendeme yulu koo emba keta piya kande doko baa karamo dokona papala nakamba iki piso baa koo pyuo karamo dokona rolo lamairi. Baame embena pii sera ramo doko embena yangonepa puu minyuo kararambisa pira.
Paa see nara ramo doko akali lama panda rema Baepole letamuii pyuo nakambana pii sinya lao lanyuo pare.

Baa dee nakambana pii see nara ramo emba Elyambu Pingi lamaipi. Dokopa Elyambu Pinginya wambu larami doko see nara ramo doko baa Juu daa rara wakale akalipi takisi nyingipi ingyuo karena lapala baa puu minya nare.
Kinyi langilyu, nakama isa yuu dakena lapo daa laraminyipape kapalamo laraminyipape doko yake panda dorena larene dokonako ingyaraŋa leya.
Dee mende langilyu. Nakama isa yuu dakena karo dokopa mendakinya palyuo mende pinya lao suu pyao ateŋa larami dokopa nambana Rakange yake panda karenge dokome pyakara.
Dokona lao wambu lama panda rema nambana kingi lao elyambu pyuo pisirami ramo dokona namba sukusa role pyao pisirusa pira, leya.

Dokopa Pitame baa kareyamo dokona epapala dopa leya. Kamongo, yuu akipare nambana yangongeme namba kando yulu koo jepa piramopa nambame nyuo kame sakamyuo kararose? Yuu yanda ipingi nyero piramopa nambame kame sakamipa pirose? leya.
Leyamopa Yesumi baa dopa lamaiya. Mee yanda ipingi iki daa, yuu akalisa pao akalisa yanda ipingi nyeroko daa, ama malu wakasa koo embapa pipa piramopa nyuo kame sakamyuo karare leto, leya.

Lapala dopa leya. Dokona suu pyao kiŋi akali mendeme banya yulu pingi akali dupwa baa keta bange mairamili dupwa joo otena laro leya doko suu pyao yake pandana isingi yulu doko kapa makande minyuo larama.
Baame kana akipare jerami ingilyase lao kanda soo yaka leyamo dokopa akali mende baame kana ama malu paka milyane dopale doko lanyuo baa kareyamo dokona epeya.

Dokopa baa maiyalana saka nayamo dokona banya kamongo dokome lao, Baamoo banya etengemoo banya wane wanake dusipape banya bange retenge dupwa peparaepe ropo pyao maipala dokome baa namba kana jerali dusipa range nyero, leya.
Dopa leyamo dokopa kendemande akali dokome wapambu pii pyaro pisipala dopa lao ama piso sokondali piya. Kamongo embame namba walyako lao laa napipi. Bange peparae kapa jeroŋo leya.
Dokopa kendemande akali dokona kamongo dokome kondapala baa mokwapala baa kana mairali dupwa kaena lao nyuo kame sakamiya.

Dopa piyamopape kendemande akali dokomeko potemo paowale pyuo karo kandeyamo kendemande akali yango mende baa kana kina mendasipa serakamiyande mairali doko kareyamo kando nyiya. Kando nyepala banya mange doko minyapala, kana jereli dupwa peyakana leya.
Dopa leyamo dokopa kendemande yango doko yuunya pongwa naro pisipala poraiyuo piso sokondali pyuo, Namba waiyako lao laa napipi. Dokopa kana kapa yano pyakaro, leya.
Leyamopa kana range akali baame daa lapala kana ene jepa nara mange dusipana karapusi anda dokona palena leya.
Dokopa kendemande yango lapo dupwame dopa piyamo doko kandapala mona randayami. Mona randapala nakamana kamongo kareyamo dokona pao dopa pipya dopa pipya lao baa pakana palyuo lamaiyami.
Dokopa banya kamongo dokome baa epena lapala dopa lamaiya. Emba kendemande akali ama koo. Embame namba rolo piso sokondali pipinyisa dokona kana malu wakasa jereb' dupwa peparae kame sakao kaeyapu.
Kaeyapunupa nambame emba kando sakapala kaeyapu doko suu pyao embame kendemande akali yango doko kando kame sakamipala kaeyaronde pipu lao suu pyaa nalese? leya.
Lapala imbwuapala banya kamongo dokome kana jereli dupwa peparae ene jepa naro ramo dokopa karapusi dokona palu palira lao karapusi rapu pingi akali dusipa keta maiya.
Doko suu pyao nakamame nakamana yangone mendena koo dupwa monarena nyuo kame sakami narami ramo doko nambana Rakange yake panda karenge dokome nakama dopako pira, leya.
Yesu pii dupwa lao otapala yuu Galili doko yaki nyepala yuu Jutia dokona ipwa Jotane dumwarena pyakambuo peya.
Peyamopa wambu malu mee rukuraka pyuo baa peyamuii pyuo peyaminyipa baame yuu dokona karo nakama pyuo nyepa piya.

Dokopa Parisi dupwame baa kareyamo dokona epapala baa apa letape lao selana makande pyuo dopa lao piso siyami. Namwana Mawa Pii palenge buku dokona renge anjukunya ingyuo enda kapa ramanyi nembarama lao apa letase? leyami.
Baame isingi lao, Kanda soo dokopa Anatumi wambu enda akalipa pyuo wasiyamo doko yaka lao kanda nayamisi?
Akali mende banya endangi rakangepa yaki nyuo banya enda dokopa pako mendaki ingyuo pisirambi, leyamo pii pyasi palamo doko nakamame kando yaka laa nangese? leya.

Anatumi lao, Dokopa mendaki ingyuo pisirambi, leyamo dokona wamba nakamba wakale wakale ingyuo pisirambi doko kaepala mendaki ingyuo pisirambi. Dokona Anatumi pakaramo doko wambumi rekya laa nana, leya Yesumi.
Nakamame baa lamaiyuo, Dopa leeneko doŋo akipamo Moseseme lao, Enda ramanyi nembalana lao kande dokopa pepa pase pyao maipala dokopa kapa enda ramanyi nembalapape, leyase? leyami.

Yesumi nakama lamaiyuo, Nakama mona kana pokapala kareyaminyisa dokona Moseseme saka napala enda kapa ramanyi nembarami leya. Dopa leyamopape ene kanda soo busiyamo kareyaminyi dokopa yulu doko pali naya.

Dokona dopa langilyu, Mendeme banya enda doko ramanyi nembapala enda mende wakale nyera ramo doko kepo pili lao pirasa pira. Enda mende akali wakale mendepa kepo pirambi ramo renge dokona iki kapa ramanyi nembara, leya.
Disaepole dupwame baa lamaiyuo, Enda akalipa nyingi dokopa dopa piralyamo dokona enda nyii napenge ingyalyamo leyami.
Yesumi lao, Pii doko akali peparae keta pali nara ingilyamo. Lapome kapa piramili dupwame iki soo yako lao nyerami ingilyamo.

Dokona suu pyao akali lapo etembo ingyuo mandeyami, akali lapo enda nyii naramili ingyuo karena lao yulu mende piyamisa etembo ingyuo karaminyi, akali lapo yake pandana isingi yulu dokona lao etembo ingyuo karamana lapala enda wanjo karaminyi. Dae leto dake akali mendeme soo yako lao kapa nyerami dupwame soo yako lao nyelapape, leya.
Dokopa wane wanakepe lapo baa kareyamo dokona lanyuo epo kingi ketae reto ateŋa lakapyali lao lanyuo epeyami. Dokopa disaepole dupwame wambu dupwa pyalana pyuo epa kaena leyami.
Dopa leyaminyipa Yesumi lao, Wane wanakepe dupwa namba karo dokona epenaleŋe kaena laa nalapape. Wane wanake dopalena yake dorena isingi panda doko sakamilyamo, leya.
Lapala banya kingi nakama ketae retakamipala yuu doko yaki nyepala peya.
Baa peyamo dokona akali mendeme epapala baa dopa lamaiya. Mana Lenge aki yulu keyange mende pyuo kararonosa kyakana renge kulisa palu palenge doko nyero lyasilisi? leya.

Dokopa Yesumi baa lamaiyuo, Aki rengendena embame yulu keyange dokona namba piso silisi? Mendaki iki keyange ingyuo karamo. Embame kyakana renge palu palenge arapu dokona sukusa paro lao suu pyare ramo doko mawa pii dupwa minyuo rolae pyuo karape, leya.
Akali dokome Yesu lamaiyuo, Mawa pii akisipa? leya. Dokopa Yesumi lao, Wambu yango pyaa nalapape, Kepo pyakami nalapape, Waa nyii nalapape, Kyambo laa nalapape,
Endangi rakangepa rape rape lao karalapape. Dee mende doko range mona reto karaminyi doko suu pyao wambu maki palenge dupwa kando dopako pyuo mona reto karalapape, mawa pii dusipana leto, leya.
Wanyane akali dokome baa lamaiyuo, Yulu dusipa peparae nambame pyuoko karenge. Aki yulu mende nambame pii nange doko piru ingilyape? leya.

Yesumi baa lamaiyuo, Embame mondo wakasa lao kararo lao suu pyare ramo doko embena bange retenge dupwa ropo pyao maipala kana laeyo nyuo pendewa wambu dupwa mokwa soo mairi. Dokopa yake panda dorename renge kulisa emba keta sakaraŋa. Dopa pipala namba paronuli pyuo ipupi, leya.
Pii doko sepala wanyane akali dokona bange malu mee retenge dokona baa sakapala kala peya.
Dokopa Yesumi banya disaepole dupwa lamaiyuo, Kinyi langilyu, Akali bange malu retenge dupwame yake pandana isingi yulu dokona sukusa panya suu pyarami ramo doko randa nao kando nyerami, leya.

Dee mende langilyu. Mena kamele doko wamyale dalyarena rumbisi kata dokona kolala kapa paa nange doko kolala pupyali doko randa nawale pupyali leya. Dokako suu pyao akali bange malu retenge mendeme Anatunya isingi yulu dokona sukusa parowale lara ramo dokopa randa nawale parali leya.
Dopa leyamo sepala disaepole dupwame mona nembo ralo pisipala lao, Wambu apimoo lete wai pyao nyeramo parami leyami.
Dokopa Yesumi nakama kando dopa lamaiya. Isa akali dupwame kapa pirami ingya nalyamo. Ingya napyamopa Anatu baa yulu peparae kapa awa awa pyuo pira, leya.
Dokopa Pitame dopa leya. Namwame namwana bangepe rarape dupwa peparae yaki nyuo kaeyo emba peenyili pyuo epeyama kande. Dokona aki mende nyeramase? leya.

Yuu gii enenge doko pyaka seramo dokopa lkinyingi Akali baa kiŋinya petenge isa neta renge dokona pisira. Dokopa nakama namba moko minyuo epenge dupwa petenge isa akalisa ipisu lama dusipana pisipala Isaraele rara akalisa ipisu lama dusipa rapu pili laro kararami leya.

Dokona suu pyao wambu mendeme andape panda yangonge dupwape panda pemalengepe panda rakange endangipi panda wane wanakepe panda yuu rangepe nambana kingi reke lao yaki nyiyami ramo dupwame akalisa pao akalisa pyasara pyasara pyuo alo pyuo nyerami. Nyepala kyakana renge kulisa palu palenge doko nyeramiko.
Doko wambu epapu mupwa ingyuo karaminyi dupwa kamame kuki ingyarami. Dokopa kamame kuki ingyuo karaminyi dupwa mupwa ingyuo kararami, leya Yesumi.

Lapala dopa leya. Dokona lao akali angingyuo karenge mendeme wamba kukwa banya isa girapo ee dokona yulu p yakarami lapala yulu pingi akali lapo rombo palyuo lanyala peyamo doko yake pandana isingi yulu doko dopale.
Baa papala yuu mendaki yulu pirami dokopa kana mone mendaki jero leyamosa kapaŋa leyami. Kapa leyami dokopa banya girapo ee dokona yulu pela pena leya.
Enakana mena moko rali pingi (nane keloke ingyuowale) dokopa baa dee kamba papala akali wakale lapo ropo pingi kamapi dokona mee kareyaminyi kandeya.
Kandapala baame nakama lamaiyuo, Nakama opetae nambana girapo ee dokona yulu pela pupwa. Dokopa kana nyingi doko suu pyao manda manjo jero, leya. Dokopa nakama peyami.
Enakana dee neta damasa penge dokopape dee kamba papa pyuo yulu akali lapo nyepa piya.
Kama enakana neta yapa sii pingi dokopa baa deeko papala akali wakale lapo kareyaminyi kandeyako. Kandapala dopa lamaiya. Akipamo nakama doo koto koto doko karamisi? leya.
Nakamame baa lamaiyuo, Mendeme namwa yulu nyuo jii napya dokona mee karamano, leyami. Baame nakama lamaiyuo, Nakama opetae nambana girapo ee dokona pyaa pupwa, leya.

Yuu kone pupuripi piyamo dokopa girapo ee range akali dokome banya yulu pingi akali yango rapu pyuo karenge akali doko lamaiyuo, Yulu pilyaminyi akali dupwa epena lapala kingi kiso nembape. Kamame enakana imi dupwa wambo kingi kiso pao wambakao imi duwpa enakana kingi kiso pipi, leya.
Dokopa neta yapa sii pingipa yulu nyuo maiya akali dupwa epapala dokopa nakama peparae kana angi mendaki lao nyepa piyami.
Wambakao yulu pela epeyami dupwa epapala dokopa kana konda pyuwale nyerama lao masiyami. Masiyaminyipape nakama peparae mee kana mendakiko lao nyepa piyami.
Nyepala nakamame akali kamongo angi doko kando mumu leyami.
Kamame enakana imi dupwa keloke gii mendaki iki pyuo karaminyipape namwa yulu andake pyuo neta dokona kepo minyuo karo pimwa doko nakama namwa dopale ingyuowako maipilyamo, leyami.
Dopa leyaminyipa baame nakama kareyaminyi dokona mende kando isingi dopa lamaiya. Yangone nambame emba koo mende pyaka nalyo. Kana mendaki jero lapunu dokopa embame kapa laa napi kandapisi?
Embena ingilyamo doko nyepala anda puu. Nakama kana jelono doko kamame enakana iminyi dupwa dopako pyuo mairu lao suu pyapala maiyalono.
Nambana range mone dokome mende piroŋo lao suu pyaronuli pyuo kapa mee pii narose? Nambame ipyuo mailinyi lapala nakama ingi koo palyaramisi? leya.
Dopa pilyamo doko suu pyao enakaro palaminyi dupwa wambakaro palirami. Dokopa wambakaro palaminyi dupwa enakaro palirami, leya Yesumi.
Enakana Yesumi Jerusaleme dokona lalyuo pao dokopa disaepole akalisa ipisu lama dupwa yapalyuo nyepala katasa nakama yalu pyuo dopa lamaiya.
Namwa Jerusaleme dokona lalyuo pelyama kande. Dokona Ikinyingi Akali doko purisi akali mupwa dupwape mawa pii mana lenge akali dupwape keta mairaminyipa nakamame kote lao baa kapa kumunya larami.
Lao otapala wambu rara wakale dupwa keta mairaminyipa nakamame baa giyalya giyana pyuo pyaroko pyao isa mamandona pyao palyuo pirami. Piraminyipa yuu repo dokopa lete minyalyuo nyera, leya.
Sepetena etenge dokome banya ikinyingi dolapo lanyuo Yesu kareyamo dokona epo wapambu pii pyaro piso mende pyakana lao piso siya.
Dokopa baame enda doko lamaiyuo, Apa pyakalase lao letepe? leya. Baame Yesu lamaiyuo, Embena isingi panda dokona nambana ikinyingi dalapo embena kingi ralipi pisirambi lakape, leya.
Dokopa Yesumi isingi lao, Emba piso silinyi doko renge soo gisa nalene. Namba kapo mendena naro dokonako nakambame kapa narambisi? leya. Nakambame baa lamaiyuo, Nambwa kapa naramba, leyambi.

Baame nakamba dopa lamaiya. Namba kapo naro dokonako narambi doŋo nambana kingi rolaerenape kingi kyairenape pisirambi dokona namba laro ingya nalyamo. Nambana Rakangeme lao rapa rapa pingi dupwa pisirami, leya.
Dokopa akali akalisa kareyami dusipame dopa lalyambinyi lao sepala yangonge dolapo kando imbwuayami.

Dokopa Yesumi nakama epena lapala dopa leya. Juu daa rara wakale dupwana kamongo dupwame isare rao iso karo nakamana akali mupwa dupwame dopa pinya dapa pinya lao karelyaminyipa pingi kandale doko nakamame silyaminyi.
Yulu dopa pingi makande doko nakama nyii nalapape. Mendeme nakama dokona andake ingyuo karapuli lao suu pyare ramo doko nakamana isaro pingi ingyuo pyuo karare.
Mendeme nakama dokona mupwa ingyuo karapuli lao suu pyare ramo doko nakamana kendemande ingyuo karare.
Doko suu pyao lkinyingi Akalimi baa wambumi isaro pyuo karena lao epa napala baame wambu dupwa isaro pyuo karala epeya. Baa range kumuo maira dokome wambu malu kiiramo nyela epeya.
Enakana yuu Jereko yaki nyuo peyami dokopa wambu malu mee rukuraka pyuo peyamuli pyuo peyami.

Dokopa akali lama lenge kwaengende kata nemba nemba dokona peteyambi. Nakambame Yesu epo pelyamo leyaminyi doko sepala kyakale lao, Dapitinya Ikinyingi, nambwa kando kondome kumuo pyuo nyepe, leyambi.
Dokopa wambu dupwame nakamba pyalana pyuo pii laa kaena leyami. Leyaminyipape nakambame porakalyuo kaeyo dee kyakale lao, Kamongo, Dapitinya Ikinyingi, nambwa kando kondome kumuo pyuo nyepe, leyambi.
Dokopa Yesumi mee karapala nakamba epena lamaiyuo, Aki mende pyakalese lao suu pilyambipi? leya.
Nakambame baa lamaiyuo, Kamongo, nambwana lenge dolapo elya pyuo nyakape, leyambi.
Dokopa Yesumi nakamba kondapala lenge dolapo minyanyi pyakamiyamosa aopa lenge rapala baa peyamuli pyuo peyambi.

Enakana nakama yuu Jerusaleme repeta epo Isa Olipi Kyau dokona yuu Betepasi singi dokona epeyami dokopa Yesumi disaepole lama pena lao dopa lamaiya. Yuu damasa anda lapo repe repe pyuo karenge dokona papala donge kumwambona mende endangi dokopa role pyao anjaro palirambinyi aopa kandarambi. Dolapo polapala namba karo dakena minyuo ipupwape.
Wambu mendeme nakamba kando larami ramo doko Kamongo dokome mende piru lapyasa nyilyambano lao range walya lao dakena lanyakao pena lalopyamo larambi, leya.
Dopa piyamo doko Anatunya poropeta akali mende wamba' leya pii doko pyaka siya. Poropetana pii doko dopa leya.
Nakamana Kiŋi doko epapu nakama keta epelyamo lao, Yuu Sayone range wambu dupwa lamaiyalapape. Pau lao epo donge dokona petamo, dongena ikyane kumwambona dokona petamo, leya.
Yesumi disaepole dolapo dopa pinya leyamuli pyuo pao nyiyambi.
Donge endangi kumwambonapa dolapo lanyuo epapala nakambana komau ketae reteyambinyipa Yesu baa dokona peteya.
Wambu malu rukuraka pyuo kareyami dupwana andapyuwale lapome nakamana komau dupwa nyuo kata barete dokona kwuayaminyi wambu lapome isa yokonge pyake pyao nyuo kata dokona kwuayamiko.

Dokona wambu malu wamboko enakao pyuo peyaminyi dupwame pii porakalyuo kaeyo lao dopa leyami. Dapitinya ikinyingi doko neta ipwamo kandalapa, Kamongona kingi lao epelyamo doko elyape keta penale. Yake dorena lakandamana leyami.
Dokopa baa Jerusaleme dokona sukusa peyamopa anda repe repe pyuo karenge dokona wambu peparae kilyipu kilyipu karalya karana pipala, Doko apisi? leyami.
Dokopa wambu malu rukuraka pyuo epeyami dupwame, Dake Anatunya poropeta Yesu yuu Galili yuu Nasarete range doko, leyami.

Dokopa Yesumi Anatunya tembole dokona kolando papala tembole anda dokona wambu bange ropo pyao lambuo maiyuo laeyo nyuo kareyami dupwa peparae kamanda ralinyi nembeya. Nembapala akali kana mone yango isingi malngi dusipana rate dusipape akali yaka wayamu ropo pyao malngi dusipana isa petenge dusipape baa minyalyapala pyao pyale leya.
Baame nakama lamaiyuo, Dopa lao pyasi palamo. Nambana anda doko ateŋa lenge anda laraminyipa karara, lenge. Dopa lapyamopape nakamame waa nyingi akali dupwana anda ingyuo karena leyamilyamo, leya.
Dokopa wambu lenge koo kimbu kwaengepe dupwa baa tembole anda kareyamo dokona epeyaminyisa baame elya pyuo nyiya.

Dopa piyamopape purisi akali mupwa dupwape Mawa Pii mana lenge akali dupwapeme Yesu yulu ama keyange dupwana pyuo kareyamo dokonape wane wanakepe tembole anda dokona pii porakalyuo kaeyo lao, Dapitinya Ikinyingi neta ipwamo kandalapa lao kareyaminyi dokope kandapala imbwuayami.

Imbwuapala nakamame baa lamaiyuo, Dupwame apa letaminyi lao silipi? leyami. Dokopa Yesumi nakama lamaiyuo, Baepolena pii mende palenge doko nakamame yaka lao kanda nangese? Ene nyaŋa dupwape anju nenge dupwape kambu dokona, lakandenge pii ama rolae larami lao rapa rapa pipilyamo lao pepa piya, leya.
Lapala nakama yaki nyepala anda repe repe pyuo karenge dokona karo kaepala pao yuu Betaui dokona paleya.
Yangama dokopa Yesu dee kapu kyuo anda repe repe pyuo karenge dokona laeyo epo dokopa lopaya.

Lopayamo dokopa isa piki mende kata nemba nemba dokona ando kareyamo kandapala repeta papala isa doko kalu kalu paeyo yoko iki pyuo kareyamo kandeya. Kandapala isa doko kando, Emba rengya jingi ama lyii nalu nao nare, leya. Dokopa isa piki doko walya lao yando nalepo piya.
Dopa piyamo kandapala disaepole dupwame mona nembapala, Isa piki doko apa pipala aopa yando nalape? leyami.

Dokopa Yesumi nakama isingi lamaiyuo, Nakama kinyi langilyu. Nakamame lamana suu pyaa nao Anatumi kapa pira lao suu pyao kararami ramo doko isa piki doko nambame mende pipu doko iki piraminde daa. Yuu kyau dake lamaiyuo, Yuu kyau, emba puruku nyepala Anatumi ipwa kota pete dokona pyambwaramopa dokona karare, larami ramo dokona dopa pira.
Doko suu pyao nakamame ateŋa lao Anatumi kapa pira lao suu pyapala piso serami ramo dokoko dopa pyakara, leya.

Yesumi tembole anda dokona kolandapala mana lao kareyamo dokopa purisi akali mupwa dupwape wambunya kamongo dupwapeme epapala dopa leyami. Pyuo karene doko anja sipyamo nyepala renge palyuo pyuo karene. Apimi emba renge palyapyamopa pyuo karepe? leyami.

Yesumi nakama isingi lamaiyuo, Nambame nakama mende piso seroko. Nakamame isingi lao namba rolo langirami ramo dokopa nambame renge palipyamopa pyuo karo yulu dupwa anja sipyamo nyepala pyuo karo lao nakama langiru, leya.

Lapala, Jone bapitisimo nyakamyuo kareya banya yulu doko anjarae epeya, yake panda dokona piso renge kuiyamo piya panda isa akali dupwame renge kuiyaminyipa piyase? leya. Dokopa nakamame akema lao dopa leyami. Yake panda dokona piso renge kuiyamo piya larama ramo dokopa baame namwa langyuo akipamo Joneme kinyi lalyamo lao suu pyaa nayamisi? laramo lapala
Jonena yulu mee isa akalinya yulu larama ramo doko mee wambu dupwame baa Anatunya poropeta akali lao suu pyao karaminyi dokome namwa laramiŋi lao pakalyamano, leyami.

Lapala dokopa nakamame Yesu isingi lamaiyuo, Namwa see naiyamano, leyami. Dokopa Yesumi nakama lamaiyuo, Dopa letaminyi dokoko suu pyao nambame renge palenge yulu dupwa anja sipyamo nyepala pyuo karo lao isingi langi naro, leya.
Apa lao suu pilyamipi? Akali mendena ikinyingi lama kareyambi. Dokopa baame wane mupwa kareya dokona papala dopa lamaiya. Rakane, epapu emba isa girapo ee dokona yulu pela puu, leya.
Dokopa baame isingi lao, Paa naro daa leya. Dopa leyamopape enakana suu pingi alowa pipala kapa peya.
Rakange dokome wane enakana kareya dokona papala wane mupwa lamaiya dopako pyuo lamaiyamopa baame, Rakane, namba kapaŋa pelyo kae leya. Lapala paa naya.

Wane lama kareyambi dokona anjukumi rakange leyamuli pyuo piyase? leya. Nakamame lao, Wane mupwa doko, leyami. Yesumi nakama lamaiyuo, Kinyi langilyu. Takisi nyingi akali dupwape enda pamuku dupwape Anatunya isingi yulu palenge dokona sukusa pao nakamba dupwa nyuo enakalyaminyi.

Dokona lao Jone yulu rolae pyuo epeya dokopa baa kinyi lalyamo lao nakamba suu pyaa nayami. Suu pyaa nayaminyipape takisi nyingi akali dupwape enda pamuku dupwape kinyi lalyamo lao suu piyami. Suu piyami doko kandapala enakana nakambame mona enenge palyapala kinyi lalyamo lao suu pyaa nayami, leya.

Yesumi kongwalu pii mende laro selapape leya. Akali kamongo mendeme isa girapo ee mende pipala kame piya. Dokona girapo ee kame pipala wara piya. Kalyuo pyarakwalana girapo jinginya ipwange pao seraŋa lao kanana yuwale kyasiya. Kyasapala ketae anda Ionde mende piya. Pipala akali lapo ee doko kando karena lao maipala yuu mendasa wakale peya.

Jingi lyingi gii doko pyaka selena piyamo dokopa akali dokome banya yulu pingi akali lapo lamaiyuo, Nambana ee kando karaminyi akali dusipa karaminyi dokona papala nambana jingi lyuo jinya lapala minyakao ipupwape, leya.
Dokona peyaminyipa akali ee kando kareyaminyi dusipame yulu pingi akali dusipa nyuo yoko lapala mendali pyaroko pyao mendali pyao kumakao mendali kaname pyao piyami.
Dokopa ee range akali dokome yulu pingi akali andapyuwale dee pena leya. Dokopa akali dusipa dee dopako pyao piyami.
Enakana nambana ikinyingiŋi lao seramiŋi lapala banya ikinyingi doko nakama kareyami dokona pena leya.

Dopa leyamopape ee kando kareyami akali dusipame ikinyingi doko kandapala nakama range lao, Wane dake rakangena moyange nyera ingilyamo doko epelyamo. Baa pyao kumakamanale, mwua. Rakange kumaramo moyange baa nyerali dupwa namwa nyerama, leyami.
Lapala baa nyuo pyapala girapo ee neta dorena pyao nembeyami.
Dokopa girapo ee range akali dokome epapala dokopa ee kando kararami akali dusipa apa pira, leya Yesumi.
Dokopa nakamame baa lamaiyuo, Baame akali koo dupwa koo keta palena lao pyao kumakara. Dopa pipala waene ee doko nyuo jingi lyera gii dusipana baa kapa maipapu pirami akali lapo nyuo maira, leyami.

Yesumi nakama lamaiyuo, Nakamame pii pyasi palamo doko yaka lao kanda nangese? Doko akali kana anda pyuo kareyami dupwame kana mende nyuo nembeyami, doko enakana anda donge dokona mupwa ingyuo epo siya. Dopa piyamo doko Kamongome renge kuiyuo piyamosa piya. Dopa piyami dokona namwame lengeme kandapala mona nembo karamano.
Dokona nambame nakama dopa langilyu, leya Yesumi. Anatunya isingi yulu nakama keta pali nana lapala range nyuo wambu rara wakale jingi mondo lao lyuo kararami dupwa maira.
Wambu kana dokona mangala pao serami dupwa pyao inji ranji pira. Piramopa kana dokome wambu mende pisiramo dokona lakao epapala dokopa pyao minjiku minyinyi nembara, leya.
Purisi mupwa dupwape Parisi dupwape banya kongwalu pii dusipa sepala namwasa lalyamo lao soo manji nyiyami.
Manji nyepala nakamame baa puu maiyalana piyami dokopa wambu malu mee baa Anatunya poropeta akali lao suu piyami dokona baa puu maiyalana pakayami.
Yesumi dee kamba kongwalu pii lapala dopa lao lamaiya.
Kiŋi akali banya ikinyingi dokona enda nyera lapala nenge andake namanale leya doko suu pyao yake pandana isingi yulu doko dopale.
Akali dokome banya kendemande akali dupwa lamaiyuo, Enda nyakamiru dokona nenge nala eparamili dupwa epena lala pena leya. Leyamo dokopa nakama pao lamaiyaminyi dokopa, Epa narama daa, leyami.

Dee banya kendemande akali wakale lapo pena lao lamaiyuo, Eparamili dupwa dopa lamaipwape, Nenge narama doko rapa rapa pipu. Nambana bulamakao lapope bulamakao ikyane rondo lasi dupwape pyapamwa doko peparae rapa rapa pisi silyamo. Enda nyakamiru dokona nenge narama ipupwape, letamo lao lamainya, leya.
Dopa leyamopa wambu dupwame minyakaso kaepala pao, mende ee dokona pao mende banya yulu pingi anda pao
menge dupwame banya kendemande akali dupwa minyarapala kilya kandalya kandana pipala pyao kumakayami.
Dokopa kiŋi akali dokome imbwuapala banya yanda pingi akali pena leyamosa nakamame wambu yango longa pingi dupwa pyao kumakao nakamana anda dupwa yango banamau lao piyami.
Dokopa baame banya kendemande akali dupwa lamaiyuo, Enda nyakamiru dokona nenge narama doko rapa rapa pisi silyamo. Sipyamopape wambu eparamili dupwa koo ingyuo karaminyi dokona epa narami.
Dokona kata dupwana papala wambu kando nyeramili dupwa enda nyakamiru dokona nenge narama dokona epena lalapape, leya.
Dokopa kendemande akali dupwame kata dupwana papala wambu kando nyiyaminyili pyuo koo keyangepe dupwa peparae nyuo malu palyiyami. Dokopa nenge narami anda doko wambumi kete piya.
Kete piyamopa kiŋi akali dokome wambu dupwa kandala kolando epapala kandeyamo dokopa enda nyingi gii dokopa komau keyange pingi dopale akali mende baa pee pii nao peteyamo kandeya.
Kandapala baa dopa lamaiya. Yangone enda nyingi gii dokopa komau keyange pingi dopale emba pii napala apa pyuo kolando andakare dakena ipisi? leya. Dokona akali dokome roma napyuo peteya.

Dokopa kiŋi dokome banya yulu pyaka malngi dupwa lamaiyuo, Baa nyuo kingi kimbupi puu pyapapala iminjingi netarena pyambwalapape. Iminjingi dorenako akali dupwa ee lao nenge ginyi ganyi lao kararami, leya.
Dokona lao malu epena letamopape mendasipa yapalyuo nyingi, leya Yesumi.
Dokopa Parisi akali dupwame pao wato lao piso, Apa pipala baa kopetame lenale lao kawanyi mendena palyuo laramase? leyami.

Lapala nakamana disaepole dupwape Erote nyimbunya lao nyiso kareyami akali lapo dupwape Yesu kareyamo dokona pena leyamisa dopa leyami. Mana Lenge, emba rolae pyuo Anatunya yulu dokona lao angi kinyi mana lao karo, dokopa Kamongoŋo lao wambu dopale dapale lao suu pyaa nao pyuo karene doko namwame silyamano.
Dokona apa lao suu pilipi? namwa isingi langipi. Namwa Sisa takisi mailyamano doko namwana Lowa dokona yalelyamase? leyami.

Dokopa Yesumi nakama baa koo keta palena lao lalyaminyi lao soo gisapala dopa leya. Nakama yanengena mamba kiso lao karaminyi dupwa, akipamo nakamame namba apa letepe lao selana nyuo kuinya palyuo makande pyuo letamipi?
Takisi maingi doko suu pyao kana mende namba lasaka pipwape, leya. Dokopa baa kana mende minyuo epo maiyami.
Dokopa Yesumi nakama lamaiyuo, Kana dakena wambu ayemba pukusi petamo pii yasi opetae palamo dolapo apinya? leya.
Nakamame, Sisana, leyami. Dokopa baame nakama lamaiyuo, Sisana bange dupwa Sisa range maiyuo, Anatunya bange dupwa Anatu range maiyuo pipwape, leya.
Nakama pii doko soo mona nembapala baa yaki nyuo peyami.
Yuu gii dokopako Satyusi dupwame wambu kumapala lopo lete epa nange lao karenge dupwa epapala baa mende piso soo dopa leyami.
Mana Lenge, Moseseme lao dopa leya. Akali mende wane manja nao kumara ramo doko banya yangonge dokome banya enda waiya doko kalyapala apo dokona wane manjakamira, leya kande.
Dokona suu pyao yangonge yanda ipingi nyero kareyami. Yangonge mupwa doko enda nyepala kumuya. Baame wane manja nayamo dokona yangonge dokome banya etenge doko kalyakana lao kumuya.
Dopako pyuo yangonge lapo dokope yangonge repo dokope pao yangonge yanda ipingi nyero dokope dusipa dopako pyuo kumuyami.
Yangonge peparae kumapeyaminyipa enakana enda doko kumuya.
Dokona lete lopo epo kararami gii dokopa akali yanda ipingi kararami dokona anjukunya mendena etenge ingyuo pisirase? Nakama peparaeme enda doko nyepa piyami kande, leyami.
Dokopa Yesumi isingi lamaiyuo, Nakamame pii pyasi dokope Anatunya porainya renge dokope soo nyepa napala kopetame lalaminyilyamo.
Lete lopo paraminyi gii dokopa akali mendeme enda nyii nao rakangeme wanenge akali mai nao pyuo kararaminyipa aŋala yake panda dokona karaminyi doko suu pyao kararami.

Deeko, wambu kumuo lete lopo eparama dokona suu pyao Anatumi nakama pii langiyamo pyasi palamo doko nakamame kando yaka laa nangese? Namba Aporakamena Anatu ingyuo karo, namba Aisakena Anatu ingyuo karo, namba Jekopena Anatu ingyuo karo pilyu, leya kande. Baa kumuo palaminyi dupwana Anatu ingyuo kara nange baa lete karaminyi dupwana Anatu ingyuo karamo, leya Yesumi.
Dopa leyamo dokopa wambu malu rukuraka pyuo kareyami dupwame sepala banya mana pii doko soo mona nembeyami.
Dokopa Parisi akali dupwame Yesumi Satyusi akali dupwa kui lanyi pyambwapyalyamo lao sepala epo sukusa sukusa piyami.
Dokopa nakama kareyami dokona Mawa Pii singi mendeme baa apa letape lao selana makande pyuo mende piso siya.
Mana Lenge, Mawa Pii palamo dokona anjuku doko mupwa wakasase? leya.
Leyamopa baa lamaiyuo, Nakamame nakamana Kamongo Anatu mona malngi renge dokomepe imambu dokomepe suu pingi dokomepe baako mona maiyuo karalapa letamo.

Doko mawa pii mendaki ama andake ingyuo palamo. Dokona suu pyao mawa pii mende lapo pyuo palamo doko dopale. Doko, nakama range kando mona retenge doko suu pyao wambu maki palenge dupwa mona reto karalapape, lao palamo.
Mawa Pii wakale wakale dupwa peparaepe Anatunya poropeta akali dupwana pii peparaepe mawa pii lama dolapome minyaro karamo, leya.
Parisi dupwa sukusa sukusa pyuo kareyami dokopa Yesumi nakama pii mende piso soo dopa leya.
Koraisa doko apa pyuonde lao suu pilyamisi? Apinya ikinyingi ingyuo karase? leya. Nakamame baa lamaiyuo, Dapitinya ikinyingi, leyami.
Baame nakama lamaiyuo, Dopa laminyipape akipamo Dapitimi Imambumi pyongo piyamosa baa kando Kamongo, lao leyase? Baa dopa leya kande.
Kamongo dokome nambana Kamongo lamaiyuo, Nambana kingi rolaerename pisa ipu. Embena yanda pimwai ingyuo dupwa nambame nyuo embena kimbu yukuna dokona rambuki nyinyi pyambwakaro. leya.
Dapiti baa kando Kamongoŋo leyapya doko apa pyuo dee banya para pyao nyiyamo dokona ingiyase?
Dokopa nakama mendeme baa isingi lamaiyalana saka nayami dokona yuu gii dokona piso pao pii lapo baa kapa piso selana pakayami.
Yesumi wambu malu mee rukuraka pyuo kareyami dupwape banya disaepole dupwape lamaiyuo dopa leya.
Mawa Pii mana lenge akali dupwape Parisi dupwape Mosesena apo dokona alo pyuo petaminyi.

Dokona nakamame nakama dopa pipwape lao langiraminyili pyuo minyuo pyuo karalapape. Karapalape nakamana yulu pinginyili pyuo kara nalapape. Dokona lao nakamame mana langilyaminyili pyuo range pii nalyaminyi.
Nakamame bange kenda andake pingi lekeleke rao singi dupwa yama pipala akali dupwana lange dokona retenge. Retapalape nakamana kingi pyambuo nyisa nange.

Nakamame yulu pingi dupwa peparae wambu dupwame kandamili lao pyuo karenge. Dokona lao nakamame Baepolena pii pyasi palenge malu nyuu byake dokona nyimbunyale lao embo nakamana komau pinjingi londenale lao pee pyuo karenge.
Wambu nenge andake nao petenge dokopa akali mupwa petenge dokonape sinakoke anda dupwana petenge mupwa dupwanape pisimwali yaka lao rungi rungi pyao karenge.
Ropo pingi kamapi dupwana karo wambu dupwame nakama kando ayaka lao, Rapu Pingi, Rapu Pingi, lao karamili yaka lao suu pyao karenge.
Wambumi nakama kando Mana Lenge lao larami doko kapa ingya nalyamo. Doko nakama peparae yangonge ingyuo karaminyipa nakamana mana lenge angi mendakiko karamo.
Doko suu pyao isa yuu dakena akali mende kando rakane emba mupwaŋa lao laa nalapape. Nakamana Rakane mendaki iki doko yake panda dokona karamo.
Dokonako suu pyao wambu dupwame nakama kando, Kamongo, lena laa nalapape. Nakamana Kamongo mendaki iki Koraisa lenge doko karamo.
Nakamana akali mupwa ramo doko baa nakamana kendemande ingyuo karena.
Mendeme namba range mupwa karo lao suu pyarami dupwa bulu bulu pyapala kuki ingyuo kararami. Mendeme namba range kuki karo lao suu pyarami dupwa anda nyimbuo mupwa ingyuo kararami.

Mawa Pii mana lenge akalipi Parisi akalipi nakama yanengena mamba kiso lao karo yake pandana isingi yulu palenge dokona wambu dupwa sukusa paa nana lao nee pyuo karenge dokona nakama keta randa epara ingilyamo. Nakama range sukusa paa nao wambu lapo sukusa panya laminyi dupwa kaena lao daako letaminyi.

Mawa Pii mana lenge akalipi Parisi akalipi yanengena mamba kiso lao karenge dupwa nakama keta randa epara ingilyamo leto. Nakamame enda waiya dupwana anda dupwa mamando pyuo pyaso nyuope mee panga soo ateŋa londe laope pyuo karenge. Dopa pilyaminyi dokona Anatumi nakama moŋo kamame andake jera.

Mawa Pii mana lenge akalipi Parisi akalipi nakama yanengena mamba kiso lao karenge dupwa nakamame akali mendakipi mende nakamana yongo nyinya lao suu pyao ipwa kotanape yuu dupwanape papyuo koto karenge. Enakana akali doko nakamana yongo nyepelyamo dokopa nakama isare pandana wane ingyuo karaminyi doko suu pyao baa ama isare pandana wane ingyuo karena lao lenge dokona nakama keta randa epara ingilyamo.

Nakama lenge kwaenge dokome wambu kata dupwana lanyuo pelyaminyi dokona nakama randa epara ingilyamo. Nakama dopa lenge kandale. Mendeme tembole anda dokona kingi lao mende pirunya lao kingi ketae nembo lapala enakana laramuli pyuo pii nara ramo doko pii pali nara lenge. Dee mendeme tembole andana kana golo dokona kingi minyuo lao mende pirunya lara ramo dokome baa mangena minyara ingilyamo lao karaminyi.
Nakama kopyali lenge kwaenge dapwa. Anjuku doko mupwase? Kana golo dokope panda tembole andame golo poo pyasi inginyi pyambulyamo dokona tembole anda dokose?

Dokonako palyuo nakamame mende opetaeko kopetame lao, mendeme bange kiso maingi rate dokona kingi minyuo mende pirunya lao kingi ketae nembo lapala enakana laramuli pyuo pii nara ramo doko pii pali nara. Dee mendeme bange maisi rate seramo dokona kingi minyuo lara ramo baa mangena minyara ingilyamo.
Nakama lenge kwaenge dapwa anjuku doko mupwase? Bange dokope panda mena kiso maingi rateme bange poo pyasi inginyi pyambulyamo dokose?
Dokona lao mendeme Anatu bange maiyuo retenge rate doko suu pyao kingi ketae nembara ramo doko ratepe bange silyamo dokope pale pale larasa pira.
Deeko, mendeme tembole anda doko kingi lao kinyi kinyi letoŋo lao, lalu lao lara ramo doko anda dokope anda dokona karenge baape laparaena palyuo larasa pira.
Dee pii mendeko doko, mendeme yake panda doko minyuo kinyi kinyi letoŋo lao lalu lao lara ramo doko Anatunya kiŋi petenge isa dokope angi baa petenge dokope laparaena palyuo larasa pirako.

Mawa Pii mana lenge akalipi Parisi akalipi yanengena mamba kiso lao karenge dupwa nakama randa andake narami ingilyamo. Dokona lao nakamame mokwamepe yambya yokope alamu yoko dee awa yokope dupwa peparaena akalisa silyamo dokona mendaki larapu Anatu maingi. Mailyaminyiko doŋo Mawa Pii palamo dokona pii kenda dusipa wambu yango kando rolae maingipi yulu angi dasipa nakamame kame sepala kaelyaminyi. Kuki doloma pyuo karo yulu angi dasipa opetae piraminde pilyaminyi.

Nakama lenge kwaenge dokome wambu kata lasaka pilyamano lao pilyaminyi. Nakama ipwa nalena dokopa bange kuki ipwana silyamo dupwa nyuo nembelyaminyipape ipwa mena kamele paleta mee nao goe letaminyisa pingi.

Mawa Pii mana lenge akalipi Parisi akalipi yanengena mamba kiso lao karenge dupwa, nakama randa narami ingilyamo. Nakamame kapope pere warakepe netarena wate pyuo karaminyipape kokorena panga soo pyaso nyuo karenge renge dupwa simbulyamo.
Parisi akali lenge kwaenge dupwa nakama kapope pere warakepe netarena elyape seraŋa lapala kokorena wate pipwape.

Mawa Pii mana lenge akalipi Parisi akalipi yanengena mamba kiso lao karenge dupwa nakama randa narami ingilyamo. Malu pingi anda kamarena mamba kakepame kisasi dokome dorename iki au koo pyuo karelyamopape kokorena akali rumbyasi dupwana kuli kwaesi dupwa simbwaro karamo dupwa nakama dopale.
Nakamame dopako pyuo wambu kandaminyipa yanengena rolae pili lao mee pyuo karaminyi. Karaminyipape nakama yanengena mamba kiso lao karengepe koo keta keke soo karengepe dusipa simbwaro karaminyi.

Mawa Pii mana lenge akalipi Parisi akalipi yanengena mamba kiso lao karenge dupwa nakama randa narami ingilyamo. Nakamame Anatunya poropeta akali dupwana malu anda pyuo wasakamyuo yulu rolae pyuo karenge wambu dupwana malu anda ketae dokona kana sulu singi doko mondo koo lao kalya pyuo karenge.

Nakamame dopa pyuo karo dokopa dopa lenge. Namwana rakange kyawa kareyami dupwa pipya kareyamili doko nakamame Anatunya poropeta akali dupwana ranjama kulimbuyami dokopa namwame dopako pyuo kulimbwakami nayamali lenge kandale.
Dokona ingyuo nakama Anatunya poropeta akali dupwa langa pyapa piyami dupwana rara karamano lao range polo lamisa pilyamo.
Dokona nakamana rakange kyawa dupwame pyuo kareyami dokonako palyuo makande minyuo pyuokondali pyuo pipwape.
Nakama kau ikyane ingyuo kaparao karaminyi. Anatumi nakama kando kote lao isare pandana yapalya yapana pinyi nembara doko apa pipala wanjinyi nembaramisi?

Dokona Anatunya poropeta akalipi rolae suu pingi akalipi mawa pii mana lenge akalipi lapo nakama karaminyi dokona mapanyi peelyo. Dokopa nakama dupwana lapo pyao kumakao isa mamandona pyao palyuo, lapo nakamana sinakoke anda dupwana pyarako pyao, lapo anda repe repe pyuo karenge dupwana randa maipapu pyuo kararami.

Dopa pyuo kararami dokopa isa yuu dakena wambu rolae pingi kareyami dupwana ranjama kulimbwapa piyami dupwa peparae nakama dupwa keta sera. Akali Epolo baa nyisu mende peteyamo kara nayamopa pyao kumakaya dokona ranjama dokona kanda soo piso pao kama enakana Berokayana ikinyingi Sakaraya doko Anatu bange kiso malngi rate dokope tembole anda donge dokope dolapo karalyaro kareyambinyipa sukusa dokona nakama dapwame baa pyao kumakayami dokona ranjama dokope kiminjapala nakama keta sera.
Kinyi langilyu, wambu dusipana ranjama peparae wambu ando karaminyi dupwa keta epo sera ingilyamo.

O Jerusaleme, Jerusaleme, Anatunya poropeta akali dupwa pyao kumakao, pii minyakamyuo epenge dupwa kaname pyapa pingi. Kola inya dokome banya ikyane dupwa papaki dokona lungwa lungwa nyuo pyambungi doko suu pyao yuu malu mee embena wane wanakepe sukusa nyipuli lao suu piyunupa emba daa lee kande.
Embena anda doko mee pii karo kwaesi sera.
Dokona lao kinyi langilyu. Nakamba namba dee kanda narami. Namba Anatunya kingi lao eparonopa nakamame lao kandalapa neta ipwamo lao karo dokopa dee kandarami leya.
Yesu tembole anda yaki nyepala katasa panya peyamo dokopa banya disaepole dupwame epapala baa tembole anda dokona pisi karenge dokoŋo kandena leyami.
Dopa leyaminyipa baame nakama lamaiyuo, Nakamame dapwa kandelyamisi? Kinyi langilyu, Pyao lalyinyi nembaraminyipa kana mendena kana yango ketae see nara, leya.

Baa Isa Olipi Kyau dokona peteyamopa disaepole dupwa iki epapala dopa leyami. Emba leene doko anjokorape pira lao rolo langipi leyami. Emba eparene dokope isa wambu dupwana yuu gii doko lumwa piramo doko wambo apa piramo kandaramanopa enakana angi doko pyaka serase? leyami.
Dokopa Yesumi nakama isingi dopa lamaiya. Akali lapome nakama suu longo nyii nana lao pyare pyanyi pyambuo waso karalapape.
Dokona lao wambu malumi nambana kingi lao, Namba Koraisa karo lapala wambu malu suu longo nyerami.

Dokopa yanda pilyaminyi lao angi rolae leyaminyipape lape lape pii leyaminyipape dopa pyuo mende siyami kande dokopa nakama paka nao ambeambe karalapape. Dokona lao rengya dopa pira ingilyamoko. Dopa pyuo pyaka seramo dokopa ene pyai napa nara.

Dokona lao yuu mendena range wambu dupwame yuu mendena range wambu dupwa pyala parami. Kiŋi rara mendeme kiŋi rara mende pyala para. Dokopa yuu wakale wakale dupwana yuusili andake minyaramo wambu dupwa lopo andake seramo kararami.
Doko enda wane ene mata pyalana kanda singi dopale ingyara.

Dokona lao yuu gii enakana dokopa akali dupwame nakama randa andake dokona nyuo minya sepala pyao kumakarami. Dokopa rara wakale wakale dupwame nakamame nambana kingi lao kararaminyi dokona kando awa narami.
Dokopa wambu malu suu longo neta papala karo, mendeme mendali mata kando lao, mendeme mendali awa nao pyuo kararami.
Dokopa akali lapome, Anatu pyongo pyapyamo nolako lao karo lao panga soo karenge dupwame sipurapala wambu malu suu longo nyerami.
Dokopa yulu koo doko konda konda pyuo ama reeko ingyaramo dokona akali andapyuwale mona reto karenge kata dupwa kii nara.
Dopa piramopa wambu nambana yulu minyuo pyuo kararaminyi dupwa yuu gii lumwa piramo dokopa kaeya nao mee pyuo karalu kararaminyi dusipa Anatumi lete wai pyao nyera.

Dokona suu pyao Anatunya isingi yulu dokona lao waili pii keyange, doko isa yuu muu dupwana boo pyao, rara wakale wakale wambu dupwa peparae sinya lao, rolo lamaiyuo pao kapa kapa pirami dokopa gii doko lumwa pira.

Anatunya poropeta akali Daniele lenge dokome, Anda poo pyasi dokona bange ama koo Anatunya lenge kambu dokona kokwa soo retarami leya doko leyamuli pyuo piya kande dokopa yuu Jutia kararaminyi wambu dupwa yuu kyau dupwana bolombaio lao ralo pupwape. (Pii dake kongwalu letamo dokona poraiyuo selapa.)
Akali mende anda yangi dokona pisira ramo doko banya bange andakare singi dupwa minyuo parowale lao andakare nyela paa nao mee raio para.
Akali mende ee dokona karara ramo doko dee epo banya komau nyii napala mee ralo pupingele.
Yuu gii dusipana enda wane rombanda palenge dupwape wane anju kareta singi enda dupwape apa pipala parami?
Apunda pilyamopa kupwa pingi gii dokopape koro petenge dokopape yulu dusipa pyaka sepa nana lao ateŋa lalapape.

Yuu gii dusipana randa andake wakasa mende pyaka sera. Doko isa yuu kanda soo busiyamopa randa nao kareyami dokona piso epo epapu randako nao karaminyi, rengya kamame randako nao kararaminyipa randa andake wakasa seramo dokome doloma pipya manda minya naralyamo.
Anatumi yuu gii nyuo muu pinyi nemba nayali doko wambu peparae koo keta palyuo kumuo oteyamuli. Doko kaepala banya wambu lapo rombo palyiyamo dupwana reke lao repele pyakanya lao muu pinyi nembara.
Yuu gii dusipana wambu mendeme nakama langyuo, Koraisa baa isa dae kata kande, panda, Baa isa dalyesa karamo leyami kande dokopa kinyi laiyaminyi lao suu pyaa nalapape.

Dokona lao akali lapome kyambo lao, Namba Koraisa karoŋo, lao sipurapala wambu kando yamaranguramili yulu andake dopale lapo lasaka pyuo pyuo kararami. Akali dupwame mee wambu dupwa suu longo nyuo karo dokopa Anatunya rombo palyisi wambu dupwa opetae suu longo nyelana lao pyuo kararami.
Ene dopa pipa naramopa dopa piraŋa lao wambo langilyu kande.
Dokona wambu dupwame nakama langyuo, Baa yuu muiyane dokona karamo larami ramo nakama dokona paa nalapape. Dee, Baa andakare lukuna karamo larami ramo doko kinyi lalyaminyi lao suu pyaa nalapape.
Dokona lao neta pyakaenge dorena piso yuu pele renge kuiyuo pipala, yuu dupwa yanga paupau lao pao neta yalyingi dorena kandenge doko suu pyao Ikinyingi Akali doko epara lyakande.
Yanenge kaoma seramo dokonako yaka ulisapu dupwa epo elyambu pyuo pisirami ingingi.
Randa andake nao kararami gii doko otaramopa aopa neta doko raa napala iminjowape, kana doko raa nao, bui dupwa yake dokona piso kondo isa epo karo yake bange poral dupwa romo romo pyuo pyuo karara.

Dokopa Ikinyingi Akali epelyamo lao yake dokona lyakal pyuo panara. Panaramopa yuu muu dupwana rara wakale wakale dupwa peparaeme ee lao kondome kumuo kararami. Dopa piraminyipa Ikinyingi Akali doko yake panda kopa rakapana dokona ama yanga paupau lapala poral wakasa ingyuo eparamo kandarami.
Dokopa bikuli andake laramopa banya aŋala dupwame porambaiye renge kuiyuo epenge yuu pinjingi kisima dusipana pao banya wambu yapasi dupwa nyela pena lara.
Isa piki doko kandapala renge mende mana nyelapape. Isa wangya piso andenge dokona byalu lapala yoko karo penge doko kandapala ee kana musi doko pyaka selana pyamolamo lao kandenge.
Doko suu pyao yulu doo lalono kandapi dusipa pyaka seramo kandeyami kande dokopa baa repeta epo pyamolyamo, kinyi kakota lumbungi repeta karalamolyamo, lao soo gisarami.
Kinyi langilyu, doo lalono kandapi dusipa ene pyaka sepa naramopa isa wambu epapu ando karaminyi dupwa wambo ota narami.
Yake yuupa otara ingyapyamopa nambana pii dupwa ota nara ingilyamo.
Dopa pira doŋo baa eparamo yuu gii dokope keloke gii dokope wambu peparae soo gisa nalyaminyi. Aŋala yake panda karaminyi dupwape Ikinyingi opetaeme soo gisa nalyaminyiko. Rakangeme iki soo karamo.
Akali Noa baa kareyamo yuu gii dokopa wambu kamenge karo yulu mee pyuo kareyami doko suu pyao Ikinyingi Akali eparamo dokopa dopako pirami.
Ipwa andake yuu muu dupwa ene yambe pyaa nayamopa wambu dupwame kamenge karo, nenge ipwape nao, enda yapo nyuo pyuoko kareyaminyipa, Noa baa sipu andake dokona kolando peya.
Mende oo piramo doko see napala langa pyuo kareyaminyipa ipwa dokome epo nakama neya. Dokoko suu pyao Ikinyingi Akali eparamo gii dokopa dopako pira.
Dokopa akali lama ee dokona kararambinyipa mende nyera, mende kaeyara.
Enda lama role pyao isa jingi pyao injo pisirambinyipa mende nyera mende kaeyara.
Dokona suu pyao nakama lenge rao karalapape. Nakamana Kamongo doko yuu gii anjokorape epara lao see nalyaminyi.

See naminyipape pii dake soo gisalapape. Anda range akali dokome waa nyingi akali doko kukwa eparape panda korakama epara lao soo gisapyali doko lenge rao isaro pisipala anda kambu lalyinyi nembapala epa nana lapyali.
Doko suu pyao Ikinyingi Akali doko keloke gii anjukunya epara lao see nalyaminyi dokona epelyape lao nakama rapa rapa pyuo isaro karalapape.

Kendemande akali apiyakalende mupwa ingyuo parase? Doko akali mende mona palenge dokome yulu kaeya nao pyuo kararamopa banya kamongo dokome baa yapo nyepala doloma rapu pyuo nenge mokwa soo maipa pyuo karena lara doko.
Kamongo dee kapu kyuo epo kendemande akali yulu rolae pyuo kararamo kandaramo dokopa kendemande akali doko baa rae maiyuo para.
Kinyi langilyu, kamongo baame banya bange peparae rapu pyuo karena lao rombo paiyara.
Dopa piramopape yulu pingi akali baa kopy ali ingyapala, Nambana kamongo waiya lao epa nalyamo lao suu pyara.
Suu pyapala yulu pingi wambu yango dupwa pyaroko pyao baamoo wambu yango role pyao nenge nao waene ipwange malu nao pipala kyawa sisingi bolombalo laramo pisirami.
Dopa pyuo piso kamongo doko waiya lao epa nara lao suu pyao kamenge pisiramo yuu gii dokopa banya kamongo epara.
Epapala baa pyakepanyi nembo kaepala wambu yanengena mamba kiso lao kararami dupwa koo keta kararami dokonako pyambwara. Koo keta kararami dokona akali doko ee lao nenge ginyi ganyi lao karara.
Yuu gii doko wanake mapwae akalisame nakamana lambe nyuo minya akali enda nyeramo doko lanyala peyaminyi doko makande minyuo yake pandana isingi yulu dopale ingyuo para.
Doko enda mapwae peyami dusipana kingi paki mona pali nange, dee mona palenge kingi pakiko.
Enda mapwae mona pali nange dusipame lambe iki minyapala keresene minya nayami.
Dee enda mona palenge dusipame lambe keresene ipwange paleta batolonape minyuo peyami.
Enda nyelana pingi akali doko yuu andarele epo peyamopa waiya lao epa nayasa enda dupwa lenge luwapala luu paleyami.
Kukwa andasukulya dokopa pii andakende lapala, Kandaiapa. Enda nyelana pingi akali doko angi epelyamo. Baa epelyamo dokona kando nyela ipupwa, leya.
Dokopa enda mapwae dupwa peparae sipurapala nakamana lambe dupwa rapa rapa piyami.
Dokopa mona pali nange dusipame mona palenge dusipa lamaiyuo, Namwana lambe dusipa kunjalana pilyamo dokona nakamana ipwange lama jelapape, leyami.

Dopa leyaminyipape mona palenge dusipame isingi lao, Nakamape namwape peparae ipwange mendakinya nyerama ramo doko kapa ingyara lyasilisi? Dokona nakamame kaepala sito anda dokona papala lapo range ropo pyala pupwape, leyami.

Dokopa nakama ropo pyala ene katasa peyaminyipa enda nyelana pingi akali doko epeya. Dokopa wanake rapa rapa pyuo otapala peteyaminyi dupwa baamoo pipya role pyao enda nyingi dokopa nenge nenge anda dokona andakare peyami. Peyaminyipa kambu upi leyami.
Enakana enda mapwae menge dusipa epapala, Kamongo, Kamongo, kambu lumbwakape, leyami.
Dopa leyaminyipa baame isingi lao, Kinyi langilyu, nambame nakama apimoo lao kando gisa nange, leya.
Doko suu pyao anjokorape eparape lao yuu giipi keloke giipi see nalyaminyi dokona kando isaro karalapape, leya Yesumi.
Dokona suu pyao akali mende kata nanesa panya lao kareyamo dokome banya yulu pyakamalngi akali dusipa epena lapala banya bange dupwa retakao karena leya.
Akali mendepe mendepe yulu palengenyili pyuo mende kana kina kingi paki maiyuo mende kina lama maiyuo mende kina mendaki maiyuo piya. Maipala baa peya.
Dokopa akali kana kina kingi paki nyiya dokome aopa minyuo pao bange lapo ropo pyao nyepapu dee kana nyuo maipapu pyuo karo enakana kina kingi paki apeto konda pyuo nyiya.
Akali kina lama nyiya dokome dopako pyuo kina lama apeto konda pyuo nyiya.
Dopa piyambinyipa akali kina mendaki nyiya dokome papala yuu apu rao banya kamongona mone doko yalu pyuo koko palyiya.
Yuu andarele epo papeyamopa yulu pingi akali dusipana kamongo dokome epapala kana dokona lao roleyami.

Dokopa akali kina kingi paki nyiya doko kina kingi paki apetasi laeyo minyuo, epapala dopa leya. Kamongo, embame kina kingi paki namba minyando jii kande doko kina kingi paki kame apeto nyepala dae minyakao epelyo, leya.

Dokopa banya kamongo dokome baa lamaiyuo, Emba yulu pingi akali keyange. Nambana pii yaki nyii nao mee pyuo karenge doko, emba mondo lao pyuo karapilyamo. Embame yulu kuki yaki nyii nao mee rolae pyuo karapi dokona embame yulu andake renge palyuo rapu pyuo karape laro. Andakare eparenepa nambapa role pyao rae maiyuo karamanale leya.
Dokopa akaii kina lama reto kareya dokome epapala, Kamongo, embame kina lama jii kande doko kina lama kamame nyepala dae minyakao, epelyo, leya.

Banya kamongo dokome baa lamaiyuo, Emba yulu pingi akali keyange. Nambana pii yaki nyii naiu nao napala mee pyuo karenge doko, emba mondo lao pyuo karapilyamo. Embame yulu kuki yaki nyii nao mee rolae pyuo karapi dokona embame yulu andake renge palyuo rapu pyuo karape laro. Andakare eparenepa nambapa role pyao rae maiyuo karamanale leya.
Akali kina mendaki nyiyamo doko opetae epapala, Kamongo, emba akali pundumwa pyuo karapala waingi wara pii nange dokona mee lyuo karo imbu nemba napala embame mee lukusi nyuo karenge doko silyu.
Dokona pakapala embena kina doko yuunya apu rapala koko palyiyu. Kana dokoko dae minyuoko epelyo, leya.

Dopa leyamopape banya kamongo dokome baa isingi lamaiyuo dopa leya. Emba kendemande koo pyuo makalana wangu lakao karenge dake, namba waingi wara pii nange dokona mee lyuo karo imbu nemba napala mee lukusi nyuo karenge doko silinyi.
Dokome akipamo nambana mone doko byange dokona retaka nana pii. Dopa piili doko namba epapala dokopa nambana range dokope kana matana piso eparamo seramo dokope namba nyipuli, lamaiya.
Lamaipala, kina minyaro kareyamo doko nyepala kina akalisa minyaro kareyamo akali doko nyuo mainya ieya.
Dokona lao wambu bange minyaro karaminyi dupwa peparae konda pyuo maironopa kaiyakaro sera. Wambu mendeme angingyuo minya naramopape koo lama minyara doko range nyeroko.
Dokonako suu pyao kendemande akali kopyali doko iminjingi netarena ralinyi nembalapa. Iminjingi dokona akali dupwa ee lao nenge ginyi ganyi lao kararami, leya.
lkinyingi Akali baa aŋala dupwa peparae pale pale yanga paupau lao epapala dokopa baa banya kiŋinya petenge yanga paupau lenge dokona pisira.

Banya lenge kambu dokona wambu rara wakale wakale dupwa peparae epo sukusa sukusa pirami. Dokopa mena rapu pingi akali dokome sipisipi dupwape meme dupwape wakale yapalyuo liti pingi doko suu pyao wambu dupwa yapalyuo liti pira.
Dokopa baame sipisipi dupwa banya kingi rolaerena karena lara, meme dupwa banya kingi kyairena karena lara.

Dokopa Kiŋi dokome banya kingi rolaerena kararami dupwa kando dopa lara. Rakangeme nyiso elyape keta pisiyamo dupwa baa yuu kanda soo wasiyamo dokopa isingi panda keyange mende wasakayamo dokona karala ipupwa lara.
Namba lopo piyamopa nakamame nenge jiyami kande, namba ipwa nano piyamopa nakamame ipwa jiyami kande, namba upunili epeyonopa nakamame yako lao nyiyami kande
Namba papara epeyonopa nakamame komau wapwakayami kande, namba anga piyamopa nakamame namba kandala epeyami kande, namba karapusi anda paleyonopa nakama yako lala epeyami kande lara.

Dopa laramo dokopa yulu rolae pingi wambu dupwame baa isingi lamaiyuo dopa larami. Kamongo, anjokorape emba lopo kareene kandapala namwa nenge jiyamase panda ipwa nano kareene kandapala namwa ipwa kamuo jiyamase?
Dee emba anjokorape upunili epeene kandapala namwa yako lao nyiyamase panda papara epeenepa namwa emba komau wapwakayamase?
Anjokorape anga piyamo siinyipape panda karapusi anda dokona paleenepape kandala epeyamase? larami.
Dokopa Kiŋi dokome nakama isingi dopa lamaira. Kinyi langilyu, nambana yangonge kuki karaminyi dapwana kuki wakasa mende kando pyakamiyami kande doko nambasa kando piyamisa piya, lara.

Lapala banya kingi kyairena kararami dupwa lamaiyuo dopa lara. Nakama koo keta palirami dupwa, namba yaki nyepala pao isare rao karalu karene dokona Satanemoo banya aŋala koo dupwa pipya kararami dokona pupwa.
Dokona lao namba lopo piyamo kareyonopa nakamame nenge jii nayami kande namba ipwa nano piyamo kareyonopa ipwa kamuo jii nayami kande.

Namba upuuili epeyonopa nakamame yako lao nyii nayami kande, namba papara kareyonopa nakamame komau jii nayami kande, namba anga piyamo siyunupape panda karapusi anda paleyonopape kandala epa nayami kande, lara.

Dopa laramo dokopa nakamame opetae dopa lao isingi larami. Kamongo, emba anjokorape lopo kareenepape panda ipwa nano kareenepape panda upuuili epeenepape panda papara epeenepape panda anga piyamo siinyipape panda karapusi anda dokona paleenepape namwame kandapala epo isaro pii nayamase? larami.
Dokopa baame nakama isingi lamaiyuo dopa lara. Nakama kinyi langilyu, wambu kuki karaminyi dapwana kuki koonde kando pyakami nayami doko nambasa kando piyamisa piya, lara.
Dokona nakama yaki nyepala randa nao karalu karala paraminyipape rolae pingi wambu dupwa kyakana renge palu palenge doko nyerami leya Yesumi.
Yesumi pii dupwa lao otapala banya disaepole dusipa kando dopa lamaiya.
Yuu gii lama epo paparamopa Pasopa nenge nenge doko pyaka sera. Dokopa lkinyingi Akali doko isa mamandona pyao yukunya lao nyuo minya serami doko nakama silyaminyi, leya.
Dokopa purisi akali mupwa dupwape wambunya kamongo dupwape purisi akali mupwa wakasa Kayapasa lenge dokona anda andake dokona epo sukusa sukusa piyami.
Pipala, Yesu apa pipala yalu pyuo puu maipala pyarama, lao wato leyami.
Doko mee wambu dupwa kilyipu kilyipu karasarami lapala Pasopa nenge ene nao kararama dokopa kaeyamanale, leyami.
Yesu yuu Betani Saimone rete rapa nenge akali dokona anda dokona peteyamo dokopa

enda mende mamba luli lenge pee mende minyuo baa peteyamo dokona epeya. Mamba doko kana malu penge. Doko minyuo epapala Yesu taepo repeta peteyamopa enda dokome mamba doko banya kyawa dokona kulimbwakamiya.
Dopa piyamo dokopa disaepole dupwa kandapala imbwuayami. Imbwuapala, Akipamo doko kokwa soo kulimbwanyi nembelyamo? leyami.
Dopa pii napyali mamba dokome maipala kana malu ropo pyao nyepala pendewa wambu mokwa soo maimwali, leyami.
Dopa leyaminyipa dopa lalyaminyi lao sepala Yesumi nakama lamaiyuo, Akipamo enda doko randa maiyuo karammyi? Baame yulu keyange namba pyakalamo.
Dokona lao pendewa wambu dupwa nakama pipya role pyao karalu kararaminyipa namba nakama pipya role pyao karalu kara narama.
Nambana yanenge dokona mamba doko kulimbwakalamo doko namba malu pirami dokona suu pyapala rapa rapa pipyasa pipya.
Kinyi langilyu, waili pii keyange doko yuu muu dupwana boo pyao lao kararaminyili pyuo enda dokome pyamo dokona dopa piya lao suu pyao lao kararami, leya.
Akali akalisa ipisu lama kareyami dokona mende Jutasa Isakeriote lenge dokome purisi akali mupwa dupwa kareyami dokona papala dopa leya.
Nambame Yesu nakama keta minya sakaro ramo doko aki bange mende jerami, leya. Dokopa kana kulingi akalisa rema baa maiyami.
Maiyaminyi yuu gii dokonako piso Yesu mata kando lalana apa pyuo laowane lao kando kareya.
Borete isi reta nange nenge yuu gii mupwa dokopa disaepole dupwa Yesu kareyamo doko epo, Emba Pasopa nenge narene doko namwa anja rapa rapa pyakala pamisi lao suu pilipi? leyami.

Dokopa baame lao, Anda malu karenge dokona papala akali mende kararaŋa doko kando dopa lao lamaiyalapape. Mana Lengeme lao, Nambana yuu gii doko repeta pyaka silyamo. Embena anda dokona nambana disaepole dupwa pipya role pyao Pasopa nenge narama, lapyasa langyala epelyamano lao lamaiyalapape, leya.
Dokopa disaepole dusipa Yesu pinya lao leyamuli pyuo dokona palyuo Pasopa nenge rapa rapa piyami.
Yuu kwualepalepa dokopa baamoo akali akalisa ipisu lama kareyami dupwa pipya taepo repeta peteyami.
Nenge nao peteyaminyi dokopa baa dopa leya. Kinyi langilyu, nakama petaminyi dokona mendeme namba mata kando lara, leya.
Dokopa nakama mona rando piso baa lamaiyuo mendaki lao, Emba nambasa lalyane lao suu pyaa napusande lalyane, leyami.
Baame isingi lao, Pee warake ipwange lapo peteta sipyamopa dokona namba role pyao borete poeyo nao pisimbwano dokome namba mata kando lara.

Pii pyasi palamo doko, Ikinyingi Akali baa paraŋa lao leyamuli pyuo para ingilyamo. Para ingyapyamopape akali mendeme Ikinyingi Akali mata kando lao nyuo maira doko baa randa andake nara. Dokona lao baa randa koo nyisaraŋa endangimi manja narande piya, leya.
Dopa leyamo dokopa Jutasa baa angi mata kando lara dokome lao, Mana Lenge, dopa piramo doko nambape? leya. Dokopa baame baa lamaiyuo, Emba leene doko leya.
Nakama ene nenge nao peteyaminyi dokopa Yesumi borete nyepala ateŋa lapala kau lao disaepole dupwa mokwa soo maiyuo, Nyuo nalapape. Dake nambana yongo doko leya.
Lapala pee lomasi mende nyepala ateŋa lao ange lapala nakama maiyuo dopa leya, Nakama peparae nalapa.
Dake nambana ranjama wambu peparaena lao kulimbuo isa para. Nambana ranjama dokome Anatunya lalu lao lenge pii enenge doko kapawai wara pira leya.
Dopa langilyu, waene ipwange doko dee naa naro. Nambana Rakangena isingi yulu paliramopa nambamoo nakama pipya waene enenge lapo role pyao narama dokopa dee naroko leya.
Enakana kenane pyao otapala neta pao yuu Olipi Kyau dokona peyami.

Dokopa Yesumi nakama lamaiyuo, Kukwa dakepa namba keta mende piramo renge dokona nakama peparaeme namba yaki nyerami. Dokona lao pii dopa lao pyasi palamo. Anatumi sipisipinya rapu pingi akali pyarono dokopa sipisipi dupwa bolombalo larami, lao palamo.
Bolombalo laraminyipape namba minyalyuo nyeramopa nakama yuu Galili eparami mare dokona namba wambo paro leya.
Dokopa Pitame Yesu lamaiyuo, Nakama peparaeme emba yaki nyepala suu pyaa nao parami ramo doko nambame dopa pii naro, leya.
Yesumi baa lamaiyuo, Kinyi langilyu, kukwa dakepako kola kali ene pii lapa naramopa embame namba repo pyuo mata joo lare, leya.
Pitame baa lamaiyuo, Namba embapa kumaramba ingyaramopape nambame emba mata joo laa naro leya. Dokopa disaepole dupwa peparae dopako lao pao suu leyami.
Dokopa Yesu nakama role pyao yuu Gesemani dokona papala baame banya disaepole dupwa lamaiyuo, Namba dulusale ateŋa lala pelyoŋo nakama dakena pisipwape, leya.
Lapala Pitamoo Sepetena ikinyingi dolapo pipya lanyuo papala baa monarename pulunongo piyamo randame kumuo kareya.
Dokopa baame nakama lamaiyuo, Namba monarename randame kumulyu. Nambamoo lenge rao karamanale, leya.

Dopa lapala mee mende papala pangu sepala ateŋa lao dopa leya. Nambana Rakane, kapa ingyara ramo pee lomasi dake namba kaepala pena lapili yaka. Dopa lapili lao suu pyapunupape nambame laro doko kapa daa, emba lare doko kapa, leya.
Lapala disaepole dusipa peteyami dokona epapala luu paleyaminyi kandeya. Kandapala baame Pita lamaiyuo, Keloke gii mendaki iki nambamoo kapa lenge rao kapa pisa nalyamisi?
Nakama makande pii nana lao lenge rao ateŋa lao pisipwape. lmambu dokome kapa pinya lao suu pyapyamopape yanenge dokome yame yame lapyamo petaminyi, leya.
Lapala dee yuu lapo pyuo papala ateŋa lao dopa leya. Rakane, pee lomasi dake naa naronopape namba kaepala paa nara ramo doko emba suu pilinyili pyuo namba keta palena, leya.
Lapala dee kamba epeya. Dokopa nakama lenge kenda kenda piyasa luu palyuo siyaminyi kandeya.
Kandapala nakama yaki nyepala dee repo pyuo papala wamba leyamo dopako lao ateŋa leya.
