Apa pyuo Anatunya Elyambu Pingi dupwape Satanena wambu dupwape role pyao kararamisi? Namwa Anatu lete karengena tembole anda dopale karamano suu pyalapape. Anatu baa range dopa pyuo leya. Namba nakama pipya yalya kando role pyao kararo. Namba nakamana Anatu ingyaronopa nakama nambana wambu ingyarami.
Dokona lao Kamongo dopa letamo. Nakamame wambu menge dupwa rekya lao kaepala liti pyuo karalapape. Wambu koo pingi dupwa yalya kando pisa narami ramo dokopa nakama yako laro.
Namba nakamana rakange ingyaronopa nakama nambana wane wanake ingyarami lao Kamongo andake wakasa doko letamo.

Yangonemoo Anatumi kinyi lalu lao leyamo renge keyange dupwa peparae namwa keta palamo. Dokona yulu mendeme namwana yongope imambupi karo pisinyi pyambungi doko rekya lao liti pimana. Yulu poo pyasi iki moko minyuo pyuo karo Anatu pako karo baa yeelyo poralyuo suu pyao karamanale.
Namwa mata joo kara nalapape. Namwa mendali kando koo pii nao kokwa see nao minyoko pii nao pyuo karenge.
Nakama koo piyami lao lapusa pii nalyamo. Wambo langiyunuli pyuo dee kamba langilyu. Namwame nakama mona retenge dokome lete kararamanopape kumaramanopape nakama pipya role pyao kararama.
Nakama mondo lao pyuo karaminyi doko sepala rae maiyuo mona anda pyakalyuo pyao karo. Randa peparae nyimwanopape paka nao raeme kumuo karo.
Kinyi yuu Masetonia pao karapala dokopa koo soo kara nayama. Randa dupwa yuu muu dupwana soo kapa piya. Wambu menge dupwa kando lalya lao paka renge neta epo piya.
Paka renge neta epeyamopape Anatumi wambu mona nembenge dupwa mona minyarambu pingi doko baame Taltesa jepala namba mona poralnyi pyambuya.

Baa epeyamo dokome iki namwa poralnyi pyambwa naya. Nakamame banya mona poralnyi pyambuyaminyi doko langiyamo sepala namwa rae maiyama. Nakama namba Pole kandamwali yaka letaminyi lao langiya. Langiyamopa nakama kondome kumapala nambana reke lao lakao karaminyi langiya. Dokona dakepa namba rae andake mailyu.
Pepa pyao jiyu dokome nakama mona kendanyi pyambuyamopape namba mende suu pyaa nayo. Angi kandeyoli dokopa kondayoliŋi dakepa konda nalyo.

Nakama mona kendanyi pyambuyu dokona lao rae mailyu laa nalyo. Nakama mona kendayami renge dokome suu pingi alowa piyami dokona lao dakepa namba rae mailyu. Nakamana mona kendo kareyami dokome Anatumi nakamana suu pingi alowa piya. Dokona lao namwa nakama randa julu joo jii nayama kande.
Namwa mona kendo kararama dokopa Anatu nyisaramopa mona kapu kyepala lete penge kata dokona rae maiyuo parama. Dopa piramanopape wambunya mona kendange renge dokome kumungi renge mmyuo epenge.

Anatumi nakamana mona kendayami dokona nyepala apa piya lao kandalapape. Dakepa nakama mona angi palyuokondali pilyamo. Koo pii nalyamano lao poralyuo simili yaka lao letaminyi. Nakama koo pilyaminyi larami ramo doko imbwuarami. Imbwuapala koo pilyaminyi laka nanale. Dake mupwa wakasa lao poralyuo suu pyapala namba kando mona andake retelyaminyi. Wambu menge dupwa koo pirami ramo dokopa walya lao pyalana letaminyi. Yulu dake piminyi dokome nakama kopetame pii nayami lao pano nolakaya.

Pepa jiyunu doko akali koo piyamo dokona reke lao pyaa nayo. Dee akali baa keta koo pyuo pisiyamo dokona lao pyaa nayoko. Nakama Anatunya lenge kambu dokona karo apa pyuo namwa mona retelyaminyi lao lasaka pelana pepa piyu.
Renge dokona namwa poralnyi pyambulyamo. Renge mende palamo doko nakama peparaeme Taltesa baa rae mamyi pyambuyaminyisa baa rae maiyuo karamo doko kandapala rae mailyamano.

Namba wambo nakama yulu keyange pingi lao Taitesa lamaiyu. Nakama enakana namba elyanyi pyambwa nayami. Yuu peparae pii rolae angi lao langyuo kareyama doko suu pyao enakana nakama yulu keyange piyami Taltesa kandeya dokome namwa pii kinyi ingyuo peya.
Baa epeyamo dokopa nakama banya pii warombo sepala lakanda minya minya pyuo yako lao sukusa nyiyami doko suu pyaro karamo. Dopa pyuo piyamisa baa nakama angingyuo mona jilyamo.
Namba nakama arapu dokona renge renge soo karapunu dokona namba rae andake maiyuo karo.
Yangonemoo Anatu mona keyange palyuo ipyuo Masetonia Elyambu Pingi wambu nyisiyamopa yulu andake piyami doko selapale lao langirowale.
Nakama randa koo nao kareyaminyipape rae maiyuo kareyami. Pendewa ingyuo karapalape nakama ipyuo wambu yango nyisamwali lao suu piyami dokome kana andake jiyami.
Rangeme sipurapala kana siyamo dupwa pyambwapala enakana dee kamameko koto nyepala konda pyuo reteyami doko kinyi langilyu.
Nakama kana doko retapala nakama suu piyaminyili pyuo wambu Jutia palenge dupwa nyiso maiyakalapape lao namwa poralyuo piso siyami.
Nakama dopa pyuo yulu andake pirami lao suu pyaa nayama. Nakama wambo mona Kamongo doko maiyuo oteyami. Enakana Anatunya suu pingi doko moko minyapala nakamame namwa mona joo oteyamiko.

Taltesa dopako pyuo nakama keta epapala yulu kanda soo piyamo doko pyulu pyuo pinya lao poralyuo lamaiyama. Dopa piramo dokopa nakama Anatu mona reto yulu andake pilyaminyi doko baame nyisaramopa pyuo otalu oto otarami.

Nakama lmambunya kamongapala nakamana Anatu kapa ingingi lao poralyuo suu pingi. Dokome Anatunya pii kapa polo letaminyi. Nakamame renge dupwa peparae soo giso otenge. Nakama namwa rae maiyuo nyisalana namwa mona andake retelyaminyi. Dokona lao Anatu mona retenge yulu doko mumu laa nao rae maiyuo pipape letamano.

Nambame nakama lowa waso joo laa nalyo. Laa napunupape wambu menge wakale lapome pendewa wambu rae maiyuo nyisalana letaminyi dokona nakama pano langyapala nakamana mona retenge renge doko angipi mee lao koto kandalana pyapi pyuo silyu.

Kamongo Yesu Koraisa baa mona keyange palyuo ipingi doko nakama silyaminyi. Baa kamongo ingyuo kareyamopape nakamana reke lao baa pendewa ingyuo peya. Dopa pyuo baa pendewa ingyuo peyamo dokome nakama kamonganyi pyambuya.
Namba dake lao suu pilyu. Ee kana wambo kanda soo piyaminyi yulu doko dakepa pyuo otalapape. Nakama wambo kanda soo pii nalana suu piyaminde daa. Nakama rae maiyuo pimwallinyi iki suu piyami.
Yulu doko pyuo otalapape leto. Nakama rae maiyuo pinya suu pyao rapa rapa piyaminyi doko suu pyao rae maiyuoko pyuo otalapape. Nakama range aelyamo dupwame nyuo pipape.
Nakama rae maiyuo mailana suu pyarami ramo dokopa bange seramuli pyuo mairaminyi doko Anatu kapa lao suu pyara. Bange daa ramo doko mende laa nara.

Nambame nakama iki randa nyuo karaminyipa menge dupwa mee manda rao karenale laa nalyo. Laa napunupa epapu dakepa nakama bange malu reto karaminyi dokona wambu pendewa dupwa nyisarami ramo doko kapa rolae ingyuo pelyamo. Enakana nakamana bange see naramo dokopa doloma bange seramo kararaminyi dokome nakama nyisarami. Dopa piramo dokopa nakamba laparaena mendare ingyuo para.
Baepoleme lao dokopa, Akalimi malu mee yapo nyiyamo doko kamame andakya naya. Akalimi kuki lama yapo nyiyamo doko kamame kukya naya letamo.
Namwame nakama rae maiyuo nyisalana suu pilyamano doko suu pyao Anatumi Taltesa opetae nakama rae maiyuo nyisinya lao kareya. Dokona lao Anatu kando sangyu letamano.
Taltesa nakama nyisarepe mee lao piso siyamanopa baa mende laa nao warombo soo piru leya. Mee piimi ŋee leyande daa. Baa nakama nyisapuli yaka lao suu piyamuli pyuo nakama keta epeya.
Akali yango mende Anatunya waili pii keyange polo letamo doko Elyambu Pingi peparaeme banya pii epe singi doko baa opetae Taltesa role pyao pena letamano.

Akaii doko, Elyambu Pingi wambu dupwame baa rombo palyapala namwa Anatu mona retenge yulu dokona pyuo kamongona kingi lakandalana baa role pyao papyuo kararama leyami. Yulu mendena baa namwamoo pipya nyisamwaii lao suu pilyamano.
Namwa keta kana malu pyamaiyiyaminyi doko ukiaki minyaramanopa wambu dupwa mumu lasaraminyi lapala waso karamano.
Kamongo Anatunya lenge kambu dokonape wambu dupwana lenge kambu dokonape yulu rolae pimwali lao suu pilyamano.

Dokona namwana yangonge akali mende opetae role pyao pena lao peelyamano. Namwa yuu malu mee banya yulu apiyakale lao makande piyamano dokopa baa rae maiyuo waa waa karo nyisalana piya. Epapu dakepa nakama mondo lao karaminyi doko sepala rae mailyamo dokona nakama lama opetae mona karo nyisapuli lao suu pyao karamo.

Dee Taltesa baa nambana yulu role pyao pingi dokome nakama pyuo nyisilyambano. Dee akali menge role pyao paraminyi dupwa nakama Elyambu Pinginya rombo palyisi akali ingyuo dupwa Koraisana kingi ketae pyambuo lakando pelyaminyi.
Nakama mona retelyaminyi dokona lasaka pyuo pipape. Dokopa nakamana yulu keyange doko namwame lakandaramano kandapala namwame kapa letaminyi lao kandarami.
Nakama lapome Anatunya wambu Jutia palenge dupwa nyiso kaelyaminyi dokona aki letoŋo lao dee pepa pyao jerose?

Nakama waa waa karo nyisalana karaminyi doko silyu. Nyisalana karaminyi doko sepala nakamana lao yuu Masetonia wambu rae maiyuo mona anda pyakalyuo pyao lamaiyuo kareyo. Ee kana wambo dokona oiso pao epapu dakepa nakama Korina Kurisene yuu Girisi karaminyi dupwame nyisalana karaminyi, dokona lao lamaiyakayo. Nakamame mona nyepala nyisalana piyaminyi dokome wambu malunya monarena piya.

Nambame nakamana lao rae maiyuo mona anda pyakalyuo pyao leyono doko mee ingyuo paa nanale lao dakepa yangonge dapwa pena leto. Doko nakama epeyaminyi kande dokopa wamba langjyunu dokona kata palyuo nyisarami lao silyu.
Dokona Masetonia wambu namba role pyao eparama dupwame nakama nyisalana rapa rapa pii nao mee kararami ramo doko kandapala elyaramanopa nakama Korina range dupwa opetaeko elya nyerami ingilyamo.

Dokona lao nambame akali wambo nembelyo dusipame kana lasaka pyuo jerama leyaminyi doko nyepala rapa rapa pirami. Namba eparono dokopa wambo elya pisi seramo kandaro. Nakama Anatu mainya mumu lao karo mai nalyaminyi. Nakama rangeme mamya suu pyaminyili pyuo mailyaminyi doko panara.
Akali mende ee kuki wara pira ramo dokopa ee jingi kukiko manjo nara. Akaii mende ee malu wara pira ramo dokopa ee makande pyuo manjo nara doko suu pyalapape.

Akaii rae maiyuo kana maingi doko kando Anatumi mona retelyamo. Dokona lao akaii mendaki mendaki lao banya suu pilyamuli pyuo simbi simbi pii nao rangena suu pyaa napala kana mainya rae maipala mainya.

Dopa pyuo pirami ramo doko Anatumi isingi bange kuki lama jii nara ingilyamo. Nyepengele dupwa kapa seramopa dee wambu lapo nyisalana suu pyarami ramo kakana pyuo seramo dokona pingyu nyepala kapa konda pyuo mairamioko.
Baepole lao dokopa, Anatu baame ipyapala pendewa wambu dupwa mee maingi. Banya anjiki pingi yulu doko mee sulu singi.

Anatumi ee wara pirami lao ee wal jepala nenge nenge dokona nyisingi kandale. Doko suu pyao nakamana bange konda napala mokwa soo maiyami dokona baame walngi keyange jeramo doko andena lapala nakama keta banya yulu andanyi pyambwara.
Anatu nakama nyiso kamonganyi nembaramopa nakama mee maso bange mokwa soo maipa pyuo kararami. Dokome kana namwa keta jeraminyipa mairama wambu malu dupwame Anatu kando sangyu larami ingilyamo.
Laraminyipa yulu keyange pilyaminyi dokona renge lama palamo. Anatunya wambu nyisaraminyipa wambu malumi Anatu kando ange lapala lakandarami ingilyamo.

Nakama ipyapala bange mokwa soo mairaminyi kandapala wambu malumi nakama Koraisana waili pii keyange lao karaminyi doko yaki nyii nao rolae pyuo karaminyi lao suu pyapala Anatu ketae pyambwarami ingilyamo.
Anatumi banya mona keyange palyuo ipingi renge keyange nakama jiyamosa dokona nakama kando mona andake reto ateŋa lakarami.
Anatunya renge ama mupwa wakasa mende jiyamo dokona lao sangyu lamanale.

Namba Poleme nakama piso sokondali pyuo leto. Namba nakama pipya karo dokopa pau lao anjiki pyuo karene lao letaminyi. Lapala namba nakama pipya kara napunu dokopa nakamana lao namba poralyuo kaelene letaminyiko. Dokona Koraisana kondange rengepe anjiki pingi rengepe dolapona lao piso sokondali piruwale.
Namba eparonopa poralyaiase lao pupi lao laa nalapape. Namwa rangena kingi lakandalana karaminyi letaminyi wambu dupwa kando pii poral kapa pupi lao laro.
Doko kinyi kinyi namwa isa yuu dakena karamano. Karamanopape isa yuunya lao pimwalyuo kara nalyamano.

Yanda pingi bange dusipame minyuo yanda pyuo karamano dupwa mee isa bange daa. Anatunya yanda pingi bange poral panda koo dupwa kokwa singi dusipame minyuo yanda pyuo karamano. Pii kyambo letaminyi dupwa namwa kokwa silyamano.

Wambu lapo Anatunya pii selana suu pyaminyipape suu pingi wakale dupwame nakamana kata doko rokolyaminyi. Doko pyao kokwa silyamano. Namwa suu pingi peparae nyuo malu palyapala Koraisa keta ralinyi pyambulyamano.
Nakamame namwana pii laramanuli pyuo mondo lao piraminyi dokopa nakamana yulu keyange doko kandapala wambu kamba lao karaminyi dupwa randa mairama.

Nakamame neta yanenge ketaena maro lapyamo doko iki kandelyaminyi. Akali mendeme namba Yesu Koraisana akali karo lao suu pilyase? Dopa pira ramo baa rangena mona anda kandenale. Baa Koraisana akali ingyuo karamo dopako pyuo namwa opetaeko Koraisana akali ingyuo karamano.
Kamongome yulu andake namwa jiyamo dokona lao yuu malu mee rae maiyuo enokwanyi nembo leyonopape namba elya nalyo. Yulu andake jiyamo dokome nakama kwaenyi pyambwa napala pyuo andanyi pyambulyamo.
Nambame pepa pase pyao joo pakanyi pyambulinyi lao suu pyaa nalapape.
Akali mendeme dopa lao dokopa, Polena pepa pase pyao imbuo pii poralyuo lengeŋe, dee namwa pipya karelyamo dokopa pii kata pao laa nangeŋe dopa pyuo lara.
Dopa larako doŋo baa akali doko dopa lao suu pinyale. Yuu nanesa karo pepa pyao jowape nakama pipya role pyao karowape pii larono dupwa wakale ingyuo paa naiyamo.

Wambu nakama range lakando mupwa ingyuo karamano letaminyi dupwa pipya namwa makande pirama ingya nalyamo. Nakama kyawa sisingi bolombalo lasi dupwa lao karaminyi. Kyawa sisingi bolombalo lasi dupwa yango sukusa apiyakale lao mendeme mende makande pyuo mendeme mende makande pyuo range karo palyuo piminyili pyuo lao karaminyi.
Namwa mee langa range lakanda narama. Anatumi yulu makande pyuo jiyamo liti doko yalo paa nalyamano liti jiyamo dokona sukusa nakama karaminyi.
Liti doko yalo paa napala nakama kando nyepala Koraisana waili pii keyange boo pyao langiyama.

Akali lapo panda wakale dupwana yulu andake piyami dokona range lakanda narama. Anatunya make yalo paa napala nakama baa kapa ingingi lao angingyuo suu pyaraminyi yulu andake pyakarama lao suu pilyamano.

Enakana nakama palaminyi matarena waili pii keyange raeyo paa nalyamo dokona kapa polo lamairama. Polo lamairama ramo dokopa akali mendeme yulu piyamo dokona lao rae maiyuo pyakaiyuo pyao lao kara narama ingilyamo.
Baepole lao dokopa, Akali mendeme sipurapala lakandalana suu pyara ramo doko Kamongome yulu piyamo dupwa iki lakandena letamo.
Mendeme keyange pilyu lao suu pyapala ketae pyambusi kara nara ingilyamo. Kamongome keyange lao suu pyaramo doko ketae pyambusi kararama ingilyamo.
Kopyali pii kuki mende laro ramo dokopa mata joo kaeya namili lao leto.

Anatumi nakama poralyuo suu pyapyamuli pyuo nambame dopako pyuo suu pyao karo. Nakama enda mapwae pepo kareta, akali role pyaa nange akali mendaki nyelana rombo paiyisi petenge doko dopale ingyuo karaminyi. Nakama akali nyerami doko Koraisa.

Nakamana kyawa sisingi kwaepala Koraisana yulu mondo lao poralyuo pilyaminyi doko yaki nyesaraminyi lao mona kendalyo. Kaumi enda Ipi panga soo lamaiyuo makande piyamo doko suu pyao nakama makande pira lyakande lao suu pilyu.

Akali mende epapala dokopa Yesunya lao pii namwa lenge doko yaki nyepala Yesunya lao pii wakale palyuo lenge ramo doko nakama mee rae maiyuo soo nyilyaminyi. Imambunya piipi waili pii keyange langiyamanopape pii dolapo kame sepala dakepa kyaka wakale imambunya piipi walii pii wakalepe koto nyilyaminyi.
Nakamana aposele akali mupwa ingyuo karaminyipa namba isa palya nalyaminyi lao suu pilyu.
Namba sipurapala pii mora piso laa nange doŋo pii renge dupwa angingyuo silyu. Doko yuu malu mee rolo langiyama.
Anatunya waili pii keyange nakama polo langyuo dokopa namba nakamana yole nyii nayo. Nakama ketae pyambwalana range isa nembo kareyo. Dopa pyuo dokopa kopetame piyusi?
Namba nakama pipya role pyao yulu piyunu dokopa Elyambu Pingi wambu wakale dupwame namba yole jiyami. Dupwana yole waa nyepala nakama nyisiyu. Pii doko mee kongwalu leto.

Dee nakama pipya role pyao karo kana mone oteyamo dokopa nakama keta kee laa nayo. Kurisene wambu yango yuu Masetonia piso epeyaminyi dupwa bange nyelana suu piyunu dusipa minyakao epeyami. Wamba namba nakama mona kendanyi pyambwa nayo kande doko rengya opetae nakama mona kendanyi pyambwa naro.
Koraisana pii kinyi namba keta palamo dokome pii dake elya nao leto. Pii doko yuu Girisi peparae dokona range pyapeta seramopa mee serami lao lalu lao leto.
Aki rengendena namba pii dake letose? Nakama mona reta napunu dokona lao letose? Ama daa. Mona angingyuo reto karo doko Anatu baa soo karamo.
Aposele menge dusipana yulu pilyaminyi dokona range lakandapala namwa pilyaminyi dokoko pilyamano laa nana lao namba yulu pilyu dakeko mee pela paro ingilyamo.
Akali dusipa aposele angi daa. Nakama Anatunya pii rolae laa nange. Namwa Koraisana aposele akali karamano kandalapape lao mee kyambo ingyuo lao karaminyi.
Yulu dopale doko silyamano. Sataneme alowa pipala aŋala yanga paupau lenge dopale ingyuo makande pyuo karenge.

Dokona lao Satane banya kendemande wambu alowa pipala rolae pingi rengena kendemande dopale ingyuo makande pyuo kararami ramo dokopa namwa mona nembo yamarangwa narama. Lumwa piramo yuu gii dokopa yulu piraminyili pyuo yole nyerami.

Pii lapunu doko dee kamba larowale. Mendeme namba kopyali minyuo letene lao suu pyaa nana. Dopa lao suu pyarami ramo doko namba kopyaliyoko lao kando nyerami. Nyeraminyi dokopa nambana yulu dokona lao suu pyao karo kuki range lakando kararo.
Namba epapu letono pii doko Kamongome lamaiyalase lapyamo laa nalyo. Namba range lakando kararo ramo doko namba kopyali minyarosa pira.
Wambu malu mee isa bangena suu pyapala nakama rangena kingi lakandelyaminyi dokona namba dopako pyuo pelana leto.
Nakama kendepuli ingyuo soo giso karaminyi dokona kopyali minyingi akali kando rae mailyaminyi.
Akali mendeme nakama iso nembo kararamopa panga soo minyako piramope dereke piramope randa joo elyanyi pyambwaramope doko baa mee kando nyerami ingilyamo.

Namwa dupwa inyimungu kareyamano dokome dopale ingyuo paa nayama. Dokona lapu dokopa elya pilyamo. Akali mendeme baa rangena lao lakandalana lara ramo doko namba opetae range poralyuo lakandaro. Dokona ingyuo namba kopyali pii leto.
Aposele angi daa dupwa, Ipuru rara ramo doko namba opetaeko Ipum rara. Nakama Isaraele rara ramo doko namba opetae dokoreko. Nakama Aporakamena para pyasisi? Namba opetaeko.

Nakama Koraisana kendemandese? Namba doko kopyalindelyamo lao seraminyipape namba kendemande mupwa ingyuo karapunupa doloma mee dolapo karaminyi. Doko namba yulu andake pyuo kareyo kande. Yuu malu karapusi palyuope yuu malu kusape nyuope dee namba andarele ingyuo repeta kumaro ingiyamopa nakama randa dopale nyii nayami.
Juu wambu dupwame wambu pyalana dokopa marapu dokome pyao karelyaminyipa yuu akalisa rema ipisu mange mendaki karo pingi doko suu pyao namba yuu kingi paki piyami.

Orome wambu dupwame yuu rema marapu dokome namba piyami. Dee yuu mendepa kana dupwame piyami. Yuu rema namba ipwa sipunya pao kareyono sipu kapu kyiya. Yuu lama kapu kyiyamopa namba walya lao nyiyaminyipape repo ingyuo kapu kyiyamo dokopa kukwa yuu gii mendaki korakama yuu gii mendaki doko peparae ipwa dokona palyuo siyu.

Namba yuu malu kata papyuo kareyono dokopa ipwa dupwa paiipalape waa nyingi akali dupwame Juu wambu yangope Juu daa rara wakale wambu dupwamepe pyalana piyami. Yuu taone dokonape imwana peyo dokopape ipwa sipu dupwanape randa epeyamopa puu angi minya nange dupwame opetaemeko randa jelana pyuo piyaminyi kareyo.
Dopa pyuo nambana yulu andake wakasa siya. Yuu malu luu pali nayo. Dee nenge ipwape nanome kumuo kareyo. Yuu malu mee nenge aeya nao anda kara nao komau see nao piyamo kareyo.
Yuu malu mee Elyambu Pingi doko randa nyilyaminyi dokome nambana mona yanyi pilyamo. Dee randa wakale lapo epelyamoko.
Elyambu Pingi wambu mendeme poralya nara ramo doko namba dopako piru. Dee mendeme yulu koo pira ramo doko namba mona nembo kararoko.
Namba rae maiyuo pyakalyuo pyao laro ramo doko namba angi daaŋa lao dokona ingyuo laro.
Namwana Kamongo Yesunya Rakane Anatu, kyambo laa nalene lao silyamo. Banya kingi poo pyasi ingyuo sulu soo sinya.
Namba yuu Damasakesa kareyonopa Kiŋi Aretasana gapomane akali dokome akali lapome namba anjirami lao taonena kambu repeta kandaro karena leya.
Taonena kana kame maiawal lasi dokona windowa mende siyamo dokona namba pisiki minyasi kameya dokona palyapala neta nembeyaminyipa neta puu pao peyo.

Rae maiyuo kingi lakandenge yulu dokome mendali nyisa nalyamo. Nyisa napyamopape kata wakale mende see nalyamo dokona mende larowale. Kamongome kombeyame dupwanape pii repa repa pyuo langiyamo dupwape polo langirowale.

Kurisene akali mende yake panda ketae dulurena lanyuo peyamo doko silyu. Yuu wamba ee kana akalisa ipisu kisima dokopa piya. (Doko kinyi angi piyase panda kombeyame ingyuo pii repa repa piyase lao see nalyo. Anatu baa iki soo gisilyamo.)

Dee kamba leto. Akaii doko walya lao panda ama elyape peya doko silyu. (Dee kambako leto. Doko kinyi angi piyase panda kombeyame ingyuo pii repa repa piyase lao see nalyo. Anatu baa iki soo gisilyamo.)
Baa yake panda karo dokopa pii lapo isa wambu dupwame kapa laa naramiii dupwa soo nyiya.
Dokona lao akaii dokona rae maiyuo lakandaro. Namba range lakanda naronopape namba angi daaŋa lao dokona iki laro ingilyamo.

Namba rangena kingi lakandalana lao suu pyaro ramo doko pii doko kinyi ingyaramo dokona namba kopyaii ingya nara. Wambu dupwame nambana yulu kando pii dokona pyapi pyuo soo pirami dokona iki suu pinyale. Dokona nambana lao suu pyaraminyi doko rolae ingyuo para. Namba rangena kingi lakandaro ramo doko angi ingya nara.

Bange keyange wakasa dupwa kandeyono dokome namba moŋokyaŋe see nare lao randa pyuo anga yakane kisiya. Doko Satanena kendemande ingyapyamo dokona namba pyapala moŋokyaŋe see nareŋe lao lasaka pilyamo.
Yuu remasa lao Kamongo kando ateŋa lao anga yakane doko neta nyuo nembakare lao piso siyu.

Dokopa Yesu baame dopa pyuo yano pyao langyuo, Nambana mona keyange palyuo ipingi renge dokome iki emba kapa pyakara. Emba koo ingyuo papala pinya saka nange dokopa nambame poralnya renge dokome emba minyalyingi, leya. Koraisana poralnya renge namba keta palira lao namba yakara pipyamopa rae maiyuo pyakalyuo pyao karo.

Namba poral napunupape Koralsana reke lao dokome rae maiyuo karo. Koraisana reke lao wambu namba kando giyalya giyana piyaminyipape randa andake wakale wakale nyiyunupape rae maiyuo kararoko. Namba poralya nange dokopa Kamongona poralnya renge dokome paka pyao singi. Poleme Korina Wambu Dupwa Ponuyuo Suu Piya

Nakama kopetame piyaminyisa namba kopyali pii lao karo. Nakama nambana kingi lakandarami ramo doko kapa ingilyamo. Namba mende daa ingyapuli doko nakamana aposele akali wakale dupwa kamame isa pumili.

Namba nakama pipya yulu mondo lao pyuo kareyono dupwa kandapala namba aposele akali angi doko range siyami. Yuu gii dokopa yulu mupwa Anatumi namba keta piya dupwa wambu kandapala yamaranguyami. Doko wambumi yulu pii nangende piyamosa yamarangyuo kareyamiko.

Elyambu Pingi menge dupwa nyisapala nakama range kame siyusi? Elyambu Pingi wakale dupwame nyisinya leyono dokopa nakama kando laronde kaeyo. Yuu gii dokopako Elyambu Pingi wakale dupwa pinginyili pyuo pii napala nakama iki nyuo kame siyupya. Dopa piiŋi lao suu pyaa nalapape.

Dake yuu repo ingyuo nakama kandala epana karo. Eparono dokopa nakamana bange mende nyelana pupi lao kee laa naro. Nakamana kana mone nyipulinya masa nalyo. Nakama namba mona nyilyu. Dokona ingyuo wane wanakepeme endangi rakangepe bange maiyuo rapu pinginde daa. Endangi rakangepena yulu singi.
Namba nakama nyisalana rae maiyuo nambana bangepe dee namba range opetae nakama joo otarowale. Nambame nakama mona wakasa ingyuo retelyono dokona nakamame namba mona kuki ingyuo retaramisi?
Namba epeyono dokopa randa jii nayoŋo doko silyaminyi. Siminyipape akali mendeme kyambo panga soo minyako piiŋi leya doko akipamo leyase?
Aki mendena minyako piyusi? Nambame wal minyingi akali pena leyono dokopa panga soo leyopyase?
Nambame Taitesa pisokondali pyuo lao dee Kurisene yango mende role pyao pena leyo. Taitesame nakama minyako piya letamisi? Taitesa nambapa suu pingi mendaki palyuo yulu mendare pyuo pii nangese?

Yuu peparae wambu dupwame pii nambwa keta yanda pimwaiyuo lakalyaminyi dokopa nambwa range kyawa minyuo letambinyi lao suu pilyamisi? Dopa pii nalyambano. Anatunya lenge kambunya karo Koraisame pii lalapape lapyamuli pyuo letambano. Yangonemoo nambwa yulu peparae pilyambano dokome nakama nyisalana pilyambano.

Namba eparono dokopa nakama kapu kyepala wakale ingyuo kararaminyi lao pakalyo. Dee nakamame namba karareli lao suu pyaraminyi doko kaepala wakale ingyuo karasarono lapala dokona mona kendalyoko. Nakama yango sukusa lalya lao yango palyuo imbwuapala rango nao wambu yango lao nembo pyuo kararami ingilyamo. Nakama kopetame pyuo mata kando lao moŋokyaŋe soo kararami ingilyamo dupwana mona kendo karo.

Dee eparono dokopa Anatunii nakamana lenge kambu dokona namba elyanyi pyambwara dokona pakalyo. Dopa suu pyao wambu malumi yulu koo pyuo kepo enda kando lyanolyano pipala mona kapu kyii nayami dupwa nakama kando ee laro, lao suu pilyu.

Dake yuu repo pyuo namba kandala eparo ingilyamo. Buku Baepole pii dokona lao dokopa. Akali mendeme mendali kando randa maiyuo lara ramo dokopa wusinisi akali lamape remapeme baa nyiso larami ramo dokopa baa kapa kote lara letamo.

Nakama wambo yulu koo piyaminyipape dee menge lapo koo piyaminyi dupwape opetae nambana pii selapape. Pii larono doko wambo yuu gii lapo pyuo epeyono dokopa leyono pii doko nanesa karo dee kamba laro. Namba dee kamba eparono dokopa mendali pyarepala paa nana lao randa mairu.
Koraisame namba keta pii lenge dokona dokopa nakama soo gisarami. Soo gisaraminyi doko Koraisame nakama kando angangi kararande daa. Dopa pyuo banya porainya renge lasaka pira.

Baa pau lasi ingyuo kareyamopa isa mamandona pyao palyiyaminyipape Anatunya porainya renge dokome Koraisa lete karamo. Baamoo pipya pakao karenge dokome namwa opetaeko pau lasi ingyuo karenge. Anatunya porainya renge namwa keta paliramopa namwa Yesupa role pyao karo nakama rapu pyuo kararama.

Nakama Kurisene panda Kurisene angi daa lao range makande pyuo kandalapape. Koraisa Yesu nakamana mona anda palamo doko soo gisilyaminyi. Soo gisa naminde pili doko nakamana Kurisene yulu doko mee ketae pupyali.
Namwa isa puu pao paa nalyamano doko nakama soo gisamili.

Nakama yulu koo mende pii namili lao Anatu kando ateŋa lakalyamano. Ateŋa lao dokopa namwana yulu mupwa ingyuo pelyamo lao laa nalyamano. Namwa isa puu pao pelyaminyi lao suu pyaminyipape nakama yulu rolae iki pirami dokona reke lao dopa pyuo ateŋa lakalyamano.
Namwa Anatunya pii kinyi dokona isa palyalana saka nange. Yulu pilyamano doko Anatunya pii kinyi dokona nyiso pingi.
Nakama porai ingyuo karelyaminyipa namwa mee karapala rae maingi. Nakama koo mende pii naraminyipa yapasi ingyuo pisirami lao ateŋa pyakalyamano.

Renge dokona lao namba nanesale karo pepa dake pyao jilyu. Dokona namba eparonopa Kamongome namba rapu pyuo iso karare leyamopape poraiyuo pyalana pyuo kara naro. Kamongome namba rapu pyuo iso karare leyamo dokopa kwaenyi pyambwa napala pyuo andanyi pyambwalase langiya.

Yangonemoo karalapape. Koo mende pii nao mondo lao karalapape. Nambana pii dake warombo selapa. Nakama mona mendare palyuo dokopa suu pingi mendaki palyuo lambo lao karalapape. Dopa piraminyi dokopa Anatu mona retengepe mona kyuu lao singipi doko baa nakama pipya role pyao karara.
Wambu yango dupwa yako lao kingi nyuo karalapape. Anatunya wambu dae karaminyi peparaeme nakama yako letaminyiko.
Kamongo Yesu Koraisana mona keyange palyuo ipingi rengepe Anatunya mona retenge rengepe Imambu Poo Pyasinya yalya kando petenge rengepe nakama keta palenale.

Namba Pole. Isa akali mendeme namba rombo palyapala nembowape panda akali ketako Anatumi namba aposele ingyuo rombo palyiyande daa. Yesu Koraisapa Rakane Anatu Yesu lopo nyiyamo dolapome rolae namba rombo palyiyambi.
Nambamoo akali yango dae role pyao karamano dupwa pipyame pepa dake Galasia Elyambu Pingi dupwana pyao jilyamano.
Namwana Rakane Anatupa Kamongo Yesu Koraisapana mona kyuu lao singi rengepe mona keyange palyuo ipingi rengepe nakama keta palena.
Koraisa namwana koo dupwana lao Rakane Anatunya suu pingi doko moko minyuo range kumuo palipala yulu koo dakepa silyamo dupwana lao namwa kiiramo nyiya.
Dokona lao Anatunya kingi doko lakando palu palena, doko kinyi.
Nakamba Koraisana mona keyange palyuo ipingi dokome kyakale leyamo doo walyako lao yaki nyepala waili pii wakale mendenako pumisa namba kando yamarangulyu.
Waili pii doko lamande daa. Dokona akali lapome Koraisana waili pii doko alowa pelana pii mendena wakale kyawa sisingi bolombalo lanyi nembamisa dokona leto.
Namwa rangemepe panda aŋala yake panda karenge dupwamepe waili pii wambo mana langiyama doko yaki nyepala waili pii wakale polo langirama ramo doko baa Satanena panda dokona para ingilyamo.
Namwa wamba lao kaenge dokona kamba leto. Nakama wambo waili pii soo nyiyami doko kaepala wakale mendeko langiramo akali doko Satanena panda para ingilyamo.

Pii dae lapu doko akali dupwame namba lakandena lao lapusi? Doko daa. Anatu rae mainyi pyambuo leto. Wambu peparae nambana kingi lena lao pilyusi? Dopa pinya lao lao karapuli doko Koralsana kendemande angi ingya napuli.
Yangonemoo pii dake langirowale selapa. Waili pii lao karo doko akalimi wasa nayami.
Akali mendali keta soo nyuope dee mendeme namba mana langyuo pii naya. Pii nayamopape Yesu Koraisa baa rangeme waili pii namba nolakao langyuo jiya.
Namba wambo Juu wambunya misi yulu dokona sukusa karo yulu kopetame piyu dokona langiyaminyi siyami. Doko anjiki pii nao Anatunya Elyambu Pinginya wambu randa maiyuo kokwa selana suu pyao piyu.

Namba Kurisene ingyapa nayonopa tembole anda yulu mana nyuo dokopa Juu wane yango andarele dupwa nyuo isa nembowale mana nyuo kareyo. Namwana rora ambasupinya yulu palenge dupwana suu pyale pyale kareyo.
Kareyonopape Anatu mona keyange palyuo ipyapala namba ene manjipa nayami dokopa baame namba rombo palyuo banya yulu dokona pyakare lao kyakale lao kaeyapya.
Baame banya lkinyingi namba keta panaronopa waili pii keyange doko Juu daa rara wakale dupwa lamairi lao suu piyapya dokona nambame wambu mendali keta apa pyuo piru lao piso sela paa nayo.
Dopa pyuo paa naoko dee wambo aposele ingiyami dupwa Jerusaleme kareyami dokona kandala paa nayoko. Kaepala yuu Arapia walya lao papala yuu Damasakesa dokona dee lalyuo epeyo.
Enakana kana rema epo papeyamo dokopa Jerusaleme Pita kareyamo dokona papala lapo piso siyu. Siyunupa koro lama role pyao kareyamba.
Dokopa namba Kamongona yangonge Jemesa iki kandeyonopape aposele menge dupwa kanda nayo.
Pii pyao retelyo dake kinyi. Kyambo laa nalyo doko Anatu soo karamo.
Enakana yuu Siria Silisiapana liti dolapona peyo.
Yuu gii dusipana Jutia Kurisene wambu dupwame namba soo pakana palyapa nayami.

Wakale dupwame nambana yulu dupwa polo lamaiyaminyi lasi pii siyami. Nakamame lao dokopa, Akalinde namwa randa jiya kande dokome epapu waili pii wambo kokwa selana piyamo dokoko minyuo lao karamo leyami.
Leyaminyi sepala nambana yulu dokona kando Anatu lakando kareyami.
Enakana ee kana akalisa dee ipisu kisima epo papeyamopa Jerusaleme Banapasapa role pyao lambuo peyamba. Dokopa nambame Taltesa opetae lanyuo peyo.

Namba dokona mee peyonde daa. Anatumi pupili lao langiyasa peyo. Doko namba Elyambu Pingjnya mupwa dupwamoo pipya wato leyami dokona nambame waili pii Juu daa rara wakale dupwa polo lamaiyuŋu lao lamaiyu. Nambana yulu dakepape dee wambo piyunupape dupwana mee ingyuo paa nana lao suu pyao peyo.
Nambana akali yango Taltesa baa Giriki rara ingiyamopape yanenge awali lao pyakepinya lao laa nayami.

Laa nayaminyipape akali lapo namwana wato lenge dokon panga soo mee yangonge ingyuo kolalyuo epeyami dupwame baa yanenge pyakepakaminya leyami. Akali dupwame namwa pipya karo Yesu Koraisana arapunya namwa karenge dokome apa pyuo lao lowana kiiramo pasi karamano dokona maa palyuo kandala epeyami. Nakamame namwa lowa malu dupwana dee puu maiyuo bwuakarami lao suu piyami.
Nakama Kurisene dupwana lao suu pyapala waili pii dokona renge keyange dupwa isa pakami nana lao nakambana pii doko ama see nayama.

Wato lao kareyama dokona akali mupwa dupwame namba waili pii lao kareyo dokona suu pingi enenge mende langya nayami. (Nakama kingi londapala lao kareyaminyipape namba dokona mende suu pyaa nayo. Anatumi wambu kuki andakepe lao mende suu pyaa nange kandale.)
Nakama Anatumi Pita Juu wambu dupwa keta waili pii lamaira lao mapanyi pyambuyamo doko suu pyao namba Juu daa rara wakale dupwa lamairi lao mapanyi peyalyamo lao kandeyami.
Anatunya porainya renge dokome Pita Juu wambu pipya yulu pinya lao aposele inginyi pyambuyamo dopako pyuo namba Juu daa rara wakale dupwana lao aposele inginyi pyambuya.

Jemesa Pita Jonemoo Elyambu Pinginya akali andake dusipame Anatumi yulu mupwa dake namba keta jiyalyamo lao siyami. Sepala namba Banapasapa yako lao kingi nyiyami. Namwa peparae yulu mendakinya pyuo nakama doloma Juu wambu pii lamairaminyipa nambwa rara wakale dupwa lamairama dupwana sepala kapa lao kaeyama.
Yulu mendaki iki jiyami doko wambu pendewa dupwa nyiso karalapape lao leyami. Dopa leyamioko doŋo namba dokonako suu pyao yulu poralyuo kaeyo pyuo kareyo.
Pita yuu Andioko epeyamo dokopa nambame wambu kareyami dokona baa kyal pyuo piyamo dokona pyalana pyuo rolo lamaiyu.

kali lapo Jemesame pena leya dusipa epapa nayaminyi dokopa Pita baa akali wakale yanenge kaloma nange dupwa pipya nenge nao peteya. Dee akali yanenge pyakepenge mawa pii dokona poral minyingi dupwa epapeyaminyi dokopa Pita pakapala rara wakale pipya yaki nyuo kaeyo nenge role pyao naa nao peteya.
Dokopa Juu yango lapo opetaeko pakapala Pita peyamo kata dokonako peyami. Dopa pyuo yambe pyao piyami kata dokona Banapasa opetae kaki rambe rambe palyuo panya piya.

Dopa piyamo dokona nambame kandapala waili pii rolae dokona kata angi paa nayami dokona lao wambunya lenge kambu dokona Pita kando dopa lao, Emba Juu angi kandape. Juu ingyuo kareeneko doŋo palyuo karo pipinyi dupwame Juu ingya napala rara wakale karo palyuo pilyaminyi dokonako mende ingilyamo. Dokome apa pyuo menge akali dupwa Juu inginya lao letese? lamaiyu.
Kinyi namwa Juu rara dokona mandeyaminyi karamano. Rara menge dupwa yulu koo paleta mandeyami dopale ingyuo kara nalyamano.

Akali Yesu Koraisa kapa ingingi lao suu pingi dupwa Anatupa rolae ingyuo penge doko silyamano. Lowana moko minyingi ramo dokome rolae ingyuo paa nange. Namwa opetae Yesu Koraisa mona reto baa kapa ingingi lao suu piyamanopa dokome namwa Anatupa rolae ingyuo peyama. Lowa iki moko minyiyamali dokopa Anatupa rolae ingyuo paa nayamali. Mendeme Lowa letamuli pyuo doko iki moko minyuo pira ramo doko Anatupa rolae ingyuo paa nara.

Namwa rara menge yulu koo pingi dopale pipala Anatu namwana yulu koo dupwa kame sakana lao Koraisa dokona repeta eparama ramo doko Koraisame namwana koo dupwa kando rae maiyuo kararasa pirase? Ama daa.
Namba Lowa wambarae kaeyapenge leyo dupwa deeko nyepala pyuo karo laro ramo doko nambame Lowa kokwa sinyi nembelene lao panara.

Lowa dokome namba mata rukyu piyamo kumasi ingyuo kareyo. Lowa rangeme dopa pyuo namba pyao kumuyamopa epapu Anatunya lete dokona karalu kararo. Koraisapa isa mamandona kumasi paleyo dokona epapu namba range angi kara nalyo. Koraisa banya lete renge doko namba keta palamo. Epapu yulu pyuo karo dupwa Anatunya lkmyingi namba mona retapala kumuyamo doko baa kapa ingingi lao suu pyao pyuo karapusa pilyamoko. Anatunya mona keyange palyuo ipingi doko mata maiyuo nemba nalyo. Akali dupwa Lowa dokome Anatupa rolae ingyuo peyamili doko Koraisa baa mee kumuo paleyali.
Nakamba Oaiasia wambu kopyali ingyuo pelyaminyi. Apimi nakama panga soo langipyasa raio karamipi? Yesu Koraisa isa mamandona kumuyamo dokona lao rolo langiyama renge dupwa kandapa nayamisi?

Nakama pii mendakindena isingi langilapape. Nakama Anatunya Imambu nyiyami kande doko apa pipala nyiyamipi? Lowa kata dokona minyapala nyiyamipi panda nakama waili pii doko soo kapa ingingi lao manjo nyepala dokona Imambu nyiyamipi?

Apa pipala nakama kopyali ingyaiu ingyuo ingilyamipi? Nakama Anatunya Imambunya yulu dokona kanda soo piyarmi kande doko, epapu nakama rangeme yanengena yulu wambarae dokome ayemba palyuo pyuo otaiana pilyamisi?
Imambunya yulu andake kandeyami dupwa mee ingyuo pelyase? Apa pyuo isa parase?

Anatumi Imambu jepala wambumi yulu pii nange dupwa nakama keta piya doko Lowana yulu minyuo karaminyi lapala dokona piyase? Panda waili pii kinyi lao soo nyiyami dokona Anatumi Imambu joo yulu andake piyase?
Buku Baepole lao dokopa, Akali Aporakame Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu piyamosa Anatumi baa akali rolae lao kandeyapya.
Dokona ingyuo akali dupwa Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyaraminyi dupwa Aporakamena wai pyao nyisi ingyuo paramisa pira.

Juu wakale dupwa Anatu mona maipa nayami dokopa nakama Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyapala rolo parami. Doko Anatumi Aporakame keta wambo ingyuo waili pii keyange lamaipala lao, Embapa lapolapo lao wambu yuu muu peparae elyape keta pisirami Baepole leya.
Aporakame Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu piyamosa elyape keta peya. Dokonako ingyuo mendeme Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyao kararami dupwa baa piyamo dopako pyuo elyape ketako paiyuo parami.

Mosesena Lowa dupwa kapa minyarama lao suu pilyaminyi dupwa koo keta karamisa pilyamo. Dokona ingyuo Baepolena pii mende pyasi palamo. Doko mawa pii malu Lowa buku dokona pyasi palamo dupwa peparae kapa minya narami dupwa koo keta parami letamo.

Wambu mende Lowa dokome Anatuya lenge kambu dokona rolo paa nara doko angi silyamano. Baepolena lao dokopa, Mendali Anatu baa kapa ingingi lao suu pyara dokome Anatupa rolae ingyuo karara dokome baa lete para ingilyamo letamo.

Lowa minyingi akalimi Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingi dokona paiyuo suu pyaa nange Dokona ingyuo buku Baepole dokona lao, Akalimi Lowa palamuli pyuo karara doko Lowa dokona yeelyo sisu lao karara ingilyamo letamo.
Koraisame namwana iao randa nyakapala Lowa namwa randa jingi dokona kiiramo nyiya. Buku Baepoie dokona dopa lao letamo. Akali isa mamandona kumuo penge doko kumungi renge baa keta palamo letamo.

Anatumi Aporakame dokona pii lala lao iamaiyamo renge keyange dupwa Juu daa rara wakale dupwa opetaena palenale lao, Koraisa Yesumi koo keta palyuo isa mamandona kumuo peya. Dokome namwa Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pilyamano dupwa Imambu Poo Pyasi kando nyerama ingilyamo.

Yangonemoo namwana yulu palenge dupwana makande minyuo langirowale. Doko akali lamame yulu mende pirambaŋa lao lao kana minyarambinyi dokopa mendeme alowa pyuope dee konda pyuo lakamyuope pii nara ingilyamo.

Anatumi Aporakame banya wane dokopa elyape keta pyambwaro lao kana minyuo leya. Doko para pyao nyeramo dupwa peparae suu pyao laa naya. Banya wane mendaki leyamo doko Koraisa dokona suu pyao leyasa piya.

Pii dokona renge polo langirowaie. Anatumi kana minyapala lala lao leto lao lao oteya. Enakana ee kana malu 430 epo papeyamopa Lowa pyaka siya. Pyaka siyamo dokome Anatu pirunya lao lao kana minyuo leyamo doko Lowa dokome isa nembara ingya nange.

Lowa dokome moyange bange doko kapa nyingi pili doko pii lao kana minyingi kata dokona moyange bange nyii napengele. Dopa pyuo nyingiko doŋo Anatumi banya moyange bange Aporakame mairu lao lalu lao leya.

Wambunya yulu pimi dokome epelyande daako. Dopa pilyamo dokona mendeme range lakandapengele ingya nalyamo.
Anatu range namwa wasiya. Namwa Koraisa Yesupa pako yulu keyange pirami lao wasiya. Namwa kata rolae dupwana papyuo kararama dupwa Anatumi wamba rapa rapa piya.

Nakamana yanenge ketae dokome Juu daa rara wakale ingyuo kareyami. Yanenge awali lao kalomenge dupwame nakama yanenge awali lao kaloma nange lenge kandale. (Yulu doko kingimi iki yanenge dokona kalomenge.) Nakama wambo apiyakale ingyuo kareyami doko kame see nalapape.

Wamba dokopa nakama Koraisapa liti pyuo karo, Isaraele rara dokopa wakale ingyuo kareyami. Anatumi Isaraele keta keyange mairunya lao pii lanyi sereyamo dokona nakama kamenge ambe ambe kareyami. Isa panda dokona Anatu soo nyii napala dokopa mende pyakarandelyamo lao mona kare kare kara nayami.
Dopa pyuo nanesa kareyaminyipape epapu nakama Koraisa Yesu keta banya ranjama isa peyamo dokome nakama banya arapunya karaminyi.

Baa namwana manda rao nyingi ingyuo karamo dokona banya rangena yongo dokome namwa Juu rara dee nakama rara wakale dupwape nyuo pakapala imbu singi kame lili piru kareyamo doko nyuo lalyinyi isa nembeya.

Juu wambunya Lowa dupwape mawa pii dupwape waso karenge dupwape peparae mee inginyi nembeya. Nembapala rara paka lakisi siyamo doko kaepala baa keta nyuo komondapala rara enenge mendakinya ingyuo manda rao karena lao piya.
Koraisame isa mamandona kumuyamo dokome yanda pii lao rambu nyepala namwa nyuo mendakyapala Anatu kareyamo dokona dee lanyiya.
Baame Anatupa Juu wambupi Juu daa rara wakalepe koto nyepala mona mendare palyingi waili pii keyange doko boo pyao lamaiya.
Koraisa yulu andake piyamo dokona namwa rara laparae Imambu Poo Pyasi keta Rakange Anatu dokona repeta eparama.
Dokona lao nakama epapu menge upunyili ingyuo kara napala Anatunya wambu yapasi dupwa pipya mendare ingyapyamopa Anatunya ree palu ingyuo karaminyi.
Anda doko aposele akalipi poropeta akalipi dupwa andana renge kuingi isa dupwa ingyuo karaminyipa pisi karamo. Koraisa Yesu baame anda pinginya ingyaro karamo.
Anda kimbu soo pisi dokona baame simuisa ingyuo minyaro karamo. Doko Kamongopa pako karo misi anda yapasi ingyuo andelyamo.
Nakama opetae Koraisa keta kimbu silya sana pyuo pisi karaminyi. Anda pisi doko Anatu Imambu dokopa paleta karenge.
Dokona lao namba Pole nakama Juu daa rara wakale dupwana lao Koraisa Yesunya anjisi akali ingyuo karo.
Anatu mona keyange palyuo ipyapala nambame nakama nyisareŋe lao yulu andake namba keta jiyamo doko siyami lao suu pilyu.
Yalu pyuo palenge renge andake doko namba keta paneyamo siyu doko, (wambo pepana muu pyuo piyu kande.
Pii pyasi doko yaka laparaminyi dokopa namba Koraisana yalu pingi renge doko kokorename kandeelyamo lao separami.)
Doko wambu kyawa ingyuo kareyami dupwame soo kara nayami doko epapuli aposele yapasi dupwape poropeta akali dupwape banya Imambumi lamaiyuo panapyamo simi.

Yalu pisi renge epapu panelyamo doko, Juu daa rara wakale dupwa waili pii keyange sepala Anatunya keyange dupwa Juu wambu pipya kapa kapa pyuo nyerami. Nakama namwapa yongo mendaki ingyapala Anatumi Koraisa Yesu keta keyange jeroŋo leyamo dupwa mokwa soo nyerami.
Anatu mona keyange palyuo ipyapala banya poral renge namba mee jiyamo dokopa namba waili pii minyingi akali ingiya.

Anatunya wambu yapasi menge dupwa peparaena namba kamame isale ingyuo karapunupape Koraisana kamongonge bange kapa pyuo soo nyii naramili dupwa namba keta epeya. Doko Juu daa rara wakale dupwa mana lamaiyuo karapenge dokona lao jiya.
Anatu baa bange peparae wasiya dokome ama kal wamba mende piru lao suu pyapala yambe piya doko namba lao panaronopa wambu peparae serami.
Dokona ingyuo Anatunya soo gisinginya renge peparae Elyambu Pingi keta lasaka piramopa yake dorena poralpi mupwa dupwapeme soo nyerami.
Anatumi wambo mende pironya lao suu pyao karengenyili pyuo namwana Kamongo Koraisa Yesu keta pipiya.
Yesu kapa ingingi lao suu pyao baa keta pyamaiyisi karo dokopa Anatu karamo dokona eŋa nembo mee kapa parama doko silyamano.
Dokona ingyo nambame nakamana lao randa nao karo dokona mona nemba nalapape. Nakama kapa palirami dokona lao randa koo nao karo.
Dokona ingyuo Rakange lao mona kando kingi lao karo.
Baa keta piso yake panda isa pandape ree palu peparaena kingi lasi dupwa epeya.
Kamongo Anatunya yanga paupau lenge renge jingi ingyuo lyuo karamo doko Imambu keta epo nakama maralyapala mona andarena poralnyi pyambunya lao ateŋa lakalyo.
Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu piyami dokona Koraisa nakamana monarena palyuo yuuli andale lena. Nakamame mona retenge renge dokona pingi pyapala poral ingyaramo kararami.

Koraisana mona rentengena makande doko kamame andake dokome, Yuu nanesa pao oto ruŋu paŋu lamo laope yuu ulu pao lepo pyuo lamo laope yuu ono komba ayanda pao lamo laope nakama Anatunya wambu peparae dupwamoo pipya, kando simili yaka lao ateŋa lakalyo.
Kinyi Yesunya mona retenge renge wakasa isa wambumi soo ota paa nange doko soo nyeraminyi dokopa Anatu dokona mona retenge renge palyuo simbuo pelyamo doko makande minyuo nakama keta palyuo simbwara.
Anatumi banya poral renge namwa keta silyamo dokome suu pyarama dupwape jinya larama dupwape kama konda pyuo yamarangunyi nembo jingi.
Wambu wambowanape enakana dupwamepe Elyambu Pingi ketape Koraisa Yesu ketape Anatunya kingi doko ketae pyambuo puu parami.
Namba Kamongona kingi reke lao puu maisi akali ingyuo karo dokome Anatu nakama kee leyamo dokona suu pyao keyange pyuo karalapape lao poralyuo leto.
Nakama pau lao anjiki pyuo wambu yango kando walya lao imbu singi nyii napala kenda jerami dupwa nyuo sakamyuo mona reto karalapa.
Imambumi nakama mona mendare palyingi dokome nakama mendakinya ingyuo anjala anjala paramopa yalya kando kararama lao poraiyuo suu pyao karalapape.
Yongo mendaki dokako iki. Dee Imambu mendaki dokako. Anatumi nakama kyakale leyamo dokona keyange mende pyakara lao mona kare kare karaminyi doko renge mendakiko.
Kamongo mendakiko, Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingi renge mendakiko, bapitisimo mendakiko.
Namwa peparaena Rakange Anatu mendakiko, baa peparaena nyilyingi ingyuo karenge. Peparaena kapa kapa pyuo pingi dee namwa peparae keta palengeko.
Koraisa keta elyape dupwa epeyamopa Anatumi manda manjo nyeramanuli pyuo mokwa soo jiya.
Dokona lao pii mende pyasi palamo. Baa pulyuo pao dokopa anamasi minyuo walku nyiyamo dupwa lanyuo papala wambu keta mora petenge renge lapo mee maiya.
Baa pulyuo peyaŋa lao pii palamo doko apa letase? Baa lupyuo yuu donorename opetaeko peyaŋa letamo.
Baa lupyuo peyamo dokoko pao yake ketae ama dulurename peparaena pawiyalana peya.
Baa mora petenge renge joo karenge dokome, lapo aposele inginyi pyambuo, lapo poropeta ingyuo, lapo waili pii minyingi ingyuo, lapo rapu pingi ingyuo, dee lapo mana lenge ingyuo pyambuo piya.
Dokome Anatunya yapasi wambu dupwa mondo lanyi pyambuo dokopa Kurisene yulu pirami dokome Koraisana yongo dokona andanyi nembaraŋa lao piya.

Yulu dokomeoko pao namwa baa kapa ingingi lao suu pingi dupwa mendarele ingyuo parama. Dee Anatunya Ikinyingi dokona soo nyerami dokopa, Koraisa baa akali angingyuo karenge dokona manda manjo namwa andanyi nembarasa pira.

Dopa pyuo pirama ramo namwa wane kuki ingyuo wambu lapo yulu koona kendapuli ingyuo suu pingi kyal dokome namwa ukiaki minyilyasa panga soo nyilya nyana pyuo kararaminyipape namwa kao pele pele lao karenge dokona ingya naramasa pira.
Dopale ingya napala namwa wambu yango mona maipala pii rolae lao kararama dokome namwana akali kyawa Koraisa dopale ingyuo andamanale.

Baa kyawa dokona namwa banya kingi kimbu lengepe rangena panda dokona pyakuiyalya pyakuiyana piro kara napala kapa pela penge. Dokona namwa yongo mendaki ingilyamo dokome mende nyisalya nyisana pyuo poraiyuo piramano dokome yongo peparae mona retenge renge dokona simuisa ingyuo ando para ingilyamo.
Kamongona kingi lao pii dake pyalana pyuo leto. Juu daa rara wakale see nao karenge dupwame kopetame suu pyao pyuo karaminyi dokona yulu dopale pii nalapape.
Nakamba suu pingi iminjiyamo karo, kamenge see nao pisipala mona kana pokwapala Anatupa rekya lao karaminyi.
Langa papyuo kanda lyanolyano pyuo yulu koo yeelyo pinya wangu lakapala pingi.
Yulu dopale doko Koraisa keta siyamo kando nyii nayami kande.
Nakama mana nyuo dokopa Yesu dokona kinyinya renge baa keta renge kuiyuo palenge doko siyami.
Yulu wambarae pinginyili pyuo, pyuo papyuo karo kanda lyanolyano pinya wangu lakao piyaminyisa nakama kokwa sinyi nembeya doko ramanyi nembalapape.
Nakama mona suu pingipi alowa pyuo enenge ingyuo karalapape.
Kyakana renge Anatu makande minyuo rolae pyuo yapasi palamo dokona nyuo maralyalapape.
Dokona lao kyambo pii dupwa nembo Kurisene yango kando pii angi lao karamanale. Namwa yongo mendaki ingyuo pelyamo kande.
lmbu singi epeya kande dokopa koo angi doko ketae nyii nao dee imbu singi paleta piso yuu kwuasinyi reta nao pipape.
Satane baa panda mai nalapape.
Waali dupwa deeko waa nyii nana. Waa nyii nao rangena kingi dolapome yulu andake pyuo rolae pyuo karena. Yulu andake pipala kakana seramo dokona nyuo wambu bange aeyange dupwa maiyuo karara.
Pii koo dupwa nakamana kambunya neta nyii nao pii keyange yapo, pii keyange dupwa lao wambu yango nyisaraminyi dokopa serami dupwa elya pisi ingyuo pararmi.
Anatunya Imambu Poo Pyasi lekeleke koo rena lao pii nalapape. Anatumi yuu gii lumwa piramo dokopa nakama kiiramo nyeronya lao kongwalu palyuo Imambu Poo Pyasi maralyinyi pyambuya.
Nakama ingi koo palyuo, imbu singi manjo, imbumi kumuo, pii porakai lao, mendali koo koo lengepe yulu dupwa rekya lao nembaiapape.
Mendeme mende kando anjiki pyuo karo mona pau lao, Anatumi Koraisa keta nakamana koo dupwa kame sakaya dokona suu pyao nakamame yango mendena koo dupwana suu pyanyi pyano kara nalapape.
Nakama Anatunya mona nyingi wane wanakepe ingyuo karaminyi dokona banya yulu pinginyili pyuo pyuo karalapape.
Koraisa namwa mona reteyamo doko suu pyao yango mona reto karalapape. Baame mona retapala namwana lao kumuo maiyamopa rendamu kyaa keyange nyingi dopale Anatu nyiya.
Nakama kanda lyanolyano pyuo enda bangepe nyipuli nyipuli lao pii dopale Anatunya wambu yapasimi lao kararami ingilyande daa.
Mora pii koralepe kopyali piipi mee ketae giyalya giyana pyuope kapa laa napenge ingingi dupwana laa kaepala Anatu dokona sangyu lao karapengele ingilyamo.

Pii dake kinyi lao suu pyalapape. Wambu kando lyanolyano pingipi suu pingi karo petengepe yanengena bange nyerami dokona iki wangu lakapala suu pyao karengepe (doko Anatu kaepala bange wakale dupwa Anatu ingyuo panda maimisa pilyamo) dupwame nakama Koraisa Anatupana iso karenge panda dokona moyange nyii narami ingilyamo.
Lapome epapala mee kambumi pii nupi soo larami dupwana waso karalapape. Koo dopale pyuo karo kamba letaminyi dupwa keta Anatumi kote lara ingilyamo.
Dokona ingyuo nakamame nakamba role pyao kara nalapape.
Nakama wamba iminjiyamo dokona isa sulu sulu paeyo kareyaminyipape epapu Kurisene ingyapala Kamongona yanga paupau lenge dokona karaminyi. Dokona yanga paupau lengena wane wanakepe ingyuo karalapape.

Yanga paupau lenge dokome yulu keyangepe yulu rolaepe yulu angipi nyuo andanyi pyambwarasa pira. 
			Kamongome epe kandarali dupwa mana nyepala pyuo karalapape.
Iminjinginya yulu kalu kalu paeyo silyamo dupwana rekya lao karapala koo pilyaminyi dupwa nyuo pano serakamipape.
(Nakamba yulu koo yalu pyuo pilyaminyi dupwa polo lakalana dokopa elya nyerama ingilyamo.)
Bange peparae yanga paupau lenge panda seramo dokopa dopalendelamo lao angi panara.
Panasi dupwa yanga paupau lasi dokona ingyuo para. Dokona lao pii dopa lao pyasi palamo. Kumasi ingyuo luu palaminyi dupwa lenge rao sipuralapape dokopa Koraisame nakama keta neta ranyi pisinyale.
Dokona nakama apa pyuo kararama lao kandokondali pyuo karalapape. Kopyali ingya napala wambu angi ingyuo paeyo karalapape.
Epapu yuu gii koo epelyamo dokona mee kara napala yulu keyange pepenge dupwa pyuoko karalapape.
Kopyali ingyuo kara nalapape. Kamongome nakama pimili lao suu pilyamo dupwana sepala pyuo karalapape.
Waene ipwange langa andare nao kyawa sisingi bolombalo lanyi nembasasara naa nalapape. Naa napala Imambu Poo Pyasi nyepala palyuo simbwaramopa karalapape.
akama yango sukusa misi kenane dupwape Imambunya kenane dupwape pyao, Kamongo keta kenane dokome monarename piso nyuo ipwa kyukunalye maiyuo pena lao pyao karalapape.
Namwana Kamongo Yesu Koralsana kingi lao Rakane Anatu dokona kaeya nao bange yulupi peparaena suu pyao sangyu lao karalapape.
Koraisa wakasa dokona mona nembo wambu yango dolomana lungwa lungwarename ingyuo karalapape.
Nakamba enda dupwa Kamongo baa mupwa lao suu pyapala banya pii dupwa warombo soo petenge dokonako palyuo akalingi kando pipwape.
Koraisa baa Elyambu Pinginya mupwa ingyuo karamo doko suu pyao akali dupwa nakamana etenge dokona mupwa ingyuo karenge. Koraisa baa banya yango Elyambu Pingi doko Lete Wal Pyao Nyingi ingyaro karamo.
Elyambu Pingi doko Koraisana pii rape rape lao soo petenge doko suu pyao enda dupwa nakamana akalinginya yulu peparaena rape rape lao soo pyuo pisipape.
Yesu Koraisame Elyambu Pingi doko mona reto karapala reke lao kumuo paleya. Dokona ingyuo akali nakamana enda mona reto karalapape.
Koraisame Elyambu Pingi doko, banya pii keyangepe ipwapeme wate pyuo mondo lapala banya iki lao yapo nyiya.
Dopa pyuo Elyambu Pingi doko banya lenge kambu dorena rao kui kui lanyi pyambuo, nyisi yaku nayape pisi nao, pepo kareta kiminju palyuo bwualyambwuana pyuo paa naramopa range nyero lao piya.
Nakama akali dupwa rangena yongo mona reto karaminyi dokonako ingyuo nakamana enda mona reto karalapape. Dokona lao mendeme enda mona reto karara ramo doko baa range mona retarasa pira.

(Akali mendeme rangena yanenge awa naa nange. Rangena yanenge mondo lao elya pyuo karenge kandale. Namwa Koraisana yongo mendaki dokonakonde kara mano dokona Koraisame Elyambu Pingi mondo lanyi pyambungi.)
Dokona lao Anatunya pii pyasi doko, Akali dupwame nakamana endangi rakangepe yaki nyeraminyipa enda dokopa pakao pisirambinyipa nakamba mendaki ingyuo para letamo.
Pii andake yambe pyasi palamo doko Koraisapa dee Elyambu Pingi dokopana letamo lao suu pilyu.

Pii doko namwa wambu peparaeta keta lao palamo. Doko nakama akali peparae range mona reto karaminyi dokonako ingyuo nakamana enda mona reto karalapape. Dee enda dupwa nakama akalingi ketae pyambuo pisipape.
Nakama wane wanake dupwape Kamongo dokona lao endangi rakangepa laraminyili pyuo warombo soo pipape. Dopa pyuo pingi doko yulu rolae.
Anatunya mawa pii lasi dupwana mende doko, Endangi rakangepa dolapo angingyuo karambinyi lao suu pyaro karalapapc leya. Pii doko andake ingyuo mende pyakaramo dokona lao kaeyo leyasa piya.
Dokona moko minyuo pirami ramo kapa palyuo isa yuunya gii andarele karare ingilyamo lao makande pyuo pyasi palamo.
Endangi rakangepe dupwa nakamana wane wanakepe imbu singi nyakami nalapape. Mondo koo lao mana lamaiyuo Kamongona kingi lao ando pena larami.
Kendemande akali dupwa nakamana yulu pyakamaingi akali dokona mona mendare palyuo inyimungu mona nembo Koraisana kingi dokona lao pyuo karalapape.
Nakamame nakama kando kararami mange dokopa iki rae maimili lao pii nao, yulu pyuo dokopa Koraisana kendemande ingyuo Anatu pimili lao suu pilyamo doko monana manjo pipwape.
Mee akalinya yanenge dokona pilyu lao suu pyao piraminde daa. Kamongo dokona lao yulu andanyi nembo pipape.
Kendemande akali mee akalimipi yulu keyange pirami dokona Kamongo baame isingi manda manjo yano pyao kingi kiso jera lao suu pyao pipape.

Nakama numi dupwame, nakamana kendemande dupwa kando mona mendaki dokona palyuo pipape. Pii porakai pyalana pyuo laa nalapape. Nakama nakambanape Kamongo yake panda karenge dokome koo epengepe dokona suu pyaa nao karenge doko suu pyalapape.
Pii dake lao lumwa pyuo leto. Kamongopa pako karo banya poralnya renge doko nyepala kulisa palyuo karalapape.
Anatunya yanda pingi bange dupwa nyuo maralyaro karalapape. Dokome imambu koo doko panga seramo dokopa poral ingyapala mee kararami.
Namwa wambu yango sukusa dokona yanda pilyamande daa. lmambu koo malu yakena palenge dupwape mupwa dupwape iminjingi pandana numi dupwape pipya yanda pilyamano.
Dokona lao Anatunya yanda pingi peparae nyuo maralyapala yuu gii kwaeyaramo dokopa porayapala pyao pyalowa pyuo karo pao nenge rekya lapala kararami.
Dokona ingyuo rapa rapa pipape. Marapu wapungi dokona kinyi kinyinya renge doko wapuo karo, romba kyangalipi dorena yulu rolae doko puu saneme komau wapusi poral pee pyuo karo.
Manda rao nyingi waili pii keyange doko kimbu dokona pee piro karalapape.
Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingi konambe doko nyepala ketaele alya minyuo koo pinginya walaka isare paleta dupwa kunjinyi nembo karare.
Kyawa rarange kapame wasisi pyuo lete nyingi doko andu pipala, Imambunya wua gela Anatunya pii doko wakyaro karalapape.

lmambumi renge kuiyuo yuu peparae kaeya nao ateŋa lalapape. Anatu dokona ateŋa peparae sokondali pyuo karalapape. Dokona lao lenge rao karo, Anatunya wambu yapasi peparae dokona kaeya nao ateŋa lakamailapape.
Nakamame namba opetaeko ateŋa lakaraminyipa dokome namba waili pii keyange koko palenge dupwa pyongo pyaramopa kambu yaepapala eŋa nembo lao kararo.
Dokonako ingyuo namba waili pii lenge akali dokona puu malminyi karo. Nakama ateŋa lakarami dokopa namba eŋa nembo mona kumapala lao karapiii lao lalapape.
Namba apa pyuo karo akinde pyuo karene lao Tikikasa namwana yangonge mona retenge Kamongona yulu rolae pingi akali dokomeoko peparae rolo langira.
Dokonako lao baa nakama karaminyi dokona pena leto. Namwa apa pyuo karaminyi dokona langyuo mona minyarambwako karara.
Yangonemoo Rakane Anatu Kamongo Yesu Koraisapana mona kyuu lao singi rengepe dee mona reto karo Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingi rengepe nakama keta palena leto.
Namwana Kamongo Yesu Koraisa dokona yaki nyii nao mona reto karaminyi wambu keta Anatunya mona palyuo ipingi renge doko palenale lao leto.

Anatunya wambu peparae yuu Pilipal palenge Yesu Koraisa kapa ingingi lao suu pingi dupwape dee rapu pingipi nyisingi opetaepe nambwa Pole Timotipame Yesu Koraisana yulu pyakamingi akali dolapo nakama yako letambano.
Namwana Rakange Anatu Kamongo Yesu Koraisapame mona keyange palyuo ipingi rengepe mona kyuu lao singi rengepe nakama keta palena lao letambano.
Yuu peparae nakama lao suu pyapala nambana Anatu kando sangyu lao karo.
Yuu peparae Anatumi nakama nyisakana lao ateŋa lao rae maiyuo karo.
Wambape dakepape nakamame waili pii boo pyao lao namba nyisokondali pyuo karami dokona rae mailyu.
Anatumi kanda soo nakama keta yulu keyange piyamo doko kare kare soo pyuo pao Yesu Koraisana yuu gii pyaka seramo dokopa pyuo otara doko namba silyu.

Nambame yuu peparae nakamana lao suu pyale pyuo karo. Dokona lao rolae ingyuo nakama kondalyo. Waili pii keyange dokona lao kote leyaminyipape nambame pii keyange doko raeyo penale lao roleyo gii dokonape dee dakepa puu jiminyi karowape nakamame namba yaki nyii napala Anatumi yulu jiya dokona namba role pyao piyamioko.
Yesunya kondange renge dokome namba pyapyamopa nakama kandowane lao suu pyao kinyi kondo karapala letene lao Anatu baa kandapyamo leto.
Nakama suu pyao ateŋa lakalyo. Ateŋa lao dokopa nakamana mona retenge doko kamame ando pulyuo paramopa nakama soo gisapala suu pingi keyange palyuo pyuo kararami lao lakalyo.
Dopa pyuo dokona nakama range keyange doko anjuku lao yapalyuo nyerami. Enakana Yesu Koraisa dee eparamo dokopa nakama keta koo wakale wakale dupwa peparae pali nara.
Renge rolae keyange dupwa Yesu Koraisa keta iki sipurao epenge dupwa peparae nakama keta palyuo simbwanale leto. Nakama keta palira ramo doko Anatunya kingi ketae pyambuo lakando palirasa pira.
Yangonemoo nakama selapa lao leto. Namba randa jiminyi renge dokona lao waili pii keyange doko raeyo pelyamo.
Doko yanda singi peparae kiŋinya anda rapu pyuo karenge dupwape dee menge dupwa peparaeme namba Yesu Koraisana kendemande akali karapusi anda palyuo karo doko nakama silyaminyi.
Namba karapusi kareyono dokome nambana Kurisene yango malu dupwa Kamongo dokona lao mona poralnyi pyambuya. Mona poralnyi pyambuyamo dokome paka napala Anatunya pii lao karaminyi.

Lapome nambana kingi londe sipyamo dokona yango palyapala namba nyuo isa palyalana dokona Yesu Koraisana pii lao karaminyi doko silyu. Dee lapome suu pingi keyange palyuo renge keyange dupwana lao karaminyi.
Dupwa namba mona retapala waili pii dokona iki lao karamisa pilyamo. Waili pii keyange isa paa nana lao Anatumi namba keta yulu andake doko retelyamo.
Wambu menge dupwa Yesu Koraisana waili pii keyange kyambo lele lao nakama rangena kingi andapyali lao letaminyi. Doko namba karapusi dokona moŋo andake jimwali lao lamisa pilyamo.
Kwao letaminyi dokona pii mende pali nara. Doko larami panda keyange ingyuo larami doko Koraisana pii polo lamanale. Yesu Koraisana lao pii wakale wakale letaminyi doko namba rae mailyu.
Nakama ateŋa lakao karaminyisa Yesu Koraisana Imambu namba nyisaramopa kiiramo pasi kararo doko range silyu. Renge dokona lao rae maiyuo kararoko.

Namba Yesunya yulu pyakamingi dokona yake nyii nao poraiyuo karapuli lao suu pilyu. Suu pyao dokopa yuu peparaepe dee angi yuu gii dakepape namba poraingi renge palyuo pyoko pyoko laramo karapuli yaka. Namba range Yesu keta pyamaiyuo kararonopa lete kararope kumuowape dokona pii mende daa. Koraisana kingi ketae palipyali lao dokona iki suu pyao karo.
Dokona lete parono renge doko akisi? Namba lete kararo ramo doko Yesu Koraisana arapu dokona kararo dee namba kumaro ramo doko renge keyange mende kando nyero ingilyamo.
Dopako pyuo namba isa yuu dakena yulu keyange pyuo lete karalu kararo ramo doko anjuku doko mupwa lao see nalyo. Dokona lao suu pingi lama palamo.
Laparaena keyange ingyuo pelyamo lao suu pyao karo. Isa panda dakena yaki nyepala Koraisapa role pyao kararo doko mupwa lao suu pilyu.
Doko keyange lao suu pilyu doŋo kuma napala nakamana reke lao pyuo kararo dokona renge andake mende palamo.

Renge andake dokona suu pyao kumungi kata dokona walya lao paa naro. Nakama role pyao karo nakamana Kurisene yulu dokona andanyi pyambuo nakama rae maiyuo pupwale lao yulu pyuo kararo doko range silyu.
Namba dee kamba nakama keta range eparono dokopa nakama namba kando rae maiyuo nyepala Yesu Koraisana kingi ketae pyambuo lakando piramilyamo.

Koraisana waili pii keyange letamuli pyuo dokoko iki pyuo karalapape. Namba kandala eparonopape epa naronopape nakama mona mendaki palyuo suu pingi mendaki suu pyao waili pii doko kapa andena lao poraiyuo pirami doko langyaraminyi sero.

Nakamana nyisu petenge dupwa kando paka napala mona kuki palyuo karalapape. Nakambame nakama kandapala nakama anamasi minya napala koo keta parami doko soo manji nyerami. Anatumi nakama nyisaramopa nyisu petenge dupwa pyuo anamasi minyarami ingilyamo.
Anatu baa mona keyange palyuo ipingi dokome Yesu Koraisana yulu pyakarami lao yulu jiya. Joo dokopa Yesu baa kapa ingingi lao suu pyarami doko iki daa. Baa reke lao randa nyeramiko.

Namba waili pii dokona reke lao yanda pyuo karo dokona nakama opetae yandako pirama. Namba wamba yanda pyuo kareyo doko dake mendaki dokoreko. Dee mendaki dokonako epapu dakepa pyuo karo doko nakama silyaminyi.

Nakama Yesu Koraisana arapu dokona karami dokome poralnyi pyambulyase? Banya mona retenge dokome nakamana mona poralkalyase? Nakama Imambupa role pyao yalya kando karamisi? Nakama mendali mendali anjiki pyuo mona reto pyuo karamisi?
Dopa pyuo piyande kande doko suu pingi mendakinya suu pyao mona mendaki palyuo rale rale pii nao nambana rae maingi renge doko andanyi pyambwarami lao poralyuo langilyu.

Rango nao range namba keta palipyali lao dee suu pingi koo suu pyao range ketae pyambuo lakando pii narami. Namba range wakasa lao masa nao wambu wakale dupwa mupwa lao suu pyao inyimungu karo mendali kondo kondo lao kararami.
Nakama rangena ikinya lao suu pyaa nao mendeme mendena kando nyiso pirami.
Yesu Koraisa suu piyamuli pyuo suu pyaro karalapape langilyu.
Yesu baa Anatu angiko ingyuo karenge. Baa rangeme sisu lao Anatu yale ingyuo karapuli lao suu pyaa naya.
Baa range banya peparae yaki nyuo kaepala kendemande akali ingyuo karapala mee isa wambu dokore isa komba pyao epeya. Epapala baa mee isa akali ingyuo ando kareya.
Yesu baa akali kukiŋi lao inyimungu karo Anatu dokona warombo sepala baa leyamuli pyuo kumuya. Kinyi baa isa mamandona kumuo paleya.
Renge dokona lao Anatumi baa minya lyuo nyiya. Anatumi minyalyuo nyepala baa kingi andake maiyamo doko kingi doloma nyuo isa palyiyasa piya.
Yesunya kingi dokona lao wambu peparaepe imambupi yake pandape isa yuu dakenape dee isa yuu dorena palenge dupwapeme wapambu pii pyaro piso banya kingi lakandarami.
Lakando dokopa wambu peparaeme Yesu Koraisa doko baa Kamongo doko lao kararami. Dopa pyuo lakandarami dokome Rakange Anatunya kingi ketae pyambuo parasa pira.

Nambana puu minyingi dupwa yuu peparae namba nakama pipya role pyao kareyonopa nakama warombo siyami kande. Doko suu pyao epapu dakepa namba nakama pipya kara nalyamano doŋo nambana pii warombo serami ramo doko ama keyange wakasa ingyara. Neta pasaramaŋa lao pakame kumuo walu walu lao Anatunya Imambunya yulu dokona pyuoko karalapape.
Anatumi nakama keta yuu peparae waa waa karanyi pyambuo dee banya renge dupwana warombo serami lao pingi.
Yuu peparae mumu lao lalya lao pii napala rae maiyuo karalapape.

Dopa pirami ramo doko nakama koo pii nao poo pyasi ingyuo kararami. Nakama Anatunya wane wanakepe koo isa palya nange dupwa yuu dakena wambu koo pyuo rango nao karenge dokona role pyao palirami ingilyamo. Nakamame bui yake dokona rao karenge dopale ingyapala,

waili pii wambu lete wal pyao nyingi doko lamaiyuo karalapape. Dopa pyuo pirami ramo doko Koraisa epara yuu gii dokopa nakamana lao suu pyao rae maipala lakandaro. Dokome nambame yulu andake pyakayono doko mee ingyuo paa naya lao pano lasaka pira.

Nakamana Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingi doko rendamu pingi kiso Anatu maingi dopale ingyuo pelyamo. Doko nambana ranjama kulimbwaraminyipa nakama suu pingi keyange pale pale Anatu dokona para ingilyamo. Dopa pira ramo doko namba rae mairu dokona nakama opetae rae maiyuo karalapape.
Mendaki dopaleko ingyuo nakama opetae rae mairaminyi dee namba opetae nakama pipya rae mairamako.
Kamongo Yesumi nyisaramopa nakama karaminyi dokona Timoti pena laro ingilyamo. Timoti baame nakamana yulu dokona lao langyuo jeramo dokopa nambana mona poralnyi pyambwara.
Namba nakama mona retapala suu pyaro karo doko suu pyao baako mendeke ingyuo pelyamo.
Wambu menge dupwa nakama rangena iki suu pyao Yesu Koraisana yulu dokona rae mai nao karaminyi.

Nakama Timotinya yulu wambo kandapala baa akali keyange dokona nakama range soo gisilyaminyi. Timotipa nambapa ikinyingi rakangepa dopale karambano dokome waili pii dokona reke lao yulu mendare role pyao pingi doko soo gisilyaminyiko.
Dokona lao namba keta apa pira iao soo nyepala aopa nakama karaminyi dokona pena larolyamo lao suu pyao karo.
Kamongome nyisaramopa namba range rengya usale eparolyamo lao silyu.

Namwana yangonge Ipaporaltasa nambapa role pyao yulu andake pyuo waili piinya lao kareyamba. Doko nakamame namba nyiso Ipaporaitasa jiyaminyipa nakamana wai pii minyuo papyuo kareya. Doko baa nakama keta pena laro lao suu piyu.
Baa nakama peparae kandapuli yaka lao letamo. Nakama baa anga pyalyamo lao siyami. Siyaminyi dokona baa mona randalyamo.
Kinyi baa anga andake piyamo repeta kumuyamopape Anatumi baa kondapala nyisiya. Baa dokona iki sakao kondayande daa. Baa namba opetaeko kondapala namba kyawa minyiya.
Dokona lao nakama rae wakasa mairami lao baa nakama kandala ipyali lao leto. Kandala eparamo dokopa namba mona kenda pii nara.
Baa Kurisene akali yango dokona lao rae maiyuo yako lao kando nyelapape. Akali baa yale dupwa opetaeko yako lao lakanaalapape.
Nakama rangeme nanesale karapala namba nyisalana saka nayaminyi dokona baame nyiso pyakaya. Doko Yesu Koralsana yulu dokona reke lao baa kumara repe ingiya.

Nambana Kurisene yango dupwa Kamongo dokome rae maingi renge nakama keta jinya leto. Pii wambo pyao reteyo doko dee kamba pyao jero ramo dokopa kapa ingyara. Dee kambako serami ramo doko nakama porainyi pyambwara ingilyamo.
Doko wambu koo pingi dupwa waso karalapape. Akali nakama yanenge kunjo kalomo karaminyi dupwa nakama koo suwa ingyuo kopetame pilyaminyi.

Anatunya Imambu namwa nyisilyamopa Anatu dokona mona kando kingi lenge. Namwa Koraisa Yesunya arapu dokona karapala rae mailyamano. Dokona lao yanenge kolomasi angingyuo peyama. Doko nakama daa. Namwa yanengena yulu ketae iki suu pyaa nalyamano.
Yanengena ketae yulu dokome kiiramo nyingi pili namba wambo kiiramo nyisi karapuli doko silyu.

Dokona ingyuo namba mandeyaminyi koro mendaki epo papeyamopa namba yanenge pyakepanyi nembakayami. Namba Isaraele akali Benjamene rara dokona ingyuo karo. Namba Ipuru akali angi doko. Namba Parisi akali ingyapala Juu wambunya Mawa Pii dokona moko minyuo kareyo.

Dopa pyuo Juu wambunya Mawa Pii mona reto rae maiyuo karapala Kurisene wambu dupwa randa maiyuo kareyo. Namwa Mawa Pii dupwa moko minyuo warombo soo karo rolae ingyuo karenge pili doko namba keta koo pali napyali.
Wamba isa bange ama keyange nyelana suu piyu dusipa Yesu Koraisana kingi reke lao dakepa mee kilya kandanyi nembelyo.

Bange dusipa iki daa. Bange peparae mee ingyuo pelyamo lao soo nyepala mende mupwa wakasa keyange ingyuo pelyamo dokona lao poralyuo suu pilyu. Mende keyange mupwa wakasa doko nambana Kamongo Koraisa Yesunya soo gisilyu renge doko. Banya reke lao bange peparae neta nembo oteyo. Yesu Koraisana arapu dokona karapuli yaka lao isa bange peparae isa pena leto.

Dopa piru ramo dokopa namba Yesu Koraisapa pakalu pakao pakarosa pira. Namba range sipurapala Mawa Pii dupwa warombo sepala dokome rolae ingyuo paa nayo doko kandelyo. Dakepa Yesu Koraisa kapa ingingi lao suu pyapala rolae ingyuo karo. Rolae pingi renge doko Yesu kapa ingingi lao suu pingi dokona Anatumi joo karamo.

Doloma kaepala namba Yesu Koraisa iki suu pyao karapuli yaka. Baa sipurao peyamo dokome porainya renge neta epeya doko namba keta palipyali yaka lao leto. Baa randa nyiyamo doko suu pyao namba opetae randa nyuo baa kumuyamo doko suu pyao namba opetae kumalana leto.
Dopa pirunu dokopa namba lete sipurao paro doko soo gisilyu.

Nambame Yesu Koraisana yulu rolae angingyuo pyuo karo laa nalyo. Dee koo mende namba keta pali nalyamo laronde daa. Koraisa Yesumi namba banya ingyuo nyiyamo dokona lete paro doko nyipuli lao kyawame suu lao pilyu.

Yangonemoo namba Yesunya make dokona kando nyepeyo lao poralyuo suu pyaa nalyo. Namba suu pingi mendaki lao suu pilyu doko yulu wamba dupwa kame soo kaepala namba range poralyaro dokome rengyana yulu nyerono dokona kando pyuo parowale.
Bange keyange wmi pyuo nyingi doko nyelana namba make dokona rolae kanda kanda makando pelyo. Anatumi Yesu keta yake panda dorena ipupwape lao kee leya bange keyange dokonasa leto.
Namwa peparae Kurisene poral dupwame suu pingi mendaki palyamanale. Nakama lapo suu pingi wakale palira ramo doko Anatumi monarena lao rolakaya.
Dopa pyuo pira ramo namwa yulu rolae wambo palenge dokona moko minyiyama doko suu pyao epapu dopako pyuo moko minyarama ingilyamo.
Yangonemoo namba yulu piyu dupwa kaeya nao makande minyuo pyuo karalapape. Yulu rolae lasaka piyama dokona moko minyuo pelyaminyi dupwa kando mana nyuo pipwape.

Yuu wamba namba yuu malu mee nakama mana langingi kandale doko dee epapu dakepa kamba ee ipwange nyuo lao langilyu. Wambu malu mee yulu koo pilyaminyi dokome Yesu Koraisa isa mamandona kumuo paleya dokona nakama yanda pimwal ingyuo pelyaminyi.
Anatu kaepala nengepe yanengena bange dupwape mupwa lao suu pilyaminyi. Dokona lao nakama Satanena panda parami. Nakama elyange yulu wakale wakale dupwana iki poralyuo suu pyao karenge.
Kamongo Yesu Koraisa namwana Lete Wal Pyao Nyingi doko yake panda piso namwa isa nyela eparamo dokona mona kare kare isaro petamano. Namwana yuu muru yake panda silyamo.

Anatumi namwana isa wambunya yongo kwaelyamo dupwa kaepala banya yongo yanga paupau lenge dokona makande minyuo alowa pyuo jera. Banya poralnya renge isa bange peparae nyuo isa palyingi dokome kapa pira.

Nambana Kurisene yango dupwa. Nakama poral ingyuo Kamongona arapu dokona dapale ingyuo karalapape lao langilyu. Namba nakama mona reto kondalyo. Namba keta yulu keyange pyuo pisaminyi dokona rae wakasa maiyuo nakama lakandelyo.
Enda Yotiapa Sindikipa nakamba Kamongona arapu dokona Kurisene kakingi ingyuo karalapape lao poraiyuo langilyu.

Dokona ingyuo nambana yulu role pyao pingi akali embame enda lama dolapo nyisakare. Enda dolapo porayapala namba role pyao yulu andake waili pii dokona raeyo lao kareyama. Kelemene dee nambana yulu mendare pingi akali lapo Anatunya letena renge buku dokona kingi pyasi palamo dupwa opetae waili pii raeyo lao kareyamako.
Kamongona arapu dokona karo yuu peparae rae maiyuo karalapape. Rae wakasa maiyuo karo pipwape lao dee kamba leto.
Nakama wambu yango dupwa kando rambi rambi lao kararami. Kamongo baa repeta usale epara ingilyamo.
Mona nembo kara nalapape. Nakama yano piramo kararami dokona nakamana ateŋa dokome Anatu piso selapape. Dopa pyuo baa piso soo dokopa mona kare kare sangyu lao pipape.
Koraisa Yesupa pako kararami dokopa Anatunya mona kyuu lao singi renge mee wambu dupwa soo gisa nange dokome nakamana mona andape suu pingi dokonape kame pyuo minyara.

Pii renge dakeme lao oto leto. Yulu keyange wambu kando epe singi dupwana iki suu pyao karalapape. Angi dupwape, suu pingi rolaepe yulu rolaepe koo pali nange dupwape au pisi dupwape mona palenge yulu dusipa iki suu pyale pyale pyuo karalapape.
Yulupi piipi namba keta mana nyiyami dupwa iki pyuo karalapape. Anatu mona kyuu lao singi renge jingi dokome nakama pipya role pyao karara.

Namba Kamongopa pako karo renge dokona rae andake maiiyu. Nambame nakama yuu wamba rekya lapala epeyo kande doko suu pyao ene alembole bange lapo nyiso jimi. Nakama namba kame soo kaeyami lao laa nalyo. Nakama nanesale karapala bange lapo jerami kata mende pali naya.
Namba pendewa ingyuo karapunu dokona pii mende daa. Bange mendasipa iki silyamosa namba mee rae maiyuo karenge.

Namba wamba yuu lapo lopo karo, yuu lapo bange malu siyasa kareyo dokona renge mende mana nyiyu. Doko lopo karowape sikya piramopa karowape bange sera panda bange see naramopa namba mee rae maiyuo kararo ingilyamo.
Koraisa baame namba porainyi pyambuyasa yulu peparaena lao mona kuki palyuo karenge.
Namba randa nao kareyo dokona nakama nyiso yulu ama keyange wakasa piyami leto.

Yuu wamba kanda soo waili pii lamaiyuo karo dokopa yuu Masetonia karapala mendasa peyo. Dokopa nakama Elyambu Pingi wambu Pilipal karenge dupwame iki namba nyisiyami doko range silyaminyi. Namba kapa kareyonopape randa nyiyunupape nakamame iki namba nyiso kareyami.
Namba Tesalonaika kareyo yuu gii dokopa yuu mendaki iki nyisapala kaeya nayami. Dee kambako nyisiyami.
Nakama bange jilyaminyi renge dokona iki rae mai nalyo. Nakamana yulu keyange wambo yake panda para lyasili. Bange malu konda pyuo jiminyi dokona kapa karo.

Bange malu kamame konda pyuo jiminyi dokona kapa karapala sangyu lao pepa dake isingi pyao jilyu. Ipaporaitasa baame nakamana bange jiminyi dupwa peparae namba nyipunu dokome epapu mende namba yangya nara ingilyamo. Anatu kyaa pyuo rendamu pingi mailyaminyipa kando nyuo rae maiyuo pingi doko.
Nambana Anatumi baa bange malu retenge dokome nakama bange yangyaramo dupwa peparae Koraisa Yesu keta isingi jera.
Namwana Rakange Anatu dokona lao kingi ketae pyambuo lakando karalu kararama. Doko kinyi.
Anatunya wambu Koraisa Yesu keta karenge dupwa peparae yako lao leto. Kurisene yango lapo nambamoo pipya role pyao karamwano dupwame opetae yako letaminyiko.
Anatunya wambu dae petenge dupwa peparaemoome dee kiŋi akalinya yulu pyakamyuo karenge dupwamoome yako letaminyi.
Kamongo Yesu Koraisana mona keyange paiyuo ipingi renge nakama peparae keta palena lao leto.
Anatumi masiyamuli pyuo namba Pole Koraisa Yesunya aposele inginyi pyambuyamopa namba namwana yangonge Timotipame

nakama Kolosi dokona Anatunya wambu namwana yangonemoo ingyuo Koraisa keta baa maso minyuo karaminyi dokona pepa peyakalyambano. Namwana Rakane Anatumi nakama keta mona keyange palyuo ipingi rengepe mona kyuu lao singi rengepe retakana lao yako letambano.

Nakama Koraisa Yesu kapa ingingi lao suu pyapala Anatunya wambu yango mona maiyuo karaminyi doko soo karamano. Renge dokona namwana Kamongo Yesu Koraisana Rakane Anatu dokona kaeya nao ateŋa letamano.

Anatunya waili pii keyange rolae doko kanda soo sepeyaminyipa keyange keta palirami doko soo gisiyami. Yake pandana bange keyange sakaiyamo dokona mona kare kare karapala Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyapala wambu yango mona reto karaminyi.

Waili pii keyange nakama siyami dokoko epapu yuu muu dupwana raeyo pelyamo. Anatumi mona keyange palyuo ipingi renge doko angi soo nyepeyaminyi mange dokopa piso epo pii doko nakama keta andapala jingi ingyuo lyingi. Nakama keta jingi lyiya dopako pyuo wambu peparae keta epapu jingi lyilyamo.
Akali Ipaporasa namwa role pyao Koraisana yulu doko namwa nyiso pyuokondali pyuo karamo. Baa wamba nakama mana lamaiyuo karapala epeya.
Imambu nakama nyisiyamopa wambu yango mona retelyaminyi doko namwa langiya.
Renge dokona sepala dokopa piso epo yuu peparae kaeya nao ateŋa lakalyamano. Nakama mona angi palipala imambunya yulu dupwa soo gisapala dokome

Anatu nakama pimili lao suu pilyamo dupwa kando nyeparami dokona loma sakao petamano. Kando nyepala dokopa Kamongome nakama yulu pimili lao rae mairali dupwa pyuo kararami. Nakama Anatunya yulu dupwa soo nyepala yulu keyange doko jingi keyange lyingi dopale pyuo kararami.
Dokonako ingyuo banya poralnya renge wakasa dokome nakama porainyi pyambwaramopa randa malu eparamo dokopa mona kuki palyuo rae maiyuo kararami.

Anatumi banya wambu dupwame nyerami lao banya sii pingi panda dorena bange keyange retakaya. Nakama banya wambu ingyuo petaminyi dupwa role pyao mokwa soo nyerami lao kata wapwakaya. Dokona Rakane kando sangyu lao karalapape.
Baame namwa iminjinginya kareyama dokona neta nyepala banya Ikinyingi mona retenge doko keta namwa banya isingi panda dorena kareya.
Baako keta namwa kiiramo nyepala namwana koo dupwa nyuo kame sakaya.
Namwa Anatu kapa kanda nange dokona Koraisa baa Anatu yale isa komba pyao karamo baame wasiyamo dupwa peparaena mupwa ingyuo karamo.

Baa ketako yake bange dee isa bange dupwapeko wasisi silyamo. Bange kandenge dee mendeme kanda nangepe Imambu dupwape kiŋi dupwape kamongo dupwape gapomane dupwape baa ketako pyuo ingiyamopa banyako silyamo.
Bange peparae ene wasapa nayamopa baa wambo ingyuo karaiu karenge. Dee baameko bange peparae serali panda dupwana reto simuo pyao minyaro karamo.

Elyambu Pingi doko banya yongo ingingi. Baa dokona akali kyawa ingyuo karamo. Banya yongo dokoko baa dokona piso renge kniyuo epeya. Kumapala sipurao lete parami dupwana baa kanda soo lete epeya. Epo baa peparaena mupwa ingyapala karamo.
Anatumi suu piyamuli pyuo banya Ikinyingi Yesu baa range ingyuo karengenyili pyuo baa keta maralyiyamopa isa komba pyao nyiya.
Anatumi yuu muu peparaena rekya lasi siyamo doko banya Ikinyingi keta dee nyuo mendakiya. Yesumi isa mamandona ranjama kuli mbuo kumuo paleya dokome Anatumi yake yuupi peparae baa keta sukusa nyiya.
Nakama suu pingi kwaenge dokome ene alembole yulu koo pyuo kareyaminyipa Anatupa yanda pimwalyuo rekya lao wakale ingyuo kareyami.

Kareyaminyipape Koraisame isa wambunya yanenge nyepala kumuo jiyasa Anatumi nakama pipya kando nyiya. Kando nyiyamo dokome nakama banya lenge kambu dorena koo keta pali nao yapasi keyange ingyuo kararami.

Dokona lao nakamana kapa ingingi lao suu pingi doko yake nyii napala poralyuo karalapape. Yesu epapala keyange pyakara lao waili pii keyange doko yake nyii nao mona kare kare karalapape. Pii doko wambu yuu muu dupwana peparae silyaminyi. Doko namba Poleme pii dokonako kendemande ingyuo lao karo.
Namba nalcama nyisapusa randa nyilyu dokome rae maiyuo nyilyu. Elyambu Pingi doko Koraisana yongo ingilyamo dokona lao baa randa nyiya. Randa nyiyamo pinjingi koko pyasi doko namba nyilyu.
Anatumi banya pii peparae langirono dokona lao namba Elyambu Pinginya isingi akali lao rombo palyiya.
Pii doko kal wamba yalu pisi singi doko epapunya banya wambu dupwa keta panasi silyamo.

Anatumi banya suu pingi neta renge yalu pisi doko, banya wambupi Juu daa rara wakale dupwape keta nyuo panara lao suu piya. Pii wambo yalu piyamopa see nayami doko Koraisa nakama keta palamo. Dokome Anatunya yanga paupau lenge panda nyerami.

Dokona namwa wambu peparae Koraisana kingi boo pyao lao singi renge wakale wakale dupwa mana lamailyamano. Dokome nakama mendaki mendaki lao mona palenge wambu ingyuo Yesupa pakao Anatunya lenge kambu dorena kararami.
Yulu doo iki pinya lao suu pyapala Koraisana poralnya renge dokome namba paka pyao sipyamo yulu andake doko randa nao pyuo karo.
