Nambame nakamape Leotosia rangepe dee wambu lapo namba kanda nange yuu wakalena petengepe dupwana lao yulu andake pyakamyuo karo leto.

Nakama mona palipala mona retenge dokome nyuo mendakyaramo kararami lao yulu andake pilyu. Anatunya singinya renge dokope suu pingi dupwape Koraisa keta wua nanga boro kumuo yalu pili laro karamo. Nakama pyuo karo dokopa renge dupwa soo nyuo mona kumapala kararami.
Wambu lapome epo pii keyange ingili lao nupi soo langiraminyi dupwana waso karalapape lao wambo langilyu.

Namba nakama pipya angingyuo kara nalyo doŋo imambunya yulu dokona ingyuo nambana mona dorena dolo nakama pipa karo. Nakama Koraisa kapa ingingi lao suu pyapala mee kana para para ingyaro karaminyi doko kandapala namba rae mailyu.
Nakama Koraisa Yesu nakamana Kamongo lao kando nyiyami dokona baapa role pyao karalapape.
Namwa Kurisene yulu mana langiyama dokona minyuo pingi pyapala ando karo mona yaepapala Anatu lakando karalapape.
Nakama isa akalinya pii rambaye dokona kyambo laraminyi sisaramano lao waso karalapape. Akali dopale dokome Koraisana mana nyii napala isa imambu koo dupwana mana nyepala pyuo karaminyi.
Koraisa Yesumi wambunya yongo maralyuo karo, Anatu angi karengenyili pyuo kareya.
Nakama baapa pakao Anatunya wambu angi ingyapala karaminyi. Baa porai dokome yake panda isa pandarena simuo pyao minyaro karamo.

Isa wambunya yanenge kalomengenyili pyuo kalomapala karaminde daa. Koraisame nakamana yongome koona wangu lakao karamo dokona rekya lao nyiyamosa karaminyi. Nakama baa keta yongo kalomanyi nembenge dopale karaminyi pilyamo.

Nakama bapitisimo nyiyami kande doko Koraisapa role pyao malu pisi siyami. Dee Anatumi Yesu kumasi siyamo dokona lete minyalyuo nyiya doko baa poral kapa ingingi lao suu piyami dokome nakama bapitisimo nyiyami dokopa Koraisapa role pyao minyalyuo nyiyasa piya.

Nakama yulu koo pyuo karo mona anda awali lao kalomo rekya lanyi nembapa nayami dokome nakama kumasi ingyuo kareyami. Kumasi ingyuo kareyaminyipape Anatumi namwana koo dupwa nyuo kame sakapala nakama Yesupa role pyao lete minyalyuo nyiya.
Juu wambunya mawa pii malu pyasi paleyamo dupwame namwa kimbwalya kimbwana piyamo kareyama. Dokona Anatumi mawa piro kareyamo dusipa nyepala isa mamando dokona pirimi pyao mee inginyi nembeya.
Koraisame isa mamando dokona mupwa dupwape imambu dupwape anamasi minyuo puu maipala yuu aupa lao anda lanyuo epeyamopa wambu peparae kandeyami.
Dokona ingyuo mawa pii malu waso retarami ingya nalyamo. Nenge ipwape nao dokonape Kurisimase lyuope nenge andake yangowape Koro Petenge yuu giipi dusipana lao mawa pii mende palya narami ingilyamo.
Dupwa angi mende daa. Imambu mee ipwa jimi jiminya kandenge dopale. Angi doko kulisa palyuo kandarami doko Koraisa karamo.
Wambu lapome kombeyame kandaramo dupwana arome pyao nakamba wangu lakapala aŋala dupwana kingi lao, isa wambunya suu pingi dokome range ketae nembapala karenge dupwame nakama nyuo isa palya nanale.
Wambu dopale doko Koraisa keta role pyao mendakinya ingyuo kara nange. Koraisa baa kyawa ingilyamopa yongo peparae minyala minyala pao karenge. Dokome Anatu suu pyaramuli pyuo andara.
Nakama Koraisapa role pyao kumuyami dokopa imambu koo nakama rambu lasi kareyami dupwana kingi rekya leya. Dokona akipamo mee isa wambu pinginyili pyuo pyuo karamisi?
Kingimi minyanda nao, angi naa nao, dee warenda nao waso karalapape lao karaminyi dokona nakama akipamo warombo sepala waso karamisi?
Mana nyilyaminyi doko mee isa wambu dupwana mana nyepala pyuo karaminyi. Waso karaminyi bange dupwa isa bangeŋe isa para ingilyamo.

Wambu lapome yulu dopale keyange suu piyaminyipape aŋalana kingi laope rangena yongo randa maiyuope inyimungu karo pyuo karaminyi yulu dupwame yangengena yulu koo pundange dupwa nyuo anamasi minya nara ingilyamo.
Emba Koraisapa lopo epasi dokome Koraisa baa Anatunya kingi rolaerena nyuo kareyamopa karamo dorena kandaro karape.
Isa bange dupwa mona reta napala yake bange dupwa suu pyao karape.
Emba kumiinyisa embena imambu doko Koraisapa Anatu dokona yalu pisi karamo.
Koraisa baame namwana angi letena renge ingyuo karamo. Rengya baa panembena epara dokopa nakama opetae Kamongona neta renge yulu dokona role pyao ingyuo para.

Pamuku yulupi suu pingi koope yongona yulupi pundao yuu pingipi bange nyipuli nyipuli lao suu pingipi nakamana yongo pundapala pilyamo dupwa anamasi minyalapape. Bange nyipuli nyipuli lao suu pingi wambu dupwa Anatu kaepala dusipa mupwa lao maso minyuo kararami ingilyamo.
Koo dopale pyuo karo kamba letaminyi dupwa keta Anatumi kote lara ingilyamo.
Nakama wamba wambu yulu koo pingi dupwa roIe pyao paleyami dokopa koo dopale pinya wangu lakapala pyuo kareyamipya.
Imbwuangepe ingi pungipi nengepe kanda sikya sikyu lengepe ingi koo manjo lalya lengepe mokwalipi lengepe dupwa nembo kaeyalapape.
Nakama yulu wambarae kaeya nao pingi dupwa nembapala enenge ingyuo karaminyi dokona yango sukusa kyambo lao kara nalapape.
Anatumi nakama wambu enenge ingyuo wasiya. Wasiyamopa nakama baa yale enenge ingyuo kisokwanyi pyambwalana pyuo karamo dokome banya dupwa soo giso parami.

Yulu enenge dokome Juu Girikipi ingyuo kingi see nara. Yanenge kalomengepe kaloma nangepe rara wakale wakalepe kingi mende see nalyamo. Dee kendemandepe mee karengepe ingya nara. Koraisa baa keta peparaena keta karengeoko dokome wakale mende yangya nara.

Nakama Anatu rangena rombo palyuo kaeyasi wambu karaminyi. Baame nakama mona retapala rangena lao rombo palyiya. Dokona lao nakama wambu yango kando sakapala anjiki pyuo karo range inyimungu kararami. Mee pau lao maka nao pyuo karalapape.

Nakama yango sukusa mendali nyiso nyiso pyuo dee yango sukusa pii paleya kande dokopa nyuo kame sakamyuo karalapape. Kamongome nakamana koo dupwa kame sakaya dokona suu pyao yango mendali keta dopako pipwape.
Yulu keyange dupwa nyuo pee pipala mona retenge renge dokome ketae nenge nyuo wapurami dokopa keyange ingyuo para.

Koraisana mona kyuu lao singi renge nyerami lao Anatumi nakama yongo mendaki dokona nyuo kiminjiya. Dokona mona anda kyuu lao see nara ramo doko koo pipulyamo lao soo pakana palyuo kararami. Dokona lao yuu peparae rae maiyuo karalapape.
Koraisana pii nakamana mona anda dokona palyuo ando nyimbunya. Nakamana mona anda dokona Anatu sangyu lao misi kenane dupwape imambunya kenane dupwape ipwa kyukunalye maiyuo pena lao pyao karalapape.
Nakama yulu pyuope pii laope Kamongo Yesunya kingi dokona suu pyao pyuo karalapape. Pyuo karo dokopa Koraisa keta Rakane Anatu sangyu larami.
Etenge dupwa akalinyinya pii minyuo laraminyiii pyuo soo pisipwape. Dokopa Kamongona lenge kambu dokona rolae ingyuo sera.
Akalingi dupwa nakamana etene kondo karapala pau lao rapu pyuo karalapape.
Wanenge ikinyingipi dupwa nakama yuu peparae rakane endakinyipinya kambu moko minyuo pipape. Dokome Anatu rae mainyi pyambwara.
Nakama endangi rakangepeme nakamana wane wanakepe imbu singi manjinyi pyambwa naiapape. Pyambwarami ramo dokopa nakamana mona kendo inyimungu kararami.
Kendemande dupwa nakamana yulu pyakamingi akali dokona pii laramuli pyuo pipape. Lengeme kandamiii lao panga soo yulu pii nalapape. Kamongo dokona pakapala monarena rolo sero yulu rolae nembo pipape.
Yulu mende piyami kande dokona mona nyepala mee akalinya daa Kamongo dokona pyakamipusa pyaamo lao suu pyao poraiyuo pipape.
Embame yulu doko Kamongo Koraisana pipisa pilyamo. Dokona lao Kamongo keta yole nyerama lao selapape.
Dee yulu koo pilyaminyi dupwa yole kooko nyerami. Anatumi mee langa wambu yapalya yapana pyuo kara nange.
Akali andake dupwa nakamana Rapu Pingi yake panda karamo doko suu pyapala nakamana kendemande akali dupwa kando rolae nembo pipwape.
Ateŋa kaeya nao lao lenge rakaro karo Anatu kando sangyu lalapape.
Koraisana yalu pisi singi dupwa kapa boo pyao larami lao Anatumi kata wapwakanale lao ateŋa lakarami. Namba pii dokoko lao kareyonosa karapusi palyuo karo.
Pii yambe pyasi palamo doko mondo lao lalana lao suu pilyu dokona loma selapape.
Mee wambu pipa pii lao yulu pyuope dokOna kandOkOndali pyuo yulu nakama keta silyamo dupwana mondo koo lao pyuo karalapape.
Kurisene ingya nange dupwa kando pii keyange ingyuo rende pyuo lamairami dokopa epe soo parami. Wambu mendaki mendaki kando aki piinde keyange lamairu lao suu pyao karalapape.
Namwana mona retenge yangone Tikikasa baame Kamongona yulu role pyao pyuo karamo. Baa eparamo dokopa namba apa pyuo karene lao langira.
Baame namwa apa pyuo karamano lao dokona langyuo nakama mona porainyi pyambwaraŋa lao mapanyi peelyo.
Nambana mona retenge Onisimasa nakamana raiape dokonande yulu wangu lakao pingi doko role pyao epara. Anelapome nakama dae apande pilyamo lao langirambi.

Aritakasa nambapa karapusi anda palamo dokome yako letamoko. Wane mende Make baa akali Banapasana kingi baa opetae yako letamo. Banya yulu dupwa wambo langiyu kande doko baa nakambana anda kata epeya kande doko yako lao nyelapape.

Josua kingi mende Jasatasa lenge dokome opetae yako letamo. Mona kapu kyingi Juu akali rema dusipa iki nambamOO pipya Anatunya isingi yulu dokona suu pyao pyuo karaminyi. Nakama namba mona minyarambu nyiso pyuo karaminyi.

Koraisa Yesunya yulu pyakamaingi akali Ipaporasa baa nakamana ralape dokonandeme nakama yako letamo. Baame nakama porayapala suu pingi lama suu pyaa nao Anatu suu pyaramuli pyuo karo eŋa nembo karamili yaka lao yuu peparae Anatu kando loma sokonda koo pyako karamo.
Baame yulu andake pyuo nakamape dee Leotosia Irapolisa wambupi dolapona nyiso pyakalyamo doko range kando karo.
Namwana mona retenge dokota Luku Dimasapa nakambame yako letambinyiko.
Yuu Leotosia sukusa wambu dupwa yako lakalapape. Enda Nipape dee wambu banya anda misi lao elyambu pyuo petenge dupwape opetaeko yako lakalapape.
Pepa pase dake yaka lapala Leotosia Elyambu Pingi wambu dokona yaka lena lao maipwape. Dee Leotosia dokona pepa pase mende reto karaminyi doko nakama kame see nao nyepala range kandalapape.
Kamongome yulu jiyamo doko waso minyuo kando pyakamilyu lao soo piri lao akali Akipasa pii dake lamaiyakamipape.
Nambana kingi dake Pole lao pyanjilyimi pyanyi palyilyu. Namba puu maiyamisa kiimbasi peto kande. Anatumi mona keyange palyuo ipingi renge nakama keta palena lao yako leto.

Rakane Anatu, Kamongo Yesu Koraisapana Elyambu Pingi yuu Tesalonalka petenge wambu dupwa pepa dake namwa Polemoo Sallasa Timotimoo pyao jilyamano. Mona keyange palyuo ipingi rengepe mona kyuu lao singi rengepe nakama keta palena.
Namwame yuu peparae Anatu dokona sangyu lao karo nakama suu pyao kaeya nao ateŋa lakao petamano.

Namwana Rakane Anatu kando ateŋa lao dokopa nakamame Anatu kapa ingingi lao soo nyiyaminyi dokome yulu keyange piyami doko kame see nalyamano. Nakama Anatu mona reteyami dokona yulu poral piyami. Dopako pyuo namwana Kamongo Yesu Koraisa dee epara doko soo gisapala mona kare kare karaminyi. Dopa pyuo keyange pilyaminyi doko kame see napala ateŋa lakalyamano.
Yangonemoo, Anatumi nakama mona reto baa rangena ingyuo rombo palyiya doko soo kaelyamano.

Namwa waili pii keyange lao epeyama doko pii yeelyo minyuo epeyamande daa. Poralnya renge paletape Imambu Poo Pyasi opetaepe nakamana monarena yulu porai piramopa kapa ingingi lao suu pyarami doko minyuo epeyamasa piya. Nakama kapa serami dokona lao namwa apa pyuo pyuo karaminyi lao kandeyami.

Nakamame Kamongona yulu dokonape namwa piyama dokonape kimbu moko minyuo pyuo kareyami. Randa andake nyuo dokopa waili pii keyange soo nyiyami. Dokona Imambu Poo Pyasimi nyisiyamopa rae maiyuo kareyami.
Nakama yulu keyange piyami dokona Kurisene wambu yuu Masetonia rangepe yuu Girisi range dupwape nakamana yulu kandapala piyaminyili pyuo pyuo kareyami.
Kamongona waili pii nakama keta raeyo peya doko yuu Masetonia Girisipana iki daa. Nakama Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu piyami doko yuu muu peparaena lao peya. Dokona namwa aki mende konda pyuo laramase?

Namwa nakamana yuu dokona kanda soo epeyama dokopa nakamame yako lapala yulu andake piyami doko wambu peparae lao karaminyi. Dokona lao nakamame bange wakale anatu yaleoko kingimi waso kareyami dupwa yaki nyepala Anatu angi lete karenge dokona dokoko wambu peparae lao karaminyi.
Banya Ikinyingi baame lopo nyiyamo doko yake panda piso lupyuo eparamo doko isaro karaminyi. Yesu eparamo dokopa Anatunya kote andake palira dokona namwa nyiso kiiramo nyera.
Yangonemoo namwa epeyamano dokopa mee ingyuo paa naya nakama silyaminyi.

Namwa yuu Tesalonalka ene epeyamanopa yuu Pilipai dokona randa jepala kilya kando leyaminyipa kareyama doko silyaminyi. Randa andake jiyaminyipape Anatumi namwa porainyi pyambuyasa banya waili pii keyange eŋa nembo lao langyuo kareyama.
Namwa waili pii keyange lawa pyuo laa napala suu pingi koo wakale suu pyaa nao dee mendali minyoko pii nao lao karamano.

Anatumi namwa kando kapa lao suu pyapala waili pii keyange boo pyao lao kararama lao namwa keta jiyamosa baa namwa lamili yaka lao suu pilyamo dupwa iki lao karamano. Namwame isa wambu rae mainyi pyambwa nao Anatu iki rae mainyi pyambwalyamano. Baame namwana mona anda kandenge.
Pii isa isa panga panga paeyo lao dee pii wakale lao nyipuli nyipuli lao epa nayama. Nakama angi silyaminyi. Anatumi pii letamano doko soo karamo.
Namwame nakama range panda wambu menge dupwame lakandamili lao pyuo kara nayama.

Lao kara nayamanopape Koraisana aposele akali ingyuo karamano dokome namwa ketae pyambwalapape leyamali doko mee kapa ingiyali. Namwa nakama pipya karo anjiki pyuo endangimi wane rapu pingi doko suu pyao pyuo kareyama.
Namwame nakama mona reteyamano dokona Anatunya waili pii keyange doko langiyama. Doko iki langiyamande daa. Namwame nakama mona reto kareyamano dokome nakama kumuo jelana suu pyao kareyama.
Yangonemoo namwame yulu poralyuo pyulu pyuo piyama doko kinyi silyaminyi. Bange lapo kee laa narama lao yuu peparae kukwamape korakamape Anatunya waili pii keyange polo langyuo yulu pyuoko kareyama.

Yulu piyama doko nakamape Anatupi soo kandeyami. Nakama Kurisene wambu dupwa keta kopetame pii napala yulu rolae dupwa piyama dokopa mende larami ingya naya doko silyaminyi. 
			Namwame nakama rakangeme ikinyingi kando pinginyili pyuo pyuo kareyama.

Namwame Anatunya isingi panda neta renge yulu dokona pena kee lao nyuo karamana leyamo dokona karalamisi lao nakama nyiso poralnyi pyambuo Anatu rae mainya lao yulu keyange pirami dupwa mana langiyama.

Renge mendena opetae yuu peparae Anatu sangyu letamano. Namwame Anatunya waili pii minyuo epeyamano doko soo nyiyami. Pii leyama doko mee wambunya pii lao masa nao Anatunya piilyamo lao soo nyiyami. Pii soo nyiyami doko Anatumi angiko. Anatumi nakama Kurisene wambu sukusa dokona yulu pyuo poralnyi pyambuo karamo.

Yangonemoo Anatunya Elyambu Pingi wambu Koraisa Yesunya arupunya karo yuu Jutia karenge dupwa Juu wambumi randa maiyami. Doko suu pyao nakama Tesalonalka range dupwa nakamana rara dupwa keta randa nyuoko petaminyi.
Juu dupwame Kamongo Yesupi poropeta akali dupwape pyao kumakapala namwa randa jiyami. Randa jiyamisa Anatumi nakama kando epekanda nalyamo. Nakamame wambu peparae yanda pimwaiyuo karaminyi.

Juu wambu dupwame rara wakale dupwa waili pii keyange lamairama doko sepala lete wal pyao nyingi kando nyerami doko kata pyakepelyaminyi. Nakama yulu koo dokore kaeya nalyaminyi dokona andalu ando andapala Anatunya lenge kambu dokona kote pii palamo.

Yangonemoo namwame nakama rekya lao kaepala yuu wakale yuu gii mendasipa iki peteyamanopape nakama kondapala lenge kambu kandalana lao suu piyama. Yuu gii dokopa nakama kame soo kaeya nao yongome iki yaki nyuo kaeyama.
Namwa dee kapu kyuo epana suu piyama. Namba Pole yuu lamasa makande pyuo epana piyu. Epana piyunupape Sataneme kata pyakepeya.
Kamongo Yesu dee epo kararamopa namwa banya lenge kambu dokona karo yulu andake pipala nakama sukusa nyiyama doko suu pyao rae maiyuo lao kararama.
Kinyi nakamana kingi lakanda lakanda pyuo rae maiyuo minyuo petamano.
Enakana mona kendapala namwa yuu Atenesa dokona isaro karo dokopa
namwana yangonge Timoti pena leyama. Timoti baa namwa role pyao Anatunya yulu pyuo Koraisana lao waili pii boo pyao lamaiyuo kareya.

Nakama randa andake nyepala neta pasarami lao baa nakama poralnyi pyambuo nakamana Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingi doko nyisinya lao pena lamaiyama. Kurisene wambu nakama randa nyinginyili pyuo Anatunya suu piyamuli pyuo nyilyaminyi doko.
Namwa nakama role pyao kareyama dokopa randa epara langiyama kande dokona leyamanuli pyuo pilyamo.

Dokona lao nambame Timoti pena lamaiyu. Isaro karo mona kendapala nakama porayapala kapa karamipi lao kandala pena leyo. Sataneme nakama makande pyuo neta nyeramopa yulu andake piyama doko mee ingyuo para doko kapa daa lao suu piyama.

Timoti nakama role pyao karapala namwa karamwano dakena dee ipya. Ipyamopa nakama Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyapala mona reto karaminyi langipyasa rae maiyuo karamano. Baame langyuo dokopa nakama namwa mona retelyaminyi lapya. Namwa nakama kandamwali yaka lamwanopa nakamame dopako pyuo letaminyi langipya.
Yangonemoo namwa randa andake nao karamwanopape nakama yulu keyange piminyi pii doko soo nyepala mona minyarambu pipyamo karamano.
Nakama kaeya nao Yesu kapa ingingi lao suu pingi doko yaki nyii nalyaminyi langipyamo pii dokome namwa mata kyakao nyilyamo.
pii doko sepala dakepa nakama keta Anatu kando sangyu letamano. Namwame Anatunya lenge kambunya karo nakamana yulu rae maipala sangyu letamanoko.
Kukwa korakamape nakama kandamwali yaka lao Anatu dokona piso silyamano. Kandapala dokopa nakama Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyao karaminyi dokona mende mwuara ramo nyisarama ingilyamo.
Rakane Anatu, Kamongo Yesupame namwa eparama kata doko wapwakana lao suu pilyamano.
Namwame mona retenge yulu doko nakama keta palyuo pyoko pyoko laramopa nakama yango sukusape wakale dupwa ketape Kamongo dokome nyisaramopa reto karamili yaka lao suu pilyamano.

Dopa pyuo kararami dokome baame nakamana monarena poralnyi pyambwakaramopa Kamongo Yesu banya sukusa wambu pipya eparamo dokopa namwa Rakane Anatunya lenge kambu dorena koo keta pali nao yapasi ingyuo kararama.

Yangonemoo lumwa pyuo langilyu doko apa pyuo piramanosa Anatu rae maiyuo para lao mana langiyama kande. Dokonako palyuo nakamame pyuo karaminyi doko silyamano. Dee Kamongo Yesunya kingi lao yulu keyange konda pyuo pirami lao poralyuo langyuokondali pyuo letamano.
Kamongo Yesunya kingi lao pii mana langiyama dupwa soo karaminyi.
Anatumi nakama enda mende mee kepo pyakami napala yapasi ingyuo karamili yaka lao suu pilyamo.
Akali nakama mendaki lao rangena enda au pyuo suu pyao nyerami lao yapasi ingyuo apa pyuo reto palyuo ketae nembo pirami ingilyamo.
Anatu see nange akali dupwame etenge dupwa mona reta nao mee nyipuli lao nyilyaminyi dopako pyuo pii nalapape.

Dopako pyuo akali mendeme banya yango mende mata rukyuo pyao etengepa role pyao palyakami nara ingilyamo. Namwa wambo nakama repe repe langyuo Kamongome wambu yulu koo dopale pingi dupwa randa maira langiyama.
Anatumi namwa rombo palyuo dokopa waa kepo pingi yulu dokona kararami lao kee leyande daa. Poo pyasi ingyuo kararamiŋi lao kee lao nyiya kande.
Dopa pyuo mendeme Anatunya pii dake yake nyera ramo doko mee isa akali mata mai nao Anatumi Imambu Poo Pyasi jingi doko baa mata mairasa pira.
Nakamana sukusa wambu yango mona retami mana langirunde daa. Anatumi nakama range dopa pyuo mona retarami lao rolae mana langiya.

Mana langiyamopa nakama yuu Masetonia peparae dokona sukusa wambu yango dupwa peparaena lao mona reteyami. Yangonemoo yulu mondo lao piyami doko suu pyao epapu andarele pipwape lao laokondali pyuo letamano.
Wambo langiyamuli pyuo nakama au pyuo manda rao karope wambu wakalena yulu suu pyaa nao nakama rangena yulu suu pyapala rangena kingimi yulu pipwape.

Dopa pyuo piraminyi doko Kurisene laa nange dupwame nakama yulu keyange pilyaminyi dupwa kandapala lakandarami. Nakama dopako pyuo yulu pyuo nenge bangepe nyepengele dupwa range nyerami ramo doko wambu menge dupwa keta kee lao kara narami.

Yangonemoo wambu wamba kumuyami dupwana lao rolo simili yaka lao suu pilyamano. Yesu see nange wambu dupwame nakamana wambu yango kumaminyi dokopa mona nembelyaminyi. Nakamame wambu kumuo penge kata dokona rolo serami dokona mona nemba narami.

Yesu kumapala dee lopo neta epo peya doko kinyi lao suu pilyamano. Dee kapu kyuo eparamo dokopa Anatumi wambu mona kapu kyingi kumuyami dupwa Yesupa role pyao lanyuo epara doko kinyi lao suu pilyamanoko.
Pii dake Kamongona mana puŋi doko nakama langilyamano. Yuu gii Kamongo eparamopa wambu kumuyami dupwa wamba karaminyipa namwa enakarama.

Yuu gii dokopa Kamongo Yesu baa range yakena piso isa eparamo dokopa pii poralyuo wakasa mende laramopa aŋala mupwa pii laramo dokopa Anatunya pii ketae lakuli pii ingyuo lao epara. Dokopa wambu Koraisa mona kapu kyuo maipala kumuyami dupwa wambo lete sipuro pararmi.

Dokopa namwa kararama dupwape wambo kumapala sipurarami dupwa peparaepe nyuo pyaso kopa dokona kata pao Kamongo yakena kararamo doko kando nyerama. Kando nyepala dokona namwa Kamongo Yesumoo role pyao yuu peparae karalu kararama.
Dokona pii dapwa minyuo lao mendeme mende mona minyarambu karalapape.
Yangonemoo Yesu anjokorape epara yuu gii dokopape ee kana dupwanape lao namba pepa pyao jepenge ingya nalyamo.
Yuu gii Kamongo Yesu eparamo doko waa nyingi akali kamenge walu lao kukwama epenge dopale ingyuo epara doko nakama angi soo gisilyaminyi.

Wambumi lao, Namwa koo soo au pyuo petamano laraminyi gii dokopa aopa randa andake dokome nakama kokwa sinyi nembara. Randa andake eparamo doko enda wane mata pilyamopa yanga mangau lao randa nyingi dopale ingyaramopa randa doko wanja narami.
Dopa piramopape yangonemoo nakama iminjingi dorenako mee petaminde daa. Yuu yangara doko waa nala epenge dopale ingyuo pyaka sera ingya nanale.
Nakama neta rao karapyamo dokonape yangapyamo dorenape karaminyi. Namwa kukwa isa sulu sulu papyuo kara nalyamano.
Dokona lao wambu menge dupwa kamenge luu palenge dopale ingyuo pali narama ingilyamo. Namwa lenge rao suu pingi rolae palyuo kando kararama ingilyamo.
Wambu luu palenge doko kukwama dokopa palyuo dee biya napala kyakange doko kukwamako kyakao pao pingi.

Namwa dopale ingyuo dopale karamande daa. Yuu yango kaepyamo biya waso kararama ingilyamo. Namwa Yesu kapa ingingi lao suu pingipi mona retengepe dolapo konambe dopale ingyuo minyaro kararama. Yesu epapala namwa lete wal pyao nyera dokona mona kare kare karamano renge doko kapame wasisi kyawana pee pingi dopale pee piru karamwasa pilyamo.
Anatumi namwa keta kote andake palira lao rombo palya naya. Baame Kamongo Yesu Koraisa keta letena renge nyerami lao rombo palyiya.
Namwa ene lete karowape kumapalape Yesu eparamo dokopa namwa baamoo pipya role pyao karalu kararama lao kumakaya.
Renge dokona lao wambu yango poralnyi pyambuo mendeme mende nyuo mona minyarambu karalapape. Epapu dakepa pilyaminyi dopako pyuo kararami.

Yangonemoo poralyuo langyuokondali pyuo letamano. Nakamame wambu nakamana yulu role pyao pyuo karo Kamongo Yesu nakama kata keyange lasaka pinya lao mana nyerami lao rombo palyiya dupwa wambu lao suu pyao ketae pyambuo karaiapape.
Yulu pilyaminyi dokona nakama mondo lao rapu pyuo mona reto pirami. Dopa pyuo nakama range sukusa mona seramo karalapape.

Yangonemoo pii dake poralyawale letamano. Makange wambu dupwa yulu pinya lalapape. Wambu pako petaminyi dupwa poralnyi pyambwalapape. Wambu pyuku lasi dupwa nyisalapape. Wambu peparae dupwa pyalana pii nao mondo lao karalapape.
Mendeme baa kando koo piya kande koo yangome yano pyaa nana lamailapape. Yuu peparae keyange dokome nyuo rolo nakama yango dupwape wambu menge dupwape kondo kondo lao karalapape.
Yuu peparae rae maipala karo ateŋa lao karalapape.
Yulu peparaena lao Anatu kando sangyu lamaiyalapape. Nakama Koraisa Yesupana arapu dokona lete karaminyi dokona Anatumi nakama yulu keyange dopakale pyuo karamili lao suu pilyamo.
lmambu Poo Pyasi nyuo ango naa narami.
Anatunya pii pyongo pyao eparamo doko male male laa nalapape.
Yulu peparae nakanjo sepala renge keyange dupwa iki minyuo kararami.
Koo wakale wakale dupwa peparae yaki nyuo kaerami.

Anatu mona kyuu lao singi renge jingi dokome nakama banya angingyuo poo pyao nyakanale lao suu pilyu. Anatumi nakamana imambupi suu pingi yongope nyisu pisi naramopa pao Kamongo Yesu Koraisa eparamo dokona inginya lao iso karenale.
Dopa pyuo nakama kee letamo doko baa kaeya napala letamuli pyuo pira.
Yangonemoo nakama namwa opetae suu pyao ateŋa pyakalapape.
Nakamana wambu yango dupwa yako lao mona reto karalapape.
Kamongo Yesunya kingi lao Kurisene wambu peparae pepa pase dake yaka lao lamairami lao poralyuo langilyu.
Kamongo Yesu Koraisana mona keyange palyuo ipingi renge nakama keta palena.
Rakane Anatu Kamongo Yesu Koraisapana Elyambu Pingi wambu yuu Tesalonalka karenge dokona namwa Pole Sallasa Timotimoome pepa pyao jilyamano.
Rakane Anatupa Kamongo Yesu Koraisapana mona keyange palyuo ipingi renge dokope mona kyuu lao singi renge dokope nakama keta palena.

Yangonemoo yuu peparae nakamana lao Anatu sangyu lapenge ingilyamo. Nakamana Yesu kapa ingingi lao suu pingi doko ando andakyapala nakamana wambu yango kando mona retaminyi renge doko ando pelyamoko. Ando pupyamosa namwa Anatu kando kapa sangyu letamano.

Dokona lao Anatunya Elyambu Pingi dokona nakamana yulu piminyi dupwana lakandelyamano. Wambu lapome nakama kando randa wakale wakale jiminyipape nakama kaeya nao Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyao karaminyi dokome namwa nakama kando rae maiyuo lakandelyamanoko.
Anatunya isingi panda dorena reke lao randa andake nyuo kata wapulyaminyi. Nakama dokona sukusa parami dokopa Anatu rolae pyuo kote lenge doko panara.
Anatu baame rolae ingyuo nakama randa jilyaminyi wambu dupwa randa maira.
Nakama randa nyilyaminyi dokona Anatumi mandaranyi pyambwara. Kamongo Yesumoo banya aŋala porai dupwamoo yake dokona piso pano eparaminyi dokopa namwa opetae koo soo pisarama.
Wambu Anatu see nangepe Kamongo Yesunya waili pii keyange warombo soo pisa nange dupwape Yesu banya aŋala poral dupwa pipya isare kekenge dokome randa maiyala eparami.
Anatu see nange wambu dupwa Kamongopa pakao kara narami. Yuu gii pyaka seramo dokopa baa poral wakasa neta renge ingyuo epapala dokopa nakama rekya lanyi nembalu nembo nembara.

Baa eparamo dokopa banya wambu baa kapa ingingi lao suu pyao karenge dupwame banya kingi ketae pyambuo lakandarami. Dokopa nakama waili pii langiyama doko soo nyiyami dokona nakama opetae role pyao kararami.

Namwana Anatu baame nakama kee lao rombo palyiyamuli pyuo nakama kapa karamili lao yuu peparae ateŋa lakao karamano. Anatu banya poralnya renge dokome nakama pyuo au pyuo nyeramopa nakamana kapa ingingi lao suu pingi doko ando kameya inginya lao ateŋa letamano.

Dokopa namwana Kamongo Yesunya kingi doko nakama dokona mange karanyi pyambwaraminyipa nakama baame dopako pira. Dokopa namwana Anatu Kamongo Yesu Koraisapana mona keyange palyuo ipyuo pingi dokona ingyuo para.
Namwana Kamongo Yesu Koraisa eparamo dokopa namwa Yesumoo role pyao pisirama dokona lao langirowale.

Yangonemoo wambu lapome Kamongo Yesunya yuu gii doko wambo pyaka soo kaeya lao letaminyi dokona nakama walu lapala kyawa sisingi bolombalo lanyi nembo mona rando pisa nalapape, lao poralyuo langilyu. Pii kyal doo leyami dokona lao akali mendeme banya suu pingi dokona pyongo piyamo leya panda mendeme misi pii ingyuo leya lao see nalyo. Panda namwa Yesunya yuu gii epapeyamo dokona pepa pase pyao reteyamaŋa dolo kyambo leyami rapisa.

Dopa pyuo panga seraminyi pii doko soo nyii nalapape. Akali koo karapenge doko wambo epara dokopa yanda pii andake sipuraramopa enakana yuu gii doko pyaka sera. Akali koo karapenge doko panda koo dokona papala karalu karara.
Koo karapenge akalimi Anatunyape dee Anatunya yulu peparaepe yanda pimwalnyi pyambwara. Pyambwapala baa wakasa dulusale ingyuo suu pyao Anatunya tembole anda pao piso namba anatuŋu lao karara.
Nakama kame simisi? Namba nakama pipya karo dokopa pii dake langiyu kande.
Langiyunupape bange mendeme akali koo karapenge doko epa nana lao minya minya silyamo. Nakama doko aki lao silyaminyi. Yuu gii angi pyaka seramopa koo karapenge akali doko baa panara.

Akali karapenge doko dakepale banya minji nanji pyuo yulu pingi doko yalu pyuo pyuo karamo. Pyuo karapyamopape baa yulu angi piramo doko ene pii nalyamo doko mendeme banya kata pyakepelyamo. Banya kata pyakepelyamo doko isa paramopa baa panara.
Panaramo dokopa Kamongo Yesumi banya porainya renge dokome akali koo karapenge doko pyao kumakao baa neta renge ingyuo yanga paupau lao eparamo dokopa akali karapenge doko isa puu pao para.
Akali koo doko Satanena porainya renge paleta epapala yulu pii nange wakale wakale dupwa pyuope yamarangungi yulu dupwa pyuoko pira.

Pipala dokopa wambu yulu koo pyuo koo keta parami dupwa kando makande wakale wakale pira. Piramo dokopa koo pingi wambu Anatunya pii angi soo nyii nao mona reta nayami dupwa kumuo otarami. Pii angi doko mona reteyamili doko nakama lete wal pyao pumili.
Dokona lao kyambo pii soo nyerami lao Anatumi nakamana kyawa sisingi ukiaki minyuo kwaenyi nembara.
Dopa piramo dokopa wambu Anatunya pii soo nyii napala koo dupwana rae maiyami dupwa koo keta parami.

Yangonemoo Kamongo Yesumi nakama mona retenge dokona lao namwame nakama suu pyao yuu peparae Anatu kando sangyu larama ingilyamo. Nakama Anatunya pii angi doko kapa ingingi lao suu pilyaminyi dokona Anatumi nakama banya wambu angi ingyara lao Imambu poralnya renge dokome nakama wambo pyuo nyeroŋa lao kee lao rombo palyiya.
Waili pii keyange polo langiyamano dokome Anatu nakama kee lao nyiya. Nyiyamo dokona namwana Kamongo Yesu Koraisana neta renge doko nakama keta palira.
Yangonemoo dokona lao paka nao poralyuo suu pyao karo Anatunya pii angi langiyama dupwa minyaro karalapape. Anatunya pii angi polo langyuo pepa pase pyao joo kareyama dusipa minyaro karalapape.

Namwana Kamongo Yesu Koraisa baapa dee namwana Rakange Anatupame nakama poral inginyi pyambwarambi. Namwana Rakange Anatu baame namwa mona retapala mona keyange palyuo ipyuo karenge dokome namwa poralnyi pyambwalu pyambuo pyambuya. Pyambuyamosa Yesu dee epara lao mona kare kare karamano.
Nakama yulu keyange pyuope pii keyange laope mondo lao karalapa lao baame nakama poral inginyi pyambwara.

Yangonemoo epapu pii lumwa pyuo leto. Doko nakama Kamongo Yesunya waili pii keyange waiya lao sepala Anatu lakandeyami. Doko suu pyao yuu muu wakale dupwana wambu peparae walya lao soo nyepala Anatu lakandarami dokona ateŋa lakalapape.

Akali koo kopyali kopetame pingi dupwame namwa koo keta pyambwa nana lao Anatu baame namwa pyuo nyinya lao dokona opetae ateŋa lakalapapae. Renge doko wambu lapo Anatunya walii pii soo nyii nange kandale.
Kamongo Yesu baa kapa ingingi dokome nakama porainyi pyambuo Sataneme nakama keta koo mende pii nana lao kyawa minyuo karara.
Namwame nakama Kamongo Yesu keta pyamaiyinyi pyambuyama dokome namwa pii langiyama dupwa moko minyuo karapala pyuoko kararami doko soo gisilyamano.
Kamongome nyisaramopa nakama Anatu dokona mona maiyapala Koralsame yulu kaeya nao piyamo dokona mana nyepala dopako pyuo karaniiii yaka leto.
Yangonemoo Kamongo Yesu Koralsana kingi lao Kurisene wambu yango lapome namwana pii dupwa soo nyii napala yulu pelana makapala mee karaminyi dupwa role pyao kara napala yaki nyuo kaelapape.
Namwa nakama role pyao karo yulu andake piyama doko soo gisilyaminyi. Nakama sipurapala dopako pyuo yulu andake pirami doko rolaeŋe lao range silyaminyi.

Nakamana nenge nenge dupwa mee langa naa nayama. Yuu peparae range ropo pyao nyuo neyama kande. Nakamana nenge nao apa nanyi nembasarama lao suu pyapala namwa kaeya nao kukwa korakamape yulu andake pyuo kareyama.
Nakama nenge mee jinya lao kapa leyamali doŋo doko laa napala range yulu pyuo nyiyama kandapala nakama dokonako palyuo parami lao suu piyama.
Namwame wamba nakama role pyao karapala dokopa dopa pyuo langiyama kande. Mendalimi yulu pii nara ramo doko nenge anja seramo nyuo narase? Lopara ingilyamo.

Wambu yango lapo nakama role pyao piso karo pilyaminyi dupwa nakama maka suku suku nao yulu pii nao karaminyi doko sepala letamano. Nakama range yulu pii napalape wambu yango dupwa kando mora pii lao kanda lyanolyano pyuo karaminyi.
Dokopa Kamongo Yesu Koraisana kingi doko nakama mondo lao karo yulu au pyuo poralyuo pyuo rangena yole nyerami lao laokondali pyuo letamano.
Yangonemoo yulu keyange doko maka nao pyuo karalapape.

Nakama role pyao karaminyi wambu dokona mendeme pii pepa pase dakena palamo dupwa warombo see nara ramo doko lengeme iki makande pyuo kandapala baa keta mende pii nalapape. Dopa pirami ramo dokopa baa elya nyera.
Baapa nyisu petenge ingyuo yanda pimwainyi pyambwa nalapape. Pyambwa nao baapa Kurisene yango ingyuo yulu poraiyuo pinya lao baa kando anjiki pyuo nyisalapape.

Kamongo Yesu baa range mona kyuu lao singi renge renge kuiyuo karenge dokome baame randa wakale wakale eparamopape panda rae maingi renge eparamopape yuu peparae nakama mona kyuu lao singi renge jinya. Kamongo Yesu nakama pipya role pyao karena.
Nambana rangena kingimi yako lao lenge pii dake namba rangena kingi pilyu. Pepa pase yuu wakale peparaena pyao maingi dokopa nambame dopa pyuo pingi. Namba Pole yako leto.
Kamongo Yesu Koraisana mona keyange palyuo ipingi renge doko nakama peparae keta palena leto.
Namba Pole Koraisa Yesunya aposele akali Anatu namwana Lete Wal Pyao Nyingi dokope Koraisa Yesu namwa keta dee epara dokope leyambinyili pyuo aposele akali ingyuo karo.

O Timoti nambana Kurisene wane angi doko emba pepa dake pyao jilyu. Rakane Anatu namwana Kamongo Koraisa Yesupame mona keyange palyuo ipingi renge dokopa sakao nyiso karenge renge dokope mona kyuu lao singi rengepe emba keta palena lao leto.

Wambo namba yuu Masetonia panya karo dokopa emba yuu Epesasa dokona karare lao langiyunu doko suu pyao epapu dee kamba emba Epesasa dokona karareko langilyu. Emba doo karapala akali lapo Anatunya pii dokona kyambo letaminyi dupwa kando kaena lamairi.

Nakama sinju pii dupwape rora ambasupinya kingi dupwape ketae pyambuo lao kara nana lamairi. Pii dopale lao kararami ramo doko wambu dupwana kyawa sisingi bolombalo larasa angi doko anjuku lao saka naramisa pira. Pii kyal dokome Anatunya yulu dupwa moko minyuo paa nalyamo. Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingi wambu dupwame iki Anatunya yulu rolae kandenge.

Nakama mona mendaki palyuo Anatu kapa ingingi lao kulisa palyuo suu pyapala koo mende nakama keta pali nalyamo doko monarena pyapi pyuo soo otapala kararaminyi dokopa mona retenge renge doko ando nyimbwaraŋa lao mana pii dake langilyamano.
Wambu lapome kata angi doko yaki nyepala mee kambu pii lao papyuo karaminyi.
Wambu dusipa nakama Anatunya mawa pii mana lenge akali karamwali lao karelyaminyipape pii poralyuo letaminyi dokona angi doko aki lao soo gisa nalyaminyi.
Namwame Anatu suu piyamuli pyuo Mosesena Lowa doko moko minyuo parama ramo dokopa Lowa doko keyange lao kandarama.

Anatumi lowa dupwa akali keyange dupwana lao wasa naya. Wambu lapome lowa dokona kokwa singipi karapusi palengepe wambu Anatu suu pyaa nangepe koo pingipi misi anda paa nangepe wambu Anatunya Imambunya yulu dokona see nangepe wambu lapo nakamana endangi rakangepa pyao kumakangepe dee wambu yango pyao kumakangepe peparaena serami lao wasiya Anatumi.

Dopako pyuo wambu pundange yulu pingipi wambu kepo pingipi wane wanake nyaŋa waa nyingipi wambu kyambo lengepe wambu pii kyarepa pingipi wambu angi rolae pii nangepe Anatumi nakamana lao suu pyao lowa pii dupwa wasiya.
Nakamame Anatunya waili pii keyange wakasa namba keta epelyamo doko yalo pelyaminyi dokona Anatu neta rengepe elyape keta karengepe baa lowa pii dupwa wasiya.
Namwana Kamongo Koraisa Yesumi namwa poralnyi pyambuo banya yulu piri lao rombo palyiya dokona rae maiyuo sangyu leto.
Namba wambo Anatu kando pii koo lapala lekeleke rena lao baa kilya kando leyonopape namba baa soo gisa napala mee kamenge lao kareyonopa baame namba kando kondo sakao karapala sukusa nyiya.

Kamongome banya mona keyange palyuo ipingi renge doko namba keta maralyiya. Dee kapa ingingi lao suu pingi rengepe mona retengepe dolapo Anatumi jiya. Namwa Koraisa Yesumoo pipya yalya kando role pyao karenge dokona Anatumi dusipa jingi.

pii langilyu dake ama kinyi kinyi palamo. Soo nyepala minyalapape. Koraisa Yesu baa namwana yuu dakena epapala wambu koo pingi dupwana lao lete wal pyao nyeroŋo lao epeya. Wambu doloma yulu koo pyuo kareyaminyipape namba kamame koo ingyuo kareyo.

Dopa pyuo yulu koona mupwa ingyuo piyunu dokona lapala Anatumi sakao pyuo nyuo nyisiya. Anatu baa rape rape lao karenge doko namba akali koo wakasa pingi doko keta lasaka piya. Wambu enakana Yesu kapa ingingi lao suu pyao kyakana renge kulisa palu palenge nyerami dupwame serami lao namba keta lasaka piyasa piya.
Kuma napala karalu karenge Kiŋi doko baa wambumi kapa kanda nange Anatu mendaki doko kando wambu peparaeme lakandapala kingi ketae nembo karalu kararami doko kinyi.

O nambana wane Timoti mawa pii dake emba langilyuŋu sepe. Yuu wamba poropeta akali dupwame emba keta nolakayami dokona suu pyao karo. Pii poropeta dupwame leyami dusipa lao minyuo nyisu petenge wambu anamasi minyare.

Minyapala embena kapa ingingi lao suu pilini renge dokome minyuo embena suu pingi renge doko poo pyasi ingyuo palena lao yaki nyii nao karare. Wambu lapome yulu rolae dupwa sepala karo kando kaeyo koo pyuo kareyaminyipa nakamana Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingi doko isa peya.
Akali lama nakambana kingi Aimeniasa Alekesandapa lenge dolapome dopako piyambi. Piyambinyisa nambame Anatunya kando pii koo laa nana lapala Satanena arapu dorena karena lamaiyu.
Wambu peparaena lao piso singipi ateŋa lengepe kee lengepe sangyu lengepe lao pii dusipa mupwa ingyuo Anatu kando lamaiyalapape lao poralyuo langilyu.
Namwa mona kyuu lao seramopa elya kalo Anatunya Imambunya yulu pyuo yulu rolae dupwa suu pyao karamwali lao Anatumi kiŋipi gapomanepe dupwa nyiso karena lao ateŋa lakamyuo karamana.
Yulu keyange dopale dokome namwana Lete Wal Pyao Nyingi Anatu doko rae mainyi pyambungi.
Anatumi wambu peparae lete wai pyao nyelana banya pii angi soo nyimili lao suu pyao karamo.
Anatu baa mendaki iki karo, dee kanya akali mendaki doko Anatu akalipa nyuo pakao pingi doko Koraisa Yesuko karo pingi.
Akali peparae kiiramo nyelana baa range kumuo maiya. Dokome Anatumi akali peparae pyuo nyelana suu piya, yuu gii rolae doko pyaka sera dokopa panara.

Renge dokona lao namba Juu daa rara wakale dupwana aposele akali ingyuo nakama mana lao karare lao waili pii angipi Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingipi dokona lao Anatumi namba mapanyi nembeya. Doko nambame kyambo letonde daa. Kinyi leto.
Anatu iki suu pingi dupwa imbuo apiyanda pyuo lao kara napala yuu muu dupwana peparae ateŋa lao karamili lao suu pilyu.

Pii mende doko enda dupwa nakama inyimungu mona palenge ingyuo piso nakama range komau kapa pira dupwa mondo lao wapunya. Dopako pyuo wambu kandamili kandamili lao kyawasi kalya pyuo kupinyi dorena palya dakena palya nalapape. Moŋokyaŋe soo mola wakale wakale dupwame kalya pii nao kana malu penge komaupi wapuo pii napenge. Dee kalya wakale wakale lapo opetae pii kaena.
Yulu keyange dupwa nyuo komau ingyuo wapurami. Dopa pirami doko Imambunya kata ingyuo paramisa pira.
Misi anda dupwana nakama range inyimungu pii laa nao mee petena.
Endame mana pii lao nakamame akali rapu pili lasarami kaena leto. Nakama mee elya kalo petena.
Doko Anatumi Atame baa wambo ingyuo wasapala Ipi enakana wasiya.
Dee Sataneme akali keta wambo panga soo maralya naya. Enda doko dokona rambu lapala keta panga soo maralyamopa enda dokome Anatunya lowa pii dokona kamba leya.
Dopa piyamopape enda dupwa Yesu kapa ingingi lao suu pyao mona nembo Anatunya Imambunya yulu pyuo inyimungu pisarami ramo dokopa wane mandenge yuu gii pyaka sera ramo Yesumi iso karara.
Pii dake kinyi palamo. Akali mendeme Elyambu Pinginya yulu pinya mona nyera ramo doko yulu keyange dokona pinya pirasa pira.

Dopa pyuo palamo dokona Elyambu Pinginya akali mupwa dupwa pii pali naramo kararami ingilyamo. Baa enda mendaki ikinya akalingi ingyuo karena. Moŋokyaŋe see nao rangena suu pingi kame pyuo niinyuo karo yulu rolae pyuo karena. Wambu upunili dupwa banya anda yako lao nyuo nenge pyuo pyuo karena. Baa niana lenge yulu dokona wanonguli ingyuo niana lao karapenge ingilyamo.

Dopako pyuo Elyambu Pinginya rapu pingi doko biya wasinyi nembo walya lao imbwualana wangu lakao pyakandenge akali ingyuo kara nara. Baa niona kyuu lao seramopa elya kalo karo kana monena niona nyingi ingyuo karara ingya nalyamo.
Baa rangena enda wanepe niondo lao rapu pyuo karo banya wane wanakepeme baa kando kamba laa napala banya kingi ketae nembo petena lao karara ingilyamo.
Rapu pingi baame banya enda wanepe niondo lao rapu pii narande ramo dokome apa pyuo Anatunya ree palu doko niondo lao rapu pyakamyuo kararase?

Dokonako ingyuo ene alembole Anatu niona nialya ramo dokome baa Elyambu Pinginya rapu akali ingya nana. Dopa pyuo pira ramo dokopa Sataneme piyamuli pyuo kyaŋe singi renge dokome ipwa ingyuo palyuo pyoko pyoko larasa pira. Satane koo keta paleyamo doko suu pyao akali dopale doko koo keta palira.
Neta wambu dupwame baako kando pisirami. Moŋokyaŋe see nara ramo dokopa kando pisaranii dokome Satanena kone makara dokona lyii nara.
Elyambu Pinginya nyisingi akali dupwa mona palyuo pii lamana laa nao karapenge ingilyamo. Ipwa waene malu mee naa nao bange nyipuli nyipuli lao suu pyao karara ingya nalyamo.
Anatumi pii kinyi doko pano lasaka piyamo doko kapa ingingi lao suu pyao mona dokona pyapi pyuo soo niinyaranii.
Nakamana yulu dupwa wambo makande pyuo kandapala kapa piranii lao suu pyarami ramo dokopa nyisinginya yulu dokona rombo palyaranii.
Nakambana enda opetae niona angi palenge ingyuo wambu mata kando dopale dapale, lao lao pisa narami. Nakama biya naa nao yulu rolae pyuo petena.
Elyambu Pinginya nyisingi baa enda niendaki ikinya akalingi ingyuo karara. Baame banya enda wanepe mondo lao rapu pyuo karara ingilyamo.
Wambu Anatunya yulu keyange pingi dupwana kingi wambu peparaenie ketae nembo pisirami. Nakamame Koraisa Yesunya wambu ingyuo banya waili pii keyange kapa poralyuo lamaiyuo pisirarmi.
Pepa dake wambo pyao jepala rengya repetaleko emba kandala eparo lao suu pilyu.

Namba walya lao epa naro ramo dokopa emba pepa pyao jilyu dake kando yaka lapala namwa apa pyuo Anatunya Elyambu Pingi ree palu wambu dupwa kapa rolae pinginyili pyuo pirama lao sere. Elyambu Pingi doko lete palenge Anatu dokona ingyaro karapyamopa dokome kinyinya renge dokome paka pyao sakao karamo.

Elyambu Pingi doko anda pinginya ingyaro Anatunya Imambunya yulu dokona renge yalu pyuo siyamopa kando nyiyama doko mendeme mupwa daa lao matarena pii larami ingya nalyamo. Wambu wai pyapala akali lenge kambu nyuo paneyamopa, Imambumi baa rolae wakasaŋa lao lao paneyapya. Aŋala dupwame baa kandeyamiko. Rara wakale dupwana baa dokona lao lamaiyuo peyami. Yuu muu dupwana baa kapa ingingi lao suu pyao mona maiyami. Baa lopo epapala yake panda peya.
Imambumi rakyame akali lapo Anatunya kata yaki nyerami doko wambo nolakao letamo. Nakamame imambu mee kyambo lenge dokona pii minyuo imambu koona mana pii larami dupwana soo parami ingilyamo.
Akali pii kyal pyuo lenge dupwame panga soo lao mana pii kyambo letaminyi. Akali dusipana monarena kerange pyao otapyasa koo keyangepe anjuku lao soo saka nalyaminyi.

Akali mana koo larami dupwame lao nakama enda nyii nao nenge lapo wasaka pyuo karo pipwape larami. Nenge waso karalapape letaminyi dusipa Anatumi narami lao jiya. Wambu Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyao pii kinyi doko soo nyingi dupwame ange lapala narami dokona jiya.
Bange Anatumi wasiyamo dupwana mende koo daa. Dokona mende yaki nyuo nembarama ingya nalyamo. Nenge dupwana lao Anatu kando sangyu lao nao kararama.
Anatunya pii dokope dee ateŋa dokomepe banya lenge kambu dokona nenge dupwa poo pyasi ingyuo pelyamo.

Embame pii dake Kurisene yango dupwa lamairi ramo dokome emba Koraisa Yesunya kendemande keyange ingyuo karare. Yuu gii dokopa Anatunya imambunya nenge nao pirisa pira. Imambunya nenge angi doko nakama Anatunya pii soo nyuo banya yulu poralyuo minyuo angi pyuope dolapo angi ingilyamo.
Arome pii kwaeyarali Anatu rae mai narali dupwa wasapala Imambunya yulu dokona rangeme range sukunde ingyuo kiso rolare.
Mee yulu andake piri dokome yanenge poraiyaramo dokopa yanengena yulu kapa pira. Dopaleko ingyuo imambu dokona porainyi pyambwarami ramo dokona isa pandape yake pandape laparaena kapa ingyuo pare.
Pii dake ama kinyi kinyi dokome wambu peparae soo nyepala kinyi lao suu pyarami.

Anatu lete karenge dokome baa kapa ingingi lao suu pilyamano dokona lao yulu andake randa nao pyuo karamano. Baame wambu peparae lete wai pyao kapa nyera ingyapyamopape baa mona angingyuo maingi wambu dupwa kaeya nao lete nyera ingilyamo.
Pii dapwa enda akalipi keta mana lamaiyuo letamanuli pyuo pinya lare.

Emba wanyane akali lapala wambu lapome emba pirinyi dupwa kando epekanda nasarami kando lao yulu auwo kandaramili dupwa iki yapo piri. Pii laope wambu yango mona retope Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyao karo emba kando laa naramili dupwana palyuo rolae pyuo karape.
Wambu peparae elyambu pyuo pisiraminyipa buku Baepole pii yaka lao misi pii lao mana lamairi. Lamaipala namba iso karowale pyuo karo dokopa yulu rema dasipanako kare kare soo piri.

Poropeta akali dupwa misi andake lao kareyaminyipa Elyambu Pinginya mupwa dupwame emba elya pyuo pyambuo nakamana kingi dupwa embena kyawana reteyami dokopa Imambumi emba keta mora petenge jiyamo doko mee kaka soo nemba napipi.
Yulu dokonako emba kumuo maipala mana nyuo piri. Pirinyi dokopa yulu doko ando paramopa wambumi kandenale.
Emba rangena yulu pyuope mana pii laope dolapona kando pyuo karape. Dopa pyuo puu pare ramo dokome emba rangepe dee wambu embena pii serami dupwape kyawa minyara ingilyamo.
Alemo dupwa kando pyalana pyuo laa nao pii elya kalo lao rakane kando lamainginyili pyuo lao rolo karare. Dopako pyuo wanyane akali dupwa embena yangone kando lamainginyili pyuo lao rolo karare.
Dee endemo dupwa endakinyi kando leto lao maso lao rolo dee mapwae dupwa kando dokopa pemalene angi lamaingi dokona kata palyuo lao rolo mende suu pyao lao kara napipi.
Enda walya dupwa saka nalya nana pyuo pisirami ramo dokopa ketae pyambuo nyiso karare.

Baa wane mandenge ramo panda apusingi karenge ramo nakambana Kurisene yulu mupwa doko endangi rakangepame wamba rapu piyambi dokona isingi rapu pyuo karena. Dopa pyuo pirami doko Anatu baa epe soo karara.
Enda waiya doko baa mendali range palya nangende ramo doko baame Anatumi mende pyakara lao suu pyao kukwa korakamape yuu peparae kaeya nao ateŋa lao petena.
Enda akalingi kumasi doko kopyali ingyuo yanengena laramuli pyuo pisira ramo doko mee peto lao lete pisiramopape kumuo kaeyo pisirasa pira.
Enda walya dupwa keta pii doko kyawa ingyuo lamairinyi soo nyerami dokona mendeme enda dupwa kando larami ingya naiyamo.

Mendeme banya ranjama mendare dee yangonge rakangepe dupwa mondo lao suu pyao rapu pii nara ramo dokome banya Kurisene yulu suu pyaa narasa pira. Mee Kurisene ingya nange akali dopale daako. Baa ama koo wakasa ingyarasa pira.
Enda walya doko wamba akali mendaki iki nyiyande ramo doko Elyambu Pinginya nyisingi enda ingyuo yulu pinya lara ramo doko kapa rombo palyuo kingi retarami. Endemo dupwa iki rombo palyarami.

Endemo yulu rolae pingi letaminyi dupwa iki rombo palyarami. Banya wane mondo lao rapu pyuo andanyi pyambuo wambu nenge pyuo Kurisene yango pipya kendemande yulu pyuo wambu randa nyerami dokopa pyuo nyiso yuu peparae yulu keyange dopale dusipa pyuo petengende ramo doko banya kingi pepana sinya.
Enda angi lapo walya ingyuo pisirami dupwa rombo palya nalapape. Nakama sipurapala akali nyelana suu pyaraminyi dokopa Yesu Koraisana yulu doko yaki nyepala parami.
Dopa pyuo pisirami enda dupwame Koraisa kando wambo lalu lao leyami pii dokona yalapala koo piramisa pira.

Enda dopale doko mora pisi napala anda kambu yaka lao papyuo pii wakale mendena laminyi dupwa palya nao lao pii laa narali dupwa kata raena lao lele lao lao pisinyi pyambuo papyuo karaminyi. Dopako pyuo pii kapa laa naramili dupwana lao yulu koo dopale dupwa mana nyilyaminyi.
Dokona enda walya dupwa akali kapa nyuo wane kando nyepala anda rapu pyuo pisipenge. Dokopa namwana yanda pimwal dupwame pii koo lao giyalya giyana pii nanale.
Dokonako enda walya lapome Anatunya kata doko yaki nyepala Satane kata dokona papelyaminyi.

Enda mende walya ingyuo peteya kande doko banya ree palu dokona Kurisene enda dupwame rapu pyuo pisirami. Doko kaepala Elyambu Pingi wambu wakale dupwame rapu pyuo karena laa narami. Elyambu Pingi doko enda waiya saka nao petaminyi dupwa nyisarami yulu doko palamo.

Elyambu Pinginya akali rapu pingi lapome Anatunya yulu doko mondo lao rapu pilyaminyi dupwa nakama yole kana konda pyuo mairami ramo doko kapa ingyara. Misi yulu dokona angingyuo pilyaminyi dupwasa leto.
Baepoleme lao dokopa, Mena bulamakaome witi jingi kambena lao kalyiya kande dokopa kambu doko puu pyakami napipi dee, Yulu pingi akalimi yole kana kapa nyepenge lao silyamano doko letamo.
Akali mendeme Elyambu Pinginya akali mupwa doko kando kyal pyuo pilyamo leya kande doko baame iki laramo dokopa pii minyakami nalapape. Dee wambu rema lamapena pii larami dokopa kote kapa larami.
Koo piyami kande dokopa wambu menge dupwana lenge kambu dokona pano pyalana pyuo lape dopa pyuo larene kandapala dokopa lapo dupwa pako kararami.
Anatu dokonape Koraisa Yesu dokonape aŋala poo pyasi dupwanape lenge kambu doko pii dake emba poralyuo langilyu. Emba wambu dupwa kando yapalya yapana pyuo lapo nyiso lapo nyisa nao pyuo kara napipi.
Kamongona yulu dokona mendali langa walya lao rombo palya napipi. Mendena koo piramo dokona mee isa lakao palele lapala pii nao range waso kandanyi nembo karare.
Yuu malu mee emba anga pingi dokona mee ipwa nao karalu kara napala embena inginya anga nyerene dokona lao waene mee kuki nare ramo doko kapa nyisara.
Wambu lapona yulu koo panelyamo dupwa kote laramo dokopa yake panda wambo pao panda koo sera. Dee wambu lapona yulu koo yalu pyuo silyamo dupwa yuu gii angi pyaka separamopa panara.
Dopako pyuo lapona yulu keyange dupwa kandelyamano. Yulu keyange yalu pyuo pilyaminyi dupwana yulu doko enakana panara silyamanoko.

Yulu pingi akali dupwame nakamana yulu pyakamaingi akali doko keyange ingyuo karamo lao suu pyao karo banya kingi ketae pyambuo pyuo kararami. Dopa pyuo kararami ramo dokopa Anatunya kingi dokonape dee Kurisene yulupi dolapona kwaelyamo laa narami.

Yulu pingi akali dupwame nakamana yulu pyakamaingi akali doko Kurisene ramo dokona baa nambana yangonge angi ingilyamo lao suu pyapala banya pii doko kamba larami ramo doko kapa ingya nara. Nakamana yulu pyakamaingi akali doko Kurisene ingyuo karenge ramo doko banya yulu ama poraiyuo mondo lao pyakamirami. Dopa pirami ramo dokopa Kurisene wambu yango dupwa nyisaramisa pira. Pii langilyu dusipa mana lamaiyuo polo lao kara.

Lapome Kamongo Yesu Koraisana pii angipi namwana misi pii rolaepe yaki nyepala pii wakale lao eparaminyi dupwa mee moŋokyaŋe sepala renge angi see nao kararami ingilyamo. Pii wakale wakale dupwana lao apiyanda pyuo karalana lalya lao karaminyi. Nakama yango palyuo sisi nyuo giyalya giyana pyuope mee nambana yulu lakao pilyaminyi lao suu pyao pingi yulu dopale pilyaminyi.

Dokona nakama akali kyawa sisingi mondo lao pali naope dee Anatunya pii kinyi angi doko nakama keta pali nangepe mee yuu peparae apiyanda pyuo karaminyi. Wambu dopale dupwame Anatunya yulu pingi dokome nakama kamongarama lao suu pilyaminyi.
Akali mendeme Anatunya yulu rae maiyuo pyuo sikya pira ramo doko baa keta renge keyange palira.
Namwa endangimi mandeyamo dokopa bange mende minyuo epa nayama. Dee yuu dake yaki nyerama dokopa bange dokona mende minyuo paa naramako.
Dokona lao namwa epapunya ingyuo nenge komaupi kapa sera ramo dusipa kapaŋa lao suu pyao karamana.

Akali bange andake nyuo retalana suu pilyaminyi dupwa isa parami ingilyamo. Kopyali minyuo bange nyelanako suu pyarami kata dokona randa opetaeko nyerami. Randa nyeraminyipa dokome nakama nyuo sinjimu paro kokwa sinyi nembara.

Kana mone mona nyingi dokome koo dokona mona anda pingi pyarasa pira. Lapome mone dokona rungi rungi pyapala Anatunya Imambunya yulu kame silyaminyi. Dopa pipala nakamana mona dokona randa nyuo kondo mona rumbungi karaminyi.

Emba Anatunya wambu dokome yulu koo doko waso karare. Yulu rolae dokonape Anatunya Imambunya yulu angipi kapa ingingi lao suu pingipi mona retenge rengepe Anatunya yulu yaki nyuo kaeya naope anjiki pyuope yulu dopale dupwa pyuo gii lao minyaro karare.

Wambu Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyapala kyakana renge nyingi doko akali bange nyelana makandenge dopale. Anatumi letena renge nyepala pyuo karare lao rombo palyiyamopa wambu malu mee kando kareyaminyipa emba sipurapala Yesunya kingi lao ketae lakandee kande.

Anatumi lete karenge renge maingi dokopa dee Koraisa Yesumi akali Pondiasa Pailate lenge kambunya karo dopa pyuoŋo lao polo leya dokope dolapona lenge kambu dokona karo epapu nambame emba dopa pyuo piri lao langilyu.
Emba mawa pii doko kokwa see nao yapasi ingyuo sinya lao poralyuo minyarenepa Kamongo Yesu Koraisa eparamo dokona iki liti pira.
Anatu baa kamongona Kamongo dee kiŋinyako Kiŋi mupwa ingyuo karenge. Baa iki wambu peparaena Rapu Pingi ama elyape ingyuo karamo. Baako Yesu eparamo gii doko pyaka seramo kandapala epena lara.

Anatu baa iki kumungi renge doko pali nange. Baa rao yanga paupau lao karelyamo dokona mendali repeta paa nange. Baa mendemepe kanda nange dee mendeme kapa kandarami ingya nangeko. Banya kingi ketae pyambuo paliramopa wambu peparae iso karalu karena, doko kinyi.

Wambu isa bange malu mee retenge dupwa moŋokyaŋe see nana lao poralyuo lamairi. Bange peparae mee ingyuo isa para dupwana lao andanyi nembo mona nyii napala Anatumi bange monarena rae maiyuo kamongarami lao jiyamo dupwana rae maiyuo mona nyuo karena lare.
Nakama bangena kamongo dupwame rango naa napala mee mokwa soo mainya suu pyapala maiyuo yulu keyange pyuo kamongo karena lamaipi.
Nakama dopa pyuo pirami ramo doko rengya kapa paiyuo parami dupwa nyuo nakamana rangena kulisa ingyuo seramisa pira. Dokona lao nakama lete kararami angi doko nyuo kaiyuo minyaramisa pira.

O Timoti emba keta Anatumi yulu jiyamo dokona waso minyuo pyuo karape. Wambu lapome soo gisapala lao karamano laminyipape pii doko Anatunya pii daa mee isa wambunya kopyali pii letaminyi dupwa waso karape. Mee pii lapo Anatunya kata dokona ingya nange dopale dupwa mata maiyuo karape. Pii dopale dupwa kyambona ingyuo singiŋi lao larami lyakande.

Wambu lapome namwa soo gisingiŋi lao karaminyi dupwa nakamame Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingi doko papu pyuo lamisa pilyamo. Anatunya mona keyange palyuo ipingi renge doko nakama peparae keta palena leto.
Namba Pole Koraisa Yesunya aposele akali Anatu pipili lao suu piyamuli pyuo mapanyi nembeyamopa Anatumi lete karenge nyerami lalu lao leyamo dokona Koraisa Yesumoo nyuo pakao karamano.

Nambana mona retenge wane Timoti emba keta pepa dake pyao jilyu. Rakane Anatu namwana Kamongo Koraisa Yesupana mona keyange palyuo ipingipi sakao nyiso karenge mona kyuu lao singipi emba keta palena lao leto.

Nambana rora ambasupimi Anatu lakando mona suu pinginya pyapi pyuo soo lenge dokona namba opetaeko piyaminyili pyuo pipala eŋa pupyamopa Anatu sangyu lao karo. Yuu peparae kukwa korakamape ateŋa lao dokopa embena lao suu pyao Anatu sangyu lao lapa pilyu.
Namba embena ee leene dupwa suu pyapala kandapulimi kumulyu dokona epo emba kandapala dokopa raeme kumaro.

Namba embame Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyao mandeene doko angi ingilyamo lao kame see nalyo. Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingi dokore embena apusingi Loisa endakinyi Yunisapame opetae suu pyao peteyambipya. Doko suu pyao embena doko mendare ingyuo pelyamo lao silyu.
Dokona lao misi andalce dokona nambame emba kingi nyuo rombo palyiyunupa Anatumi banya yulu emba keta jiyamo doko isasa pinyi pyambuo karape lao langilyu.
Anatumi Imambu jiyamo dokome pakange renge doko jinginde daa. Pakange renge jilyuŋi lao dokopa poralnya rengepe mona retengepe range rapu pyuo karengepe dupwa Imambumi joo simbungi.

Namwana Kamongo dokona pii polo lalana elya nao dee namba banya ingyuo karapusi palo dokona lapala elya nyii napipiyoko. Dopa pyuo Anatu emba poralnyi pyambwaramopa waili pii keyange dokona lao randa emba keta eparamo epena rao laoko karape.

Baame namwa lete wal pyao nyepala banya ingyarami lao kyakale leya. Doko namwame range yulu keyange piyamande daa. Baa rangena suu piyamuli pyuo mona keyange palyuo ipyapala kyakale lao rombo palyiya. Yuu ene wasaroŋo lao karo dokopa Koraisa Yesu keta mona keyange palyuo ipingi doko joo kaeya.

Namwana Lete Wal Pyao Nyingi akali Koraisa Yesu baa epo panapala Anatunya mona keyange palyuo ipingi doko baa keta paneya. Koraisame kumunginya rengena poralnya renge namwa keta palenge doko nyuo anameya. Anamo waili pii keyange dokome kuma nange renge doko nyuo nolakaya.
Anatumi namba aposele yulupi mana lenge yulupi dolapona waili pii keyange polo lare lao rombo palyiya.

Renge dokona lao namba keta randa nyilyu. Randa nyipunupape namba dokona lao elya nalyo. Nambame akali kapa ingingi lao suu pyao karo doko range silyu. Yuu gii mupwa ene pyaka sepa naramopa yulu piri lao rombo palyakaya dokona minyuo pyuo kararo dokopa kyawa minyuo karara.
Pii langiyunuli pyuo piri lao pii angi langiyu dupwa minyuo karape. Koraisa Yesupa pakaro karaminyi dokona Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingipi mona retengepe dolapo poralyuo minyuo pyuo karalu karare.
Imambu Poo Pyasi namwa maralyiyamo dokome emba nyisaramopa renge keyange emba keta palamo doko sakao sakao pyuo minyuo karape.
Yuu Esia wambu peparaeme namba yaki nyiyami dokopa Piselasa Emoseuisapa opetaemeko yaki nyiyambi doko emba silinyi.
Ouisimasa namba yuu malu mee rae mainyi pyambuyamo dokona Kamongome banya ree palu sakao pyuo nyinya. Baame namba karapusi kareyo dokona elyapala kaeya naya.
Dopa pyuo karo baa yuu Orome epapala dokopa namba kaeya nao karapala kando nyiya.
Yuu gii mupwa pyaka seramopa Kamongo dokome Ouisimasa baa sakao nyiso karena lao suu pilyu. Embame nambana lao yuu Epesasa dokona Ouisimasame yulu andake pyakaya doko ama soo gisasi karene.
Nambana wane Timoti emba Koraisa Yesupa pakao karo baa mona keyange palyapala ipyuo kararamopa porayapala karape.
Wambu malu soo kareyaminyipa lao kareyo pii dupwa emba soo gisii kande dupwa embame wambu mona palenge dupwa lamairinyipa nakama soo nyepala wambu wakale lamairami dokona mana lamaiyuo karape.
Koraisa Yesunya yanda pyakamaingi akali ingyuo yasoko nao karare ingilyamo.
Akali aminya yulu pingi dupwa yulu wakalena minyuo komonda nange. Baa aminya yulu dokona yeelyo ami rapu pingi akali mupwa doko rae mainyi pyambuo pingi.
Akali bange nyelana makandenge baame makandengena lowa dupwa minya napala dokome bange nyuo kapa wini larande daa.
Ee wara pingi akalimi randa nao yulu poralyuo piramo dokome ee mupwasa doko manjo nara ingilyamo.
Namba pii langilyu dupwa apa pyuonde lao suu pyao pisirinyipa Kamongome epapala nyisaramo dokopa kapa rolo sere.
Yesu Koraisa Dapitinya para pyasi baa kumuo palyuo lopo epeyamo dokona waili pii keyange nambame lao karo doko suu pyaoko karape.
Namba waili pii keyange lapunu dokona lao randa nyipunupa wambu pingi akali dopale ingyuo puu saneme kiimbwaminyi karo. Dopa piminyipape Anatunya pii doko puu maiyuo retarami ingya nalyamo.

Dokona lao Anatunya rombo palyisi wambunya reke lao randa peparae nyuo karapusa pilyamo. Doko Koraisa Yesumi nakama opetae lete nyakaramopa yanga paupau lenge panda dokona karalu kararami lao randa nao karo.
Pii dake angingyuo letamo lao soo nyimana. Namwa Yesu kumuyamo dokona kumuyamande ramo doko baa lete karamuli pyuo karamwasa pilyamo.
Namwa Anatunya yulu reto kaeya nao pyuo kararama ramo doko baapa role pyao iso kararamasa pira. Banya kingi reto kaeyarama ramo doko baame namwana kingi reto kaeyarako.
Namwame banya yulu au pyuo rape rape lao pii nao karamanopape baame namwa yaki nyii nara. Baa rolae dupwa renge kniyuo pyuo karenge dokome alowa pipala kopetame pira ingya nalyamo.

Pii dakeme embena wambu dupwa dee kamba mana lamairi. Dopa pyuo Anatunya kingi lao nakama pii wakale wakaleme minyuo yanda pii nana lao lamaipi. Pii dopale dokome wambu nyisa napala, serami wambu dupwa kokwa serasa pingi.

Emba yulu poraiyuo pipala Anatunya lenge kambu dorena angi yulu pingi wambuŋu lao kandaraminyi karape. Yulu akali angimi rangena yulu dupwana elya nyii nange. Dopale ingyuo Anatunya waili pii doko rolae mana lamairi.
Anatunya daa mee kopyali pii larami dokome Anatunya kata dupwana rekya lao paramili dopale dupwana wanjo karape.
Nakamame mana lamairami doko rete andake minjunya pipala ipwange nao isa ingyuo kulimbungi dopale. Aimeniasa Pallitasapa dolapo dokona mana lao karambinyi.

Nakama pii kinyi angi rolae lenge kata doko yaki nyepala wambu wambo kumuyami dupwa lopo neta epapeyami lao kyambo lao karaminyi. Nakambana pii dopale dokome akali lapona Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingi doko ipwa palyinyi nembo lamisa pilyamo.

Dopa laminyipape Kurisene yulu doko Anatumi kanda soo piyamo doko ama poral wakasa ingyaro karamo dokome isa paa nara. Dokona pii dasipa pyasi palamo. Kamongo baame apimoo banya lao soo karamo. Mendeme, Namba Kamongona karo lara ramo doko baa koo dupwana rekya lanyi nembo kararasa pira.

Anda andake dokona pete sanapengepe rara wakale wakale dupwa singi. Dokona lapo golope kana kulingipimi wasisi dee lapo isape yuupimi wasisi dupwa singi. Lapo ama yapasi ingilyamosa mee langa nyuo yulu pii nange. Lapome meeŋe lapala dokome andakarena yulu pingi.

Dokona suu pyao mendeme range waso poo pyasi ingyuo karara ramo doko baa yulu yapasi dupwana pira. Kamongo Anatumi baa rombo palyapala banya yulu mupwa lapo dupwa opetaeko pyakana lara ingilyamo. Dokona lao yulu keyange peparaena kapa pira ingilyamo.

Wanyane wambu keta suu pingi koo palamo doko wanjo yulu rolae doko anjuku lao pyuo Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingipi mona retengepe mona kyuu lao singipi dusipana ingyuo pyuo karape. Doko wambu mona yapasi paliramo Kamongo nyisinya lao ateŋa lenge dupwamoo pipya karo. Dopako pyuo kararami ramo doko kapa ingyara.
Angi see nange kopyali dupwame lalya lapala apiyanda pyuo pyakandarami ingilyamo doko silinyi. Emba dopaleko ingya napipi.
Kamongona kendemande akali dupwame pyakandarami ingya nara. Baame wambu pipya anjiki pyuo mana lenge akali keyange ingyuo elya kalo pyuo karena.

Baa akali kamba lao karenge dupwa kando anjiki koo pyuo nakamana yulu kyai pilyaminyi dupwa lao rolakamirasa pira. Baame kamba lenge dupwa kando anjiki pyuo lara ramo dokopa Anatumi kata wapwakamiramopa nakama mona kapu kyuo pii angi doko serami ingyara.
Dokopa Sataneme nakama rambu lapala banya kame dokona karapusi kareyamo dupwa kingi rekya lapala kapu kyuo eparamisa pira.
Yuu gii lumwa pinya piramo dokopa randa wakale wakale dupwa epara ingilyamo doko soo karape.

Akali peparae rango nao bange nyipuli nyipuli lao suu pyao rangena kingi lakando moŋokyaŋe soo pii koo keta palyuo lao endangi rakangepena pii see nao sangyu laa nao Anatunya kingi kokwa sili lao kararami.
Wambu yango kilya kando karo yango mendali saka nao yango mata kando yulu koona wangu lako karo pyakando pyuo pyao yulu keyange dupwa isa nembo kararami.

Nakamana puu minyingi dupwa nyuo yanda pimwal keta mairami. Mondo lao range wasa nao mee langa karapala moŋokyaŋena renge dokome palyuo pyoko pyoko laramo kararami. Yanengena rae maingi dupwa mona nyepala Anatu mona reta narami lyakande.
Anatunya kata angi dokona mee pele lao yongona mamba kiso karapala banya poralnya renge doko mata mairami. Wambu dopale dupwa waso karape.

Akali dupwana lapome enda mona pali nange dupwana andana papala kyambo lengenyili pyuo lao enda dupwa anamasi minyingi. Enda dopale dupwana koona renge palipyamo dupwame nyaa nyaa pupyasa punduo petaminyi.
Enda dupwa yuu peparae mana rolae nyelana piminyipape angi pii kinyi doko see nalyaminyi.

Akali Janisa dee Jambarisapame Mosesena pii sepala kamba leyambinyili pyuo akali dupwame pii angi doko sepala kamba lao karaminyi. Nakambana suu pingi rolo see nalyamosa kapa ingingi lao suu pingi doko isa penge.
Janisa Jambarisapa kopyali ingyuo kareyambinyi wambu peparaeme siyami doko suu pyao akali yulu koo doko pyuo karaminyi dupwana yulu repetale isa para ingilyamo.
Embame nambana yulu rolae pyuo karo dupwa soo nyepala moko rminyuo pilinyi. Namba Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyao maka napala mana lao karo wambu yango mona reto pyuo kareyonopa
randa andake nyiyu dupwa kandee. Namba yuu Andioko Aikoniuma Lisatape randa andake wakasa nyepala au palyuo kara nayo doko emba siiyako. Dopa pyuo randa nyiyunupape Kamongome namba kiiramo nyiya.
Wambu peparae Koraisa Yesunya arapu dokona Anatunya Imambunya yulu pinya mona nyilyaminyi dupwa randa nyerarmi lyakande.
Satane akali Anatunya yulu pii lao mee karenge akali dupwame yulu koo pyuo pao kamame koo wakasa dokona pirarmi. Wambu mendali kando dereke pii lami dokona nakama range keta lao nyuo lamisa pilyamo.
Pii emba mana langiyaminyi soo nyiinyi dupwa minyuo karare. Doko apimoome mana langiyami lao range soo karene.
Emba wamba wane dokopa buku Baepole pii poo pyasi doko mana nyii kande. Pii dokome emba singinya renge joo Koraisa Yesu kapa ingingi lao suu pyarenepa lete wal pyao nyera.

Buku Baepole pii peparae Anatu keta epenge. Dokome pii kinyi dokona mora pisinyi pyambuo pii kyal dupwana lasaka pyuo pingi. Yulu kopetame dupwana lao nyuo rolapala apa pyuo rolae pyuo kararama lao mana lenge.
Dopa pyuo Anatunya yulu pyakamaingi wambu dupwame mana nyepala yulu keyange dupwana mora piso pyulu pyuo pirami.

Koraisa Yesumi wambu kumasi dee lete karaminyi dupwa peparae kote lara dokope dee Anatunya lenge kambu dokonape nambame emba poralyuo dopa pyuo langilyu. Yesu Koraisa baa pano epapala Kiŋi ingyuo karalu kararamo dokona banya waili pii doko wambu dupwa polo lamaipi. Yuu gii rolae doko pyaka serape panda see nara doko mupwa daaŋa lao emba lamaiyuoko karape. Yesunya pii dokona kinyi letene lao suu pinya lao pyalana pyuo lamaiyuo wambu porainyi pyambuo nakamana koo dupwa pano lamaiyuo pyuo karalu karare.

Renge pii kinyi doko kale yukupala see narami lyakande. Nakama pii angi kinyi doko soo nyii napala rangena suu pingi dokona moko minyuo mana lenge akali rangeme rombo palyapala pii wakale wakale dupwa mana langinya lao kararami.
Nakama pii angi doko yaki nyepala sinju pii wakale wakale dupwa kale yukupala lao soo kararami.

Dopa piraminyipape emba yuu peparae rangeme kame pyuo minyuo karare. Randa eparamopa mee pyuoko karo waili pii keyange dokona mondo lao lenge akali ingyuo Anatunya kendemande akali ingyuo karo embena yulu peparaena elya pyuo pyuo karare.
Emba pyuo karare doŋo nambana yuu gii otara doko repetale pyaka sepelyamo. Namba Anatunya yulu dokona reke lao kumuo mairulyamo.
Namba range porayapala makandalana suu piyunu yuu dokona kaeya nao pao otapu. Imambunya yulu keyange dupwa nyelana lao suu pyao makando puu pao pupu.

Dopa pyuo pupunu dokona pyuo wini lapala yole nyero ingyaro silyamo. Yole rolaena kyawa rarange doko Kamongo kote pii rolae singi dokome yuu gii mupwa eparamo dokopa jera. Nambako iki jerande daa. Wakale lapo opetae baa epelyape lao mona reto iso karaminyi dupwana opetae ingyara.
Emba range porayapala walya lao namba kandala epare.
Akali Dimasa baa isa yuunya bange rae maipala namba yaki nyepala yuu Tesalonaika dokona peya. Akali Kurisene doko baa yuu Galasia peya. Dee Taitesa baa yuu Dalamesia dokona peya.
Luku iki dae karamo. Embame Make nyepala dae lanyuo epare. Eparambinyipa Makeme Anatunya yulu pyuo namba kapa nyisara.
Akali Tikikasa yuu Epesasa pena leyo.

Emba dae epana dokopa nambana komau pee pingi andake yuu Toasa range Kapasana andana yaki nyiyunu doko minyakao ipupi. Dopa pyuo epo dokopa nambana buku dupwa opetae minyakao epo dokopa buku kuki namba rangena pii pyao palyingi dusipa kame see napipi.
Ane kapa wasingi akali Alekesanda dokome namba randa andake jiya. Baa apa pyuo piya lao Kamongome yano pyara.
Baa waili pii lao kareyama dokona imbu singi mandeya dokona emba range baapa kandokondali pyuo karape.
Namba kanda soo kote leyami dokopa mendeme nambana lao nyisapa nayami. Mee peparaeme namba yaki nyuo kaeyami. Anatumi nakamana koo piyami dokona suu pyao kaeyakaminya leto.

Dopa piyaminyipa Yesumi namba role pyao karapala banya poralnya renge jiya. Jiyamo dokona waili pii angi doko lamaiyunupa Juu daa rara wakale dupwa peparae kapa siyami. Mende doko namba mena laenena nenge kata dokona Anatu baame nenge raka lao nyiya.
Kamongome namba yulu koo dupwana kingi raka lanyi nembo banya yake panda iso karenge dorena mondo lao lanyuo para. Dokona lao banya kingi doko neta renge ingyuo sulu sinya, doko kinyi.
Pirisila Akuilapa yako lao dokopa Onesiporasana ree palu opetae yako leto.
Irasatasa yuu Korina dokona karo kaeyamopa, Topimasa baa anga piyamosa yuu Mallitasa dokona yaki nyiyu.
Emb kupwa pingi pyaka sepa naramo dokop wambo ipulinya suu pyao karape. Yupyulasamoo, Pyutenesa, Lalnass Kolotiamoo dee lapo dupwa opetaem yako letaminyi.
Kamongome nakama pipya rol pyao kararamopa Anatunya mon keyange palyuo ipingi doko nakama ket palena.

Namba Pole Anatunya kendemande akali ingyuo karo Yesu Koraisana aposele akali dokome pepa pase pyao jilyu. Anatunya rombo palyisi wambunya kapa ingingi lao suu pingi doko andanyi pyambwapala pii angi namwana misi pii lenge doko nolakare lao Anatumi emba kyakale lao mapanyi peelyo pare langiya. Ene busiyamo dokopa Anatu kyambo laa nange dokome nakama lete karalu kararami lao kinyi lalu lao leya.

Banya yuu gii rolae dokopa waili pii dokona namwa nolako langiya. Langyapala dokopa waili pii doko namba keta jepala polo lamaikare lao namwana Lete Wal Pyao Nyingi Anatu dokome letonuli pyuo piri leya.
Nambana Kurisene wane angi Taltesa emba pepa dake pyao jilyu. Rakane Anatu Koraisa Yesu namwana Lete Wal Pyao Nyingi dokopana mona keyange palyuo ipingipi mona kyuu lao singipi emba keta palena.

Nambame yuu Kirita dokona karo yulu lapo pyuo maleyono silyamo dupwana pyuo otakareŋe lapala yuu dokona karape leyo. Dopa pyuo taone dupwana yaka lao Elyambu Pinginya akali mupwa lapo rombo palyare lao leyo kande. Pii dusipa kame see napipi.

Elyambu Pinginya akali mupwa doko baa pii pali naramopa enda mendaki ikinya akalingi ingyuo karena. Banya wane wanake dupwa Kurisene inginya lao kando karo kingi lakami naraminyipa mena rae lenge ingyuo kamba laa nao ando pena lao rapu pyuo karena.

Elyambu Pinginya akali mupwa doko Anatunya yulu rapu pyuo karenge dokona yuu peparae rolae pyuo karena. Baa mena marakal ingya naope imbwualana wangu lakapala imbwua naope biya naa naope walya lao langa pyakanda naope bange nyipuli lao suu pyaa nao karena.
Wambu eparami dokopa yako yako lao nenge pyuope yulu rolae dupwana mona retena. Baa range rapu pyuo karope rolae pyuope poo pyasi karope rangeme mondo lao rapu pyuo karena.

Waili pii angi Anatunya mana pii lengenyili pyuo pingi doko baa poralyuo minyuo karena. Dopako pira ramo doko pii rolae lamaiyuo wambu serami dupwa andanyi nembo pirasa pira. Dopa pyuo pira dokome wambu pii rolae rae mai nange dupwana pii kyai ingilyamo lao lasaka pyuo nolakara.
Wambu malumi mee pii kopetame lapala pii angi doko nembo wakale dupwa kando panga soo lao karenge. Juu yanenge kalomasi dee Kurisene ingiyami dupwa panga sooko karaminyi.
Akali dopaleme kana mone nyimwali lapala yulu ama koo pyuo pii kopetame mana lamaiyuo ree palu wambu dupwana suu pingi bolombaio lanyi nembo randa mailyaminyi doko kaena lamairi.
Kirita wambu rangena poropeta akali mende dopa leya. Kirita wambu yuu peparae kyambo lao mena rae lenge dopale ingyuo maka suku suku napala nenge nyura nao pyuo karenge leya kande.
Pii doko kinyi leya. Dokona lao nakamana Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingi doko kapa andaramo dokona pii poralyuo lao pyalana pyuo lamaiyuo karape.
Juu wambunya sinju pii dupwape dee isa wambu lapo pii angi yaki nyiyami dupwana mawa pii dupwape mmyuo kara nana.

Wambu mona rolae singi doko kata yulupi dupwa peparae rolae ingyuoko penge. Wambu mona karo petenge Yesu mona mai nangena mona anda dee yulupi dupwa koo ingyuo singi dokona yulu peparae rolae ingyuo paa nange.

Nakama kambu dokome Anatunya wambuŋu lao yulu piminyi dupwame banya ingyuo paa nalyamo. Nakama kamba lao yango mende kando awa epekanda napala yulu koo pingi dokome yulu keyange pinya saka nalyaminyi.
Pii lare dupwa Anatunya mana pii palamo dupwana iki moko minyuo lapengele.

Alemo dupwa biya malu nao enokwanyi nemba nao mona palenge ingyuo rangena suu pingi kame pyuo minyuo karena lamairi. Dokona ingyuo nakama Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingipi mona retenge yulupi dolapo pyuo karo randa eparamo dokopa porayapala karena lao mana lamaipi.

Endemo nakama Imambu Poo Pyasinya yulu pingi endana yulu dopale pyuo petena lamairi. Mendali koo keta palyuo kingi isa nembalana suu pyao kyambo laa nao biya malu nao pisarami ingya nana lamairi. Yulu keyange dupwa mana lamaiyuo petena.
Doko enda angi dupwame nakamana akalingi ikinyingipi rapu pyuo mona retarami dokona mana lamainya lamairi.
Nakama suu pingi rangeme kame pyuo minyuo mondo lao piso anda dokona yulu au pyuo pyuo nakamana akalinginya pii soo petena. Dopa pirami ramo dokopa lapome Kurisene yulu kooŋo lao laa narami.
Pii dokonako ingyuo akali parange dupwa suu pingi rangeme kame pyuo minyinya lao poralyuo mana lamairi.
Embame range yulu keyange dokona nyiso pyuo wambu yango dupwa lasaka pingi ingyuo karare. Pii angi dupwa suu pyao mana lamaipala mee langa male lalya lana pyuo laa napipi.
Pii angi dokonako larenepa akali dupwame pii dokona koo mende koto nyii nana lao karape. Dopa pirinyipa embena nyisu petenge dupwame namwa keta koo lao lalana saka napala elyuo karenale.

Yulu pingi akali dupwame nakamana yulu pyakamingi akali dupwana pii minyuo nakama rae mainyi pyambuo karena. Nakamame kamba pii laope waa mende nyakamiwape pii nana. Dopa pilyamano lao dokopa nakama mondo lao keyange pyuo karalu karena. Dopa pyuo pirami ramo dokopa nakamana yulu peparaeme namwana Lete Wal Pyao Nyingi Anatunya mana pii dokona ketae pyambuo piramisa pira.
Anatu banya mona keyange palyuo ipingi wakasa dokome akali peparae lete wal pyao nyelana piya doko nyuo paneya.

Banya mona keyange palyuo ipingi dokome dopa lao mana langingi. Nakama dae karo Satanena kata yaki nyepala yulu koo dupwana mona andanyi nemba nao suu pingi rangeme kame pyuo minyuo rolae pyuo Imambunya kata dupwana karalapape lao langingi.
Namwa yuu gii elyape keta pisarami lao namwana Anatu kamame wakasa dee Lete Wal Pyao Nyingi Yesu Koraisapa neta renge ingyuo panarambi doko iso karamano.
Koraisame baa namwana koo dupwana kumuo jepala namwa baa rangena wambu kipungi poo pyasi inginyi pyambuo kiiramo nyiya dokome yulu keyange dupwa angingyuo pinya suu pyao pimana.
Pii lasi dusipa nyuo mana lamaipi. Wambu embena pii serami dupwa poralnya renge dokome paleta mona poralnyi pyambuo pyalana pyuo lare. Mendeme emba kando ketae nemba nana.

Embena wambu yango dupwa kando gapomanepe kanjilipinya pii rape rape lao soo pisirami doko kame see nana lamairi. Gapomanepe kanjilipi yulu keyange lapo mairami ramo dokopa embena wambu dupwame mumu laa napala pinya lamairi.
Nakamame akali peparae kando mona seramopa yako lao anjiki pyuo karo mendali kando pii koo laa nana lao lamairi.

Wambo namwa range kopyali ingyuo kamba lao kopetame pyuo kareyama. Namwa yulu koo dupwana mona andanyi pyambuo kopyali yulu wakale wakale dupwa pipala dokona kendemande ingyuo kareyamako. Mendali koo keta palyalana kanda lyanolyano pipala wambu dupwa kando awa epekanda nayamano dokopa nakamame namwa kando awa epekanda nayamiyoko.

Namwana Lete Wal Pyao Nyingi Anatu anjiki pingipi mona retenge rengepe paneyamo doko baame namwa lete wal pyao nyiyasa piya. Doko namwame yulu keyange piyamandena lete wai pyao nyiyande daa. Anatu rangena sakao nyiso karenge renge dokona banya Imambu Poo Pyasinya manjo nyingi enengepe lete karenge enengepe dolapo jiyamo dokome namwa poo pyao lete wai pyao nyiya.
Namwana Lete Wai Pyao Nyingi akali Yesu Koraisa keta Anatumi banya Imambu Poo Pyasi peparae namwa pipya kulimbuo jiya.
Banya mona keyange palyuo ipingi dokome Anatu namwana koo dupwa nyuo kame sakao roleyamo dokona namwa lete karenge dokona lao nyimwali yaka lao suu pilyamano doko kapa nyerama.
Pii dake kinyi palamo. Anatu mona maingi wambu dupwame wambu yango nyiso embame yulu keyange dupwa yapo pyuo petena lao poralyuo mana lamaiyuo karape. Yulu dopale keyange ingyapala wambu nyisingi.

Kopyali ingyuo apiyanda pyuo laa nao mumbwange kauwange kamongo dupwana kingi lasi londe dupwa minyuo dopale kandale lao pyuo lao karare doko kapa ingyuo paa nalyamo. Lalya laa nao Lowa pii dokona lao suu pyao sisi nyuo kara napipi. Dusipame mendali nyisa nao mee ingyuo pelyamo.
Wambu lapome Elyambu Pinginya yulu kwaenyi nembalana nembo nembo minyuo larami ramo yuu lama rolo lamairinyi see narami ramo dokopa role pyao yalya kando pisa nalapape.
Akali dopale baa Anatunya Imambunya yulu suu pyaa nao kumasi kyukurenge karo banya koo dupwame baa akali kyal lao lasaka pingi doko emba silinyi.
Nambame Atemasa panda Tikikasapa nakama keta pena laro dokopa namba kupwa pingi yuu gii dokopa yuu Nikopolisa karalana dokona emba opetae Nikopolisa ipili lao suu pilyu dokona waiya lao ipupi.
Lowa minyingi akali Sinasa Apolosapa ene epena pirambinyi dokopa emba nyiso bange peparae nakamba yangyarali dupwa mairinyi eparambi.
Namwana wambu dupwa yulu keyange pyuo nakamana wambu yango nyiso yangyarali dupwa mamgiŋi lao mana lamaipi.

Wambu dae yalya kando pisimwa dupwa peparaeme nakama kando yako letaminyiko. Yako lenge pii doko namwana Kurisene yango dupwa lamaiyakape. Anatunya mona keyange palyuo ipingi doko nakama peparae keta palena.

Namba Pole Koraisa Yesunya namba reke lao karapusi akali karo dokome pepa pyao jilyu. Nambapa namwana yangonge Timoti dokopa emba namwana puu minyingi keyange yulu mendakinya pingi dokona yako letambano.
Dokona nambame pepa pase pyao namwana pemalenge Apia dee namwana yanda singi yango Akapasapa pyao mailyu. Doko Elyambu Pingi wambu embena anda dokona Anatu lakandenge dupwa yako lao pepa dake jilyu.
Namwana Rakane Anatu dee Kamongo Koraisa Yesupa nakambame mona keyange palyuo ipingipi mona kyuu lao singi rengepe nakama keta jinya leto.
Yangone Pilimone sepe. Nambame ateŋa lao dokopa emba suu pyapala embena kingi lakao Anatu kando sangyu lao pingi.
JCamongo Yesu kapa ingingi lao suu pyao Anatunya wambu dupwa mona reto pyuo karene laminyi soo karo dokona ateŋa lakapa pilyu.

Namwa nakama pipya yalya kando Kurisene ingyuo petenge dokona lao nambame ateŋa lakao karo. Dokona Anatumi namwa Koraisana arapunya karenge dokona renge keyange nyingi dupwa peparaena lao soo gisalase lao lasaka pira.
O yangone, embena mona retenge dokome namba nyuo rae maiyuo poralnyi pyambuya. Dopa pyuo emba Anatunya Elyambu Pingi wambu dupwa peparaena monarena rae mainyi pyambwakamiyoko.
Renge dokona lao namba Kurisene yangonge ingilyamo dokona dopa pyuo piri lao eŋa nembapala langiru ramo doko kapa ingyara.

Ingyaramopape emba mona retenge dokome namba pyapyamo dokona lao mee manda rao pisilyu. Namba dopa pilyu doko namba Pole Koraisa Yesunya pii lakala puu lao peeyamo dokome banya reke lao epapu lao karapusi pilyamo.

Nambame emba piso soo nambana ikinyingi Onisimasa doko poralyuo suu pyakape leto. Baa nambana ikinyingi angi Yesunya arapunya karenge. Namba karapusi dokona karo dokopa banya Kurisene rakange ingyuo kareyo.
Wamba baa yulu kopetame pyuo emba nyisa naya. Nyisa nayamopape epapu baa yulu keyange pyuo nyiso embapa nambapana mupwa ingyuo pelyamo.
Baa keta nambana mona doko yukwaro karapyamopa role pyapeta epapu baa emba range keta mapanyi peeyakalyo.
Namba waili pii dokona reke lao karapusinya karo dokopa emba dae kara napala namba nyisalana saka nalene dokona Onisimasa doko role pyao karambwali lao leto.
Emba nyisa lao poralyuo laa nalyo. Embena masinginya maso suu pilinyili pyuo pipi. Nambame mende maso pii napala embame suu pyarene doko piru.
Emba Onisimasapa yuu peparae role pyao kararamba lao baa yuu kuki lama neta peya rapisa.
